Qinee aniara rufiaidaqa. Qinee ani andeeqasee rainannimaqaranara irunanoo rufiarafa qini qumbiqa qimaqaidanoo.
Qinee andeeqara oosana faqa amiqira oosana faqa maree marunausa maridaqa. Anee minara iriseenana sia qini minni qisainaqa namuqaa qini mandaikamma qimaqaaqa.
Anee kuqaa qima afeekaikammasee aneenna ainainira faiqi qini dadaaqia. Ramoo ramaa imariasa sia qini nári uriqararanannai rafaaqafu qimaqaaqa.
Oo Yaawee qinee ani asumu mara qimaqaranara kisaaqasaa rakisidaqa marunanoo qifuki qaunduaridanoo. Anee qini namuqaa nisaukukinaana rafiaranara qima afeekaikamma qoonnanara afeesi marunanoo qifuki qaunduaridanoo.
Oo Yaawee aneenna sia taikaaninna amuqusirana amana kai qini amiqimma qimaqasee aneenna naamuaqira ufa daamua qia.
Oo Yaawee qinee ani ainainira fasiqa maridaqa anee irirana oosana qiminaqa qinee ani naamuaqira ufa oosana irianaura.
Oo Yaawee faiqí anaasee ani sandufa rukieemarianara anee oosana uqannifiqara aukuana doo kambiqaidanoo.
Ani naamuaqira ufara qini didirafa koora uraaqaranoo maridanoo. Kaaqa amiqira koora uqanna faqa uraaqaranoo maridanoo.
Minara qinee ani aiqama naakapara ufa afaqaidaqa aiqama aaqara oosanara fidiaqaa idaqa.
Ani naakapara ufa kaaqa amiqirafa marifaqa qinee qeeqa qimuqusa aiqamannoo afaqaidaqa.
Ani naakapara ufa oosana qimannimirafa kaaqa qarana nimidanoo. Mi ufafa sia iri mariasa irirana nimidanoo.
Ani naamuaqira ufa aniranara kisaaqasaa rakisidaqa doo raqasee daannanai daannanai qida maridaqa.
Anee aniara rimamasara misa nifauee marianafa mariananoo. Anee qinee unnannai quandafi qini faqa qifauama qisaa.
Aneenna qima afeekaikunandee qinana qini saamuriranasaa itita qisaa. Anee qinanoo aaqara oosana fannoo sia qini rafaaqa fu qimaqaani.
Faiqí misa nári uriqararanannai qini rafaaqafidammia, anee minakinaana qini mara qisaa. Miqimma sainaqa qinee ani naamuaqira ufa mau fuanaura.
Anee aneenna oori afu amiqi amiqiranannai qini amiqimma qimaqasee aneenna sanda ufa daamuaqia.
Faiqí anaasee ani sandufa mau sia fuanara qini daukunu fannoo nammariara foora adiaidanoo.
Oo Yaawee anee kaaqa andeeqarafa mariananoo. Ani sandufa faqa aiqamausa amana amana kai andeeqa nimaqee marifa maridanoo.
Ani aataata fuaqee ufa fannoo kaaqa amana amana kai andeeqa nimaqee marifa maridanoo.
Qini namuqaa ani naamuaqira ufa minnisee mana mana imarianara qini aanoo qirafa idara foora qini qitaku qidanoo.
Ani qima afeekaikira ufa kaaqa mapukirafa maridanoo. Minara qini kaaqa dididanoo.
Qinee oorudupirausa marunaqa misa qiniara fidiaqaaidaqa. Miqi mariafaqa qinee sia ani naamuaqira ufara mana manamasee qaunidaqa.
Oo Yaawee ani andeeqarafa naaru naaru mariannoo. Ani sandufa faqa aiqama kari kuqaa anoona maridanoo.
Ummaara faqa inunurirafa faqa qiniki qumbiqaidanoo. Miqi marifanoo ani naamuaqira ufa fannoo asasirana qimidanoo.
Ani naakapara ufa aiqama kari amana amana kai andeeqannimaqee marifa maridanoo. Minara iriseenana anee irirana oosana qiminaqa maa maqanasaa kaqi marianaura.
Oo Yaawee qinee qeeqa qimuqusannai ani aaraidaqa. Qini nammeera qiranara qima qiminaqa qinee ani naamuaqira ufa mau fuanaura.
Qinee ani aaraidaqa qini mandainainakinaana uqeera qisainaqa qinee ani sanda ufa afaqaanaura.
Suani afu maqee urimarinana, anee qini dadaaqianneera aaraidaqa. Qinee qeeqa irirana ani qima afeekaikira ufasaa quqasee maridaqa.
Maqee eendirana namu faqa kaqi marunanoo qifu faqbaqa iaqaqaifaqa ani naakapara ufauqara oonu mafi iridaqa.
Oo Yaawee ani sia taikaaninna amuqusirafa marinara qini innaaruqirana iria. Aneenna nifauarana uqaqifiqasee qini marirana afeedamma qisaa.
Nidafirana faqa narirana faqa qimi mariasa adeedi anidaqa. Misa ani sanda ufa sia afaqee mariasa maridaqa.
Miqi mariafana anee Yaaweefa qini daaqa mariananoo. Ani aiqama naamuaqira ufauqa naaruara marifa maridanoo.
Qinee ooqai ani naakapara ufa iriqiafana. Mi ufausa anee qunaqa naaru marira ufauqaika mafiqau.
Qini aupurarana qafamasee minakinaana qini maraqisaa. Qinee sia ani sandufa qaununnanara miqimma qisaa.
Qinee ufaki marunnana ititaqimaqasee qini idukuqisaa. Anee aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana qini amiqiraqoo mara quqaqisaa.
Manda oosana maree mariasa misa ani sanda ufa mau sia fimariasa anee sia mareeqee amiqira qoo quqanniseennaranoo.
Miqi mariafana oo Yaawee anee qiniara amudaaoo qirafa firaaqoo marinara aneenna nifauarana uqaqifiqasee mareeqee amiqiraqoo quqaqisaa.
Qini namuqaauqa ummaara qimi mariasa moomoo maridaqa. Misa miqiqa mariafaqa qinee sia ani sandufasaaqari quandaki moosaa fiqa kaqi mi mau kai fidaqa.
Ani sanda ufa minnisee ueeqee mariasa qinee niqafamasee fidiaqaamma nimaqaidaqa. Sia ani naamuaqira ufa mau fimarianara miqidaqa.
Oo Yaawee doo qafaa, ani naakapara ufara firaaqoo dididanoo. Ani aidirafa sia moosaa fimarinara mariqoo kai marinara qini marirana afeedamma qisaa.
Ani sanda ufa oosana anoona maridanoo. Marifanoo ani aiqama andeeqara rainannimaqara ufafa naaru naaru marirafa maridanoo.
Misa faiqí uriqararausa misa fifau qini mandaikamma qimaqaidaqa. Misa miqi mariafaqa qinee ani sanda ufara kai qeerairammasee qaindusidaqa.
Qinee ani qima afeekaikira ufara firaaqoo asasidaqa. Mee faiqí moo fannoo koorara paqurimmasee asasindee qinee faqa miqi kai masee ani ufara asasidaqa.
Qinee aiqama unna ufara qikooqeenoo fidiaqaa uqanna qidaqa. Miqi marunanoo ani sanda ufara kai dididanoo.
Qinee aiqama faasaana moodaanai qisauku taikasee dinni oonu qaaraqanda marasee kari ani andeeqara rainannimaqaranara dufi dufi qimamaqaidaqa.
Ani sandufara nidi marisa asooaranaki maridaqa. Sia moo ainaina fannoo nikuama niminaqa saamurifaranoo.
Oo Yaawee anee qini asumu mara qisaanneera afeesidaqa anee daamuaqianna mau kai fidaqa.
Qinee ani naakapara ufa mau fidaqa. Qinee qeeqa aiqama qimuqusannoo minara dididanoo.
Qinee ani naamuaqira ufa faqa ani naakapara ufa mau fidaqa. Qinee aiqama ainaina auqee marunnana anee qafee mariananoo.
Oo Yaawee qini nammeera qirafa anee iannannai oorufuani. Aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana irirana oosana qimia.
Qini innaaruqirana irisee aneenna qima afeekaikammaqoonnana amana kai mara amiqira qoo quqaqisaa.
Anee aneenna sanda ufa qima qimiannanara qinee aiqama kari ani amooqianaura.
Ani naamuaqira ufa aiqamausa andeeqasee raina nimaqee marifa marinara ani sanda ufara idi raanaura.
Qinee ani naamuaqira ufa afaqee marunnanara aiqama kari qini dadaaqirara deedaqina maria.
Oo Yaawee qinee ummaaraki marunnanara firaaqoo ani afeedamma qimaqaranara rakisidaqa. Qinee asasirana ani sandufaki paquridaqa.
Anee maqee marirana qiminaqa amana qinee ani amooqianaura. Ani naakapara ufa fannoo qini dadaaqamma qimaqaani
Qinee auiara sipsipara foora auiaqa nidaqa. Qinee sia ani sandufa qimeesu uqimarunnanara anee aniree qini aneenna ainainira faiqi randasee paquria.
Qinee manda ummaaraki maridaqa Yaaweena aaraunanoo mifa eedoo qimasee dadaaqinoo.
Oo Yaawee unnaqimariasa faqa ueeqee mariasa faqa nisaukukinaana mareeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa.
Innee unna qimariasa Anutufa inni naqaa fee mannimaqaannoo. Mifa naqimmaseenoo fee inni aupurarana nimiannoo fee.
Sundia rakira feefannoo faqa fidika arira idaurunnai faqa naruannoo.
Inni qambaanai marirafa kaasau maqannaa aamina maqannaasa qambaanara foora mandaikiqa maridaqa.
Qinee asooaranara fidiaqaa imariasaki kisaaqasaa uqanna mariaafanausa maridaqa.
Qinee asooaranara qimarunaqa misa rakiranara kai qidaqa.
Qinee aaqanai qifu maqasee, qini dadaaqirafa yaindari fee aniannoo fee qidaqa.
Qini dadaaqirafa Yaawee finaindari kai aniannoo. Maa maqana faqa innaaruna faqa auqu quqoo finnaindari kai aniannoo.
Mifa sia aniara qinana aqufinnaranoo. Ani rakisi amaqee marifa aiqama kari afu maqaida maridanoo.
Isaraee maqannaasasaa rakisinnimaqee marifa sia moo kari qaunduarinoo sia faiqaidannoo.
Yaaweefa ani rakisi amaqaannoo. Mifa ani itita amaqarara ani aaqa maridanoo.
Suani fannoo faasaana sia naruannoo. Kafaa eendaki quqoona fannoo sia naruannoo.
Yaaweefa aiqama mandainainaki innisaa ititamma nimaqaannoo. Mifa inni nariranasaa itita nimaqasee innisaa rakisiannoo.
Mifa kai inni firannai anirannaira rakisi nimaqaannoo. Maqee faqa naaru naaru faqa rakisi nimaqaannoo.
Yaaweena amaana maaqai firaree qimasee qimaqimiafaqa qinee asasiqa.
Maqee maasa maaqoo Yeerusaree faandaamura kooqiki keeqafi afuqaki maridaqa.
Yeerusaree maqusa usakasoofanoo kaaqa amiqirafa atiuqa amana amana kai inoo maridanoo.
Isaraeena akeeku akaaku miqimmasee aniree Yaaweena naamuaqira ufa amana kai dufi dufi qirana amidaqa.
Maaqoo Yeerusaree maqannaa karaambaiqauqa nariqa faiqí anaasee ufa andeeqa nimaqararee qimasee ooqu mariqau.
Yeerusaree maqusa asooaranaki marianifeera innaaruqiaqa. Yeerusaree maqusara rimariasa aiqama ainaina rairaa iani
Oo Yeerusaree maqusa ani faandaamura afuqaki asooarafa kai mariani. Ani karaambaiqauqa nári maaqaki amiqimmasee mariaqa.
Qeeqa ainainara faqa qeeqa qiqoondiuqara faqa irisee Yeerusaree maqusara maaqi qidaqa. Asooarafa aniki mariani.
Yaaweena maasa Anutuna amaana maaqara irisee inni Yeerusaree maqannaasee irairaamma nimaqaranara innaaru qidaqa. Anutufa qimudaoo qirana amiani fee innaaru.
Oo Yaawee qinee anee iannannai qifu maqaidaqa. Innaarunai anee rakisi nimaqee mariannannai qifu maqasee dadaaqianneera innaaru qidaqa.
Ainainira faiqi nariqa rakisiranasaa nifu mundi mariandee iqa kafaa faqa ainainira maanaaqa miqikai inoo narí rakisira aanaaseesaa mundidanoo. Oo Yaawee maasa Anutufa maasa miqi kai iqa ani qafaqa maridaqa anee maasara qimudaoo qirana qimianneera afeesidaqa.
Oo Yaawee maasara qimudaoo qimasee qifauama qimaqaa. Maasa moomoo aasaandaana ufa qima qimaqaidaqa.
Ainaina faqaasa kisaaqasaa maasara uteeti qidaqa. Kafaa nári nimoo qimariasa nári mara maree uriranannai maasa rafaaqafusee ataasa ataasa qima qimaqaidaqa.
Yaaweefa maasa sia dadaaqinaqau naqaa fee unaiqini. Oo Isaraee maqannaasa minara qima qimifaqa iria.
Yaaweefa maasa sia dadaaqinaqau namuqaa nári aanoo qiranannai maasa qumarasee kaqi kasi marunaqa nambiqaa qini.
<range>
Miqinanoofau nammari aufirafa maasa maree fiqini. Kaifaa nammari maasa rafaaqafu qisaiqini.
Nammari aufinoo firaaqoo aiai qimarifa maasa ukuqnama qimaqaiqini.
Yaaweefa maasa namuqaara qifaqa sia maasa mandaikamma qimaqaanara maasa mina dufi dufi qimamaqaa.
Maasa ufiniara foora faiqí ufini ufanaki arurudukaki fiara foommiqa. Mi fasiqana ufaana raudafifaqa maasa qifaaqa quqasee mana mana idaqa.
Maasa dadaaqirafa Yaawee finnaindari anidanoo. Maqa faqa innaaruna faqa auqu finnaindari anidanoo.
Yaaweena saqariki mariasa Sioona aaqanara foora maridaqa. Sia amana kasi annoo sia moo fannoo mina mareeqee moosaa quqaannoo.
Aaqanauqa Yeerusaree maqusa fiqu fiqumma datinoo marindee inoo Yaaweefa narí faiqí anaasee fiqu fiqumma ititannimaqasee maqee faqa naaru faqa rakisi nimaqaidanoo.
Mandoosana maree mariasa sia amana andeeqarausa maqasaa aiqama kari rakisifaranoo. Misa miqifaqa andeeqarausa misasaaqaraa aaqara oosana maree foora.
Oo Yaawee andeeqara oosana maree mariasa amiqi amiqimmannimaqaa. Ani naamuaqira ufamau fimariasa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaa.
Miqidana anee manda oosana maree mariasa aupurarana nimidana ani ufa minnisee kaqi runna fimariasa faqa aupurarana nimia. Asooarafa Isaraee maqannaaki mariani. Manda ainainakinaana mara kaqinni uqannisaani fee innaaru.
Yaaweefa maasa Yeerusareenni qifiqee anufa qainasaara foora marinau.
Maasa firaaqoo naanaidara qida asasida idiree mariqau. Miqi mariafanaqa akaqa maqannaasa maasara maaqi qiqau. Yaaweefa firaa ainaina dadaaqinoo fee qiqau.
Kuqaa mifa firaa ainaina maasa dadaaqufaqa maasa minara firaaqoo asasiqiafana.
Aadaturunna aaku rifanoo nammari qumi marindee inana kaifaa maasa amiqi amiqimma qimaqaa.
Naukuna namu faqa ummaqi mariasa asasira idi namu faqa unakuaqanani.
Asumu ainaina ummaqiraree qimasee naukunu namufaqa maree munu ummaqusee mariifaqa nara aukuana unaku maree asasira idi namu faqa maree anifaranoo.
Yaaweefa sia maaqa usakaifanoo, usakara saika fannoo anoona siaifa mariqini. Yaaweefa sia maqusasaa ititee marifanoo aufari mari fasiqafa kikiqinoo marida rakisi mari oosanafa sia amanaikiqini.
Fifau kananaana eendai uqanna findifi ainaina kadaapirina fifiina eendi mariananoo. Yaaweefa narí aidi marisa faiqaqee iafanoo narana nimidanoo.
Faiqi asumu Yaaweefa kaqi nimi mari ainainafa maridanoo. Mifa kaaqa afaaramasee amiqi amiqimma qimaqaidanoo.
Kumaaraasaa maqainna faiqisa nári nikoona asaukuki rakira fasiqauqa duru feefara foora maridaqa.
Miqira fasiqa moomoo faiqi duru feefara foora mina asaukuki karariqa mariafanoo asasidanoo. Mifa ufa iriranaki mina namuqaauqa sia mina rafaaqa fifaranoo.
Yaaweena ufamau fimariasa asasidaqa. Mina naamuaqira ufasaa mariasa faqa asasidaqa.
Anee miqi marianafa aiqama kari ani kadaapirirafa narana ainaina amiannoo. Ani ainaina reemindeemirinoo marinana asasinnarannoo.
Ani anaaqa fannoo wainna sandara foora maaqaki mariranaki moomoo qaqama iraannoo. Ani akoonaiqi faiqiuqa oorifa amiqira saqariara foora ani narana nee marianna difaanina fiqu fiquiqa marifaranoo.
Faiqí Yaaweena ufamau fimarifa miqimmaseenoo kaaqa amiqi amiqiannoo.
Yaaweefa Sioonna maqusakiqari inni amiqi amiqimma nimaqaani. Inneeqa kaqi marinna kamu Yeerusaree maqusaki aiqama ainaina reemindee mirirana qafaaqanani.
Innee kisaaqasaa marida inneeqa ninaiqimara niqafaaqanani. Asooarafa Isaraee maqannaasaki mariani.
Innee Isaraee maqannaasa innee kumaaraasaa maruqooqari inni namuqaa ummaara nimi maree ani marianara qima qimiaqa.
Qinee kumaaraa mariafannaqooqari qini namuqaauqa niranaqee marufaqa qini mandaikamma qimaqee mariqau. Miqidaqa sia qini uridaaqaree mariqau.
Maqarumasee afuqaki oora ateekee mariandee iqa namuqaauqa qini kaakadi qitaufaka runna oorara foora meemai uqanna ateekee mariqau.
Miqi marufanoo Yaaweefa andeeqarafa maridanoo rumbaranakinaana iduku qisanau.
Aiqama Sioonna maqusara fidiaqaa imariasa rafaaqa fusaifaqa anirandeeqa sandeefarannoo.
Misa maaqasaa ururee mari andanda fara foora urureenoo aadana usidanoo.
Sia moo fannoo mina suqu moodaanaki quqaidaqa sia rumbamaree fidaqa.
Aiqaree fimariasakiqari sia moo fannoo Yaaweefa amiqi amiqimma amaqaanifee qifaranoo. Maasa Yaaweena auqusaa amiqi amiqimma amaqaidee qidaqa.
Qini qimuqusa mandaikirafa faruma uqnauriara foora inoo marifaqa oo Yaawee qinee ani innaaru kiqari aaraidaqa.
Oo Yaawee anee qini nameera qirana iria. Anee aaqoo rammatinimmaseenana qini qiki raqarana iriseenana dadaaqia.
Oo Yaawee anee maasa aaqarana papiqaki kaqi akara rumasaina marinanoo yafee ani ufa nimiranaki fiqaraannoo.
Maasara aneenna afusaa naaquqamasee mariaqeera maasa manda oosana akiiqara minninnisee marianafa mariananoo.
Qinee Yaaweena dadaaqiranara asasida afeesidaqa. Mina ufa saqarikidaqa.
Qinee Yaaweena dadaaqiranara asasida afeesi marunafa aufari maria fasiqausa suani afu uriranara rakisi mariana uraaqaranoo maridanoo.
Yaaweena sia taikaaninna amuqusirafa marinara faqa mifa maasa mandainainakinaana dadaaqirara aidi marinara faqa irisee, Isaraee maqannaasa Yaaweena saqarikiaqa.
Mifa narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa nári aiqama aaqaranakinaana dadaaqiannoo.
Oo Yaawee qinee qeeqa qimooqirana minniseeqa. Qeeqa ramoo ramaa irana faqa minnisee qimeesa uquseeqa. Qinee sia firaa ainainauqara oonu mafi iridaqa, qinee sia amanaiki marunna ainainara faqa sia iridaqa.
Qinee sia miqidaqa, qinee asooaranaki qifaaqa quqasee maridaqa. Faiqi aanaaqi nári ninausa nifundanasaa ireeda faiqaqee iandee iqa marunanoo qini qimuqusa fannoo ireeda qiniki maridanoo.
Oo Isaraee maqannaasa maqee faqa naaru faqa Yaaweena kai saqari kiaqa.
Oo Yaawee anee sia Dafidinara qaunua. Mifa oosana oosana aupurarana maroonara faqa sia qaunua.
Oo Yaawee Dafidifa qima afeekaikunara iria. Mifa ani afeeka faqaa Anutuna Yakooboona Anutuna faqa qima afeekaikunara iria.
Qinee sia qeeqa faiqara maaqai fuanaura.
Qinee sia idooeeqa faiqeeqa ianauranoo.
Qinee afeeka faqaa Anutuna Yakooboona Anutuna maqusa deedaqammaseeqa inaaqianna faiqaanaura.
Maasa Beeteereeqeemma maqusaki maridaqa moodaanaki kira bookisara irisee Yeearimma afaasasaa paqurimmasee qafaqiafana.
Maasa maaqi qiafana. Anifaqa maasa Yaaweena amaana maqai oonuree mina ufa irira qaari oorinni oonuree amooqiaqa.
Oo Yaawee moodaanaki kira bookisa namu faqa mara maree aneenna naauqara uiqaana maaqaki ania. Mi moodaanaki kira bookisafa ani afeekara kooroo imarina faqa maree aniree maaqoo naaruara maria.
Ani aanaiqikirausa aiqama kari andeeqara ainaina kai auqaaqanani. Ani faiqí anaasee faaqa fuisee qidaqa asasiaqanani.
Oo Yaawee aneenna ainainira faiqi Dafidinara qima afeekaikinau. Sia aneenna utaaqamaqaanna karaambaiqana minni aisaa.
Anee oori kandamasee Dafidinara qima afeekaikinau. Sia kaifaa mi qima afeekaikirana rukaanauranoo fee qimasee qima afeekaikamasee maaqi qinau. Qinee ani faiqi namukinaana moo karaambaiqaika masaananoo anee kuqu finanoo mifa Isaraee maqannaasasaa rakisiannoo.
Ani faiqi namu qini moodaanaki kira ufamau andeeqasee fiqa qini naamuaqira ufa nimunnana mau andeeqasee fifanoo misa faiqi namu faqa anee kuqinaqa ani amaaqa maqasee karaambaiqa marifaranoo.
Yaaweefa narí faiqara maaqaikianifeera Sioona maqusa utaaqanau.
Maaqoo qinee naaruara maridaqa rakisinnimaqaanaura.
Qinee Sioona maqusanaasa nidi mari ainainausa aiqama nimianaura. Mi maqusanakinaasa kudi mariasa naranannoo amiqimma nimaqaanaura.
Qinee mi maqusanakina aanaiqikirausa mariasa auqainna aiqama ainainna amiqi amiqimma nisaanaqa minakinaa fasiqa anaasee asasira idi raidaqa faaqa fuisee qifaranoo.
Mi maqusanaki qinee Dafidina akeeku akaakukinaana afeeka karaambaiqaika masaanaura. Mi maqusanaki qinee qeeqa utaaqamaqaunna karaambaiqana rakisinnimaqarana afeedamma aisaanaura.
Qinee mi karaambaiqana namuqaauqa nisauriranannoo rafaaqafu nisaanauranoo. Mina rakisinnimaqaranaki mariasa amiqiranaki marifanoo aiqama ainaina irairaa iannoo.
Anutuna faiqí anaasee moodaanaki marida narí amiqi narí amiqirafa kaaqa amiqirafa maridanoo.
Mi amiqi amiqirafa Aaroona akiiaaqa oorifa fadameena amiqirana adiasoofanoo qumu rameeqee oosaumau qumundee ira amiqi amiqirafa maridanoo.
Mi amiqi amiqirafa Qeeramoona aaqanasaaqaraa qifi faramu Sioona aaqanasaa aqufinoo aiqama ainaina asooama nimaqaindee idanoo. Yaaweefa miqi qimasee narí amiqi amiqirana nimiraree qimasee qima afeekaikinau. Mi amiqi amiqirafa kisaaqa marirafa maridanoo.
Innee Yaaweena naaquqara amaana maqaki eendaki ainaini mariasa innee aiqama aniree Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Amaana maqaki inneeqa nisauku uqeerasee innaaru qidaqa Yaaweena amooqimma amaqaaqa.
Yaaweefa maa maqana faqa miri innaarunna faqa auqu quqoofa Sioona maqusakiqari inni amiqi amiqimma nimaqaani.
Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Yaaweena auqu mina ainainira faiqiuqa amooqiaqa.
Innee Yaaweena naaquqara amaana maqaki ainaini mariasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Yaaweefa andeeqarafa marinara mina amooqima amaqaaqa. Mifa maasara qimudaoo qimarinara mina auquara amooqira idi ramamaqaaqa.
Mifa nariara Yakooboona utaaqanau. Mifa mina akeeku akaaku Isaraee maqannaa fasiqa anaasee naríndi kiaqeera utaaqanau.
Maasa Yaaweefa aiqama unna qira anutusa firaaqoo uriqararafa marinara iridaqa.
Innaaruna ameemaanai faqa maqasaa faqa ooruku nammariki faqa mina aundurai faqa Yaaweefa narí aidiranannai kai imarifa maridanoo.
Mifa narí kai qifanoo asuru nannamu ira oonamu maqa dinni atindari uridanoo. Asukuna arira oonamuki Yaaweefa aakuasaa quqasaifanoo aaku namu faqa qumidanoo. Mifa narí afeedira maaqaki qariara foora ufaira qifanoo uqidanoo.
Yaaweefa Isipa maqannaasa ooqa faiqiuqa faqa misa aandau ooqa anaaqiuqa faqa moodaa karammasee narinau.
Miqoo mifa misa karaambaiqa faqa misa faiqí firaasa faqa aaqarana akiiqara aupurarana nimiraree qimasee misaki faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainaina faqa naaquqara ainaina faqa auqanau.
Mifa moomoo maqannaasa mandaikamma nimaqasee misa afeeka karaambaiqauqa kuqa narinau.
Amoora maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Sioonana faqa Basanna maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Ookana faqa Kannaa maqannaasa karaambaiqauqa aiqama faqa kuqa narinau.
Naruseenoo misa maqa maaqa rafieeqeenoo narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa niminau.
Oo Yaawee faiqí anaasee aiqama kari aniara Anutu fee qimasee koorooifaranoo. Aiqama naaru kambiqainausa aniara irifaranoo.
Yaaweefa narí faiqí anaasee ititannimaqasee narí ainainira faiqiuqara qimudaoo qiannoo.
Anaamuru mariasa misa unna qira anutusauqa koorannai faqa siruaannai faqa faiqí nisaukunnoo auquqoofauqa maridanoo.
Misa noo aamara marifaqa sia ufa qidaqa, nifu marifaqa sia qafaidaqa.
Misa naaqoo marifaqa sia ufa iridaqa. Misa naikaamaraindari sia uqanna kaqi kaaqoo naannamma naidaqa.
Mi unnaqira anutusa auqu quqoosa faqa mina saqariki mariasa faqa mi sia kasi mari ainainnara foora mariaqanani.
Oo Isaraee maqannaasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Innee aanaiqikirausa Aaroona faiqi namu innee faqa Anutuna amooqiaqa.
Innee Reefina aiku asauku mariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Aiqama innee minara innaru qimariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Sioona maqusakiqari Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Yaaweefa andeeqarafa marinara dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Aiqama unnaqira anutusa uriqararana dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Aiqama karaambaiqauqa afeeka urinnaaqararana dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa kai firaa naaquqara ainaina auqi marifa maridanoo. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa narí amiqira iriranannai innaaruna auqufa maridanoo. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa maa maqana auqeeqee nammari faruma amuaaqa quqanau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa suani faqa quqoona faqa auqinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa suaniara anee iaqaranasaa rakisiannee qimasee auqinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa quqoona faqa fasauqara faqa eendirana saa rakisiaqee qinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa Isipa maqannaasa ooqa faiqiuqa narinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa Isaraee maqannaasa Isipa maqusaindaraana aana muqunufaqa fiqau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa misa narí afeeka asaukunnai nifiqee finau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa Taatuqee nammari qambaana rakeeinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa narí faiqí anaasee minaki aana muqunufaqa fiqau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Fitaqa fufanoo Isipa maqannaasa karaambaiqa narí rakira fasiqauqa faqa oonuroofanoo ukuqnama nimaqanau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa narí faiqí anaasee nifu uqufaqa aadana maqa maaqaki fiqau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa maqasaa afeeka faqaa karaambaiqauqa narinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa firaa nuqu faqaa karaambaiqauqa narinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Amoora maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Siqoonnana arinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Basanna maqannaasa karaambaiqa mina auqu Ookana faqa arinau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Yaaweefa mi maqannaaqanda maqa maaqa rafieeqeenoo narí faiqí anaasee Isaraee maqannaasa niminau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Narí ainainira faiqiuqa Isaraee maqannaasa niminau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Maasa namuqaa rafaaqafu qimaqoofanoo mifa maasara sia qauninau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa maasa namuqaa rumbaranakinaana idukuqisanau. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Mifa kai faiqí faqa aiqama aandau auqu rarana faqa doodaani auqu rarana faqa narana nimidanoo. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Anutufa innaarunai marina dufi dufi qimamaqaaqa. Mina amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo.
Maasa Yuda maqannaasa Babiroonia maqannaasa rumbaranaki maridaqa Babiroonnia nammariuqa afainni ooqufaaqee idaqa Sioonna maqusara irisaidaqa iki raqee mariqiafana.
Maasa miqoo maridaqa doori runusee nariqa piripunna saqari asaanasaa diri qiafana.
Maasa rumbaqimaqee marusa maasara qidaqa idi raaqee qiqau. Idi raidaqa maasa asasirana qimiaqee qiqau. Sioonna maqusara rara idi rama nimiaqee qiqau.
Misa miqi qufaqa maasa maaqi qiqiafana. Maasa naqimasee fee aanaamuru maqa maaqakiaqa Yaaweena amooqira idi raanauree. Sia amana.
Qinee Yeerusaree maqusara qaunuseefau qinee sia kaifaa naaruara piripunna amana aruanaura.
Qinee ani Yeerusaree maqusara sia aiqama kari irifau sia amana kaifaa naaruara idi raanaura. Anee qini uriqarara asasirafa mariannanara qaunusee sia amana kaifaa idi raanaura.
Babiroonnia maqannaasa Yeerusaree maqusa faandaamura rakeemmasee keeqoo faqa Eedoomma maqannaasa namuqaa fuki faaki qidaqa Yeerusree maqusa rapeepaa iaqeera qunara Yaawee anee iriseenana mina akiiqara ia. Oo Yaawee anee misufara iriqaraasammasee sia qaunua.
Oo Babiroonnia maqannaasa innee kuridi fifaranoo. Maasa Isaraee maqannaasa saaroo qinana Babiroonnia maqannaasa narinafa asasiannoo.
Inni Babiroonia maqannaasa faiqi aanaaqiuqa qumaree maasa Isaraee maqannaasa saarooqi oonisaa rutukinafa asasiannoo.
Oo Yaawee qinee qeeqa qimuqusa ookiqari dufi dufi qimamaqaidaqa. Unna anutusa nifusaa ani Yaaweena amooqira idi raanaura.
Qinee ani naaquqara amaana maqa maritinai ubeekamafi qiqoori saunu arafi ani auqu amooqianaura. Ani sia taikaaninna amuqusiranara faqa ani mapukusee marira oosana faqa marinara ani amooqianaura. Anee aneenna auqu faqa aneenna naamuaqira ufa faqa aiqama ainaina urinnaaqararana uqannifiqoonnanara ani auqu amooqianaura.
Oo Yaawee qinee aaraunana iriseenana anee qimaqimiananoo. Aneenna afeekannai qini afeekaikamma qimaqaananoo.
Aiqama maa maqa maaqanaki maria uriqararausa ani Yaaweena ufa irianara ani amooqifaranoo.
Misa anee auqoonna ainainara faqa ani firaa afeekara faqa irisee idi reefaranoo.
Anee kaaqa mirinni uriqarana maridana ureeqarausasaa rakisinimaqee mariananoo. Faiqí nári nimoo naamoo qimariasa sia amana ani afusaaqari kukeeqeefaranoo.
Manda ummaara qini fiqu fiqumma datinoo marifana anee minakinaana qini amiqimma qimaqaananoo. Qini namuqaauqa aanoo qiafana aneenna afeekannai misa nindaqaa qimarianafa mariananoo.
Anee aiqama ainaina qima afeekaikamma qoonnandee innaranoo. Oo Yaawee ani amuqusirafa naaru naaru marifa maridanoo. Anee maasa Isaraee maqanaasara dadaaqiraree qunnana sia qaunusee minnisaa.
Oo Yaawee anee qini qimuqusaki diuqummaseenana qiniara irimariananoo.
Qini ooqu marirana faqa findifirana faqa aiqama ainaina auqee marunnanara faqa anee irimariananoo. Anee nianaindari qini Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakin Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakinaa Anee nianaindari qini qitikurakinaa iriranara irimariananoo.
Anee qinee ainaini marunnana faqa idooee marunnana faqa diuqimariananoo. Anee qinee aiqama ainaina auqee marunnanara irimariananoo.
Oo Yaawee qinee moo ufa qianeerunana anee faasai mi ufana aiqama irimarianafa mariananoo.
Anee qini fiqu fiqu ina datina aiqamatinai mariananoo. Anee aneenna afeekannai qini itita qimaqee mariananoo.
Ani qiniara irirafa kaaqa firaafa uriqaranoo maridanoo. Ani mi irirafa qini irirana faqa fiaaqaranoo maridanoo.
Qinee ani Yaaweena maraquna minnisee yaifee moosaa fuanauree. Qinee ani afu saaqari yaifee moosaa fuanauree.
Qinee innaarunai ooru firaree qianana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo. Qinee kuqirausa mariannai firaree qianana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo.
Qinee qaqamaree suani afu ururee marina ooqiaaqarama fuanana anee minni faqa marinnaranoo. Suani keeqee marina fiaaqaraanana anee miqoo faqa marinnaranoo.
Qinee mitinai marianana anee miqoo maridana qini aana muqunimma qisarara faqa miqoo marinnaranoo.
Qinee asukunara kukeeqa qimaqaannee qimasee kaaqa qarafa qini fiqu fiqu inoo marifa quandaki asukunaikiannee qiananoo asukuna fannoo sia ani afusaa asukunara foora maridanoo. Asukuna fannoo faasaanara foora kaaqa qaannoo. Asukuna faqa kaaqa qarafa faqa ani afusaa amana amana kai maridanoo.

Anee Yaaweefa kai qini daundurakinaa ainaina aiqama auqunafa mariananoo. Anee qini qinoona aranandaki qini qifaaqa moodaanaki ootupama qisaananoo.
Aniara rufiee mariafa mariannanara ani amooqidaqa. Anee aiqama ainaina auqee marianafa mookira ainaina naaquqara ainaina auqee marianafa mariananoo. Qinee minara qeeqa aiqama qimuqusannoo iridaqa.
Qini qimudaani moodaanaki ootupee marufana anee ireeda qini qinoona aranandaki moodaanaki quqaqisanau. Qinee miqoo kukeeqaranaki innooqee mariafanana anee qinee mariafannanara iri marinau.
Anee sia kambiqaqa mariafana qiqafanau. Qinee naaru moodaa moodaa faasaana auqaanna ainainara ani papiqaki akara rinoo maridanoo. Mi moodaa moodaa faasaanafa sia kambiqanoo marufanoo miqoo ani papiqaki akararinoo maridanoo.
Oo Anutu ani iriranara irunanoo firaaqoo ummaara darinoo. Moomoo uqanna maridanoo.
Qinee asaana ruananoo nukuda faqa arusee fiqaranoo mariannoo. Qinee faiqaqee marii findi fiqa ani mi iriranara kaqi kai irimaree fidaqa.
Oo Anutu anee mandoosana maree mariasa narinnaranoo fee qidaqa. Faiqí fidika ruqiqee mariasa qini quqasee fififaqa qeeqaraa marianauree qidaqa.
Misa manda ufa ani qimamaqaidaqa. Misa oosana oosana manda ufa ani auquara qidaqa.
Oo Yaawee aniara fidiaqaa imariasa qinee misa fidiqaqmma nimaqaidaqa. Ani ufamau firanara ititammasee aanoo qimariasara qinee firaaqoo qikooqaidanoo.
Qinee miqimariasara kaifaa firaaqoo uqanna fidiaqaamma nimaqaidaqa. Qinee misara qini namuqaauqee qidaqa miqidaqa.
Oo Anutu qini diuqummasee qini iriranara iria. Anee qini qimanammasee qini irirana oosanara iria.
Qini daunduraki manda ainaina qafamaseenana naaru marira aanaindari qinisaa rakisiqisaa.

Oo Yaawee mandoosana maree mariasa nisaukukinaana qini maraquqisaa. Faiqí nariqanuasasaa faqa ititaqisaa.
Misa aiqama kari mandainainara tupundaaridaqa. Misa aiqama kari aanoo qirana kai uqeeraidaqa.
Misa nifauru nimaakiri kuqimaria sakanifara foora maridanoo. Misa nookinaa ufa fannoo ukadiqa manda marasinnara foora maridanoo.
Oo Yaawee manda oosana maree mariasa afeeka ameemaanaindaraana qini ititaqisaa. Faiqí nariqanuasa qini qiku qama qimifaqa aqufuaneera misa tipundaridaqa. Minara anee misa saa ititaqisaa.
Nári nimoo naamoo imariasa qini qimaara ufaanara foora fufidaqa. Misa nári ufaana aatataa qini qimaara fufidaqa.
Oo Yaawee qinee maaqi qimasee aniara qidaqa. Anee qini Anutufa mariananoo. Oo Yaawee anee qini dadaaqianneera aaree marunnana iria.
Oo qini uriqarara Yaaweefa, anee qini amudaanai qimasee itita qimaqee marianafa mariananoo. Rakiranaki anee qini ititaqimaqaananoo.
Oo Yaawee sia anee mandoosana maree mariasa nidi mari ainaina nimia. Anee misa tipundaarirana ititannisainanoo sia anoonaikiani.
Anee qinaqa qini namuqaauqa sia rakiranaki uriqaraaqa. Anee qinanoo misa darirari maria ufafa quandaki nariqa naruani.
Miqi mariasasaa fidika arira ida auru adia nimaqaa. Misa dikaandaki aqusaina sia kaifaa minakiqari uruaqa.
Niqoonausara unna qimasee misa kikiqusi mariasa aiqama ainainirafa sia anoonaikiani. Mandainaina fannoo faiqí kuqa nariqanuasa rafaaqafuseenoo mandaikamma nimaqaani.
Oo Yaawee anee kudi fasiqa anaasee kootaki itita nimaqaannanara qinee iridaqa. Anee sarau imariasa amana amana kai itita nimaqaannanara faqa iridaqa.
Andeeqarausa kuqaa uqanna ani amooqifaranoo. Misa ani afusaa marifaranoo.
Oo Yaawee qinee ani aaraidaqa qini maqee dadaaqia. Qinee ani aaraanana iria.
Qini innaaru qirana amiqira afundimari ida munanara foora maraa. Qinee qisauku uqeerasee innaaru qirana eeneemari suqee maria tatufiranara foora maraa.
Oo Yaawee anee qini doosaa rakisianinna quqasainanoo rakisi marinanoo qini dookiqari sia manda ufa ururaani.
Qini mandainaina auqarara didi marina ititaqisaa. Manda fasiqauqaki ootupamafi misa manda oosana mararanasaa ititaqisaa. Qinee sia misa qoomaqa dadaaqi naanaura.
Andeeqara fasiqa fannoo qini aaqarana akiiqara qini dadaaqianifee aupurarana qiminaqa qinee minara qini amiqi amiqimmidanoo fee qianaura. Aaqee mariasa qiniara uriqarara fee qifaqa qimooqirana sia maraanaura. Qinee maqee maqee misa manda oosannara taikaannee qimasee innaaru qimarunnanara misa qimooqirana sia maraanaura.
Andeeqara uriqararausa manda oosana maree mariasa misa uriqararausa rafuseeqee maaninni aqusaifaqa faiqí anaasee qini ufara kuqaa anoonee qifaranoo.
Mi manda uriqararausa nimudaani saqari araira foora moomoo madika afaiqara irairaa inoo mariannoo.
Oo Uriqarara Yaawee qinee kaqi ani saqarikidaqa. Qinee ani itita imaqaranara randaidaqa. Anee qiniara qaoo qinaqa sia kuquanaura.
Qini qimaara qinukufana fufuqaanasaa ititaqisaa. Manda oosana maree mariasa qiku ufana fufuqaanasaa ititaqisaa.
Manda oosana maree mariasa nariqa ufaanaki aru fifaqa qinee amiqimmasee fuanaura sia minaki aruanaura.

Qinee dadaaqianifeera Yaaweena aaraidaqa. Qinee qiki raqaidaqa minara innaaru qidaqa.
Qinee qeeqa aiqama inunu rira ufauqa mina amidaqa. Qinee qeeqa aiqama ummaara mina qimamidaqa.
Qinee minnisara runanoo qinee andeeqasee qianna ainnainnara mifa iridanoo. Qinee fimarunna aannanasaa qini namuqaa qini qimaara kukeeqasee ufaana fufidaqa.
Qinee qeeqa inaaqiannai dadaaqiranara qafaunanoo sia maridanoo. Sia moo fannoo qini ititaqimaqaaninafa maridanoo. Sia moo fannoo qiniara qimudaoo qidanoo.
Oo Yaawee anee dadaaqianneera aaraidaqa. Anee Yaaweefa qini itita qimaqee marianafa mariananoo. Maa maqanasaa mariranaki maridaqa aniara kai ridaqa.
Oo Yaawee qinee dadaaqianneera qiki raqee marunnana iria. Manda ummaara fannoo qini nammariara foora ukuqnama saifaqa kuqiraridaqa. Qini namuqaa kaaqa afeeka faqaasa marianara qini misa nisaukukinaana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
Qini teerookinaana iduku qisainaqa ani faiqí anaasee suqiranaki ani amooqianaura. Anee qini amiqimma qimaqaannanara ani amooqianaura.
Oo Yaawee qini innaaruqirana iria. Aneenna andeeqaranakiqari qini afeeka innaaruqirana iria. Aneenna mapukira oosanakiqari qini ufa anoona qima qimia.
Sia moo fannoo maa maqanasaa qaraafa ani afusaa andeeqarafa maridaqa. Minara anee sia qini aneenna ainainira fasiqa mareeqee aneenna kootaki quqasee qimanammasee qafaa.
Qini namuqaa qini qifaqasee firaaqoo uqanna qini rafaaqa fidaqa. Mifa qini asukuna rumbaranaki quqasaifaqa qinee ooqai kuqusara foora maridaqa.
Miqimmasaifaqa qinee minnisarara deedaqidaqa. Qini qimuqusa fannoo munara minari marifaqa kaaqa kuquaqaa idaqa.
Qinee indaaru mariaafanna mariranara oonu mafi iridaqa. Qinee anee aiqama ainaina iannanara iridaqa. Anee aiqama ainaina auqaannanara qeeqa iriranaki minisee iridaqa.
Qinee innaarukiqari qeeqa qisauku anee iannannai uqeeraidaqa. Aadana maqara foora qini qimana fannoo aniara nammariara foora aididanoo.
Oo Yaawee qini marirafa taikaaqaammidanoo. Qini ufa irisee mina anoona qimaqimia. Sia qini qiqafamasee kukeeqaa. Anee miqinaqa qinee kuqirausa fimariannai fuanaura.
Aiqama kananaana anee daaqoo auqainaqa ani sia taikaaninna amuqusiranara irisee qeeqa saqarikirana aniki quqaanaura. Qini innaaru qirafa anee iannannai ooru fidanoo. Anee qiniara fuannee qinnaqoo uqaqifiqainaqa fua.
Oo Yaawee ititaqimaqaanneera anee iannannai fidaqa. Qini namuqaa nisaukukinaana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa.
Anee qini Anutufa mariannanara aneenna aidira ainaina qima qiminaqa auqaa. Qini amiqimma qisaseenana amiqira aanasaa ititaqimaqainaqa fua.
Oo Yaawee aneenna qima afeekaikunandee inana qini namuqaa nisaukukinaana maraqu qisaa. Aneenna andeeqaranakiqari qini ummaarakinaana mara quqaqisaa.
Anee qiniara aidi mariannanara qini namuqaa kuqa narua. Qinee ani ainainira fasiqa marunnanara nári uriqararanannai qini rafaaqafi mariasa aiqama kuridi nimaqaa.
Qini itita qimaqee marina Yaaweena amooqia. Mifa rakira oosana uqaqifiqaseenoo qini rakiranaki firana deedaqamma qisaidanoo.
Mifa qini aiqama kari itita qimaqee marifa maridanoo. Mifa qini auqaanara foora qini asumu maree marifa maridanoo. Qini amiqimma qisaanifeera mina saqarikidaqa. Mifa faiqí anaasee mareeqeenoo qini qiramandunnai quqaidanoo.
Oo Yaawee faiqí anaasee nana ainainee mariafanee anee misara iridanee. Faiqí anaasee nana ainainee fifau ainaina mariafanee anee misa rakisi nimaqaidanee.
Faiqí misa naidoora foora fuaqasaafanoo dauni taikeera foora irausa maridaqa. Mina marirafa nimanandara foora kaqi kaqi mandaaqee marifa maridanoo.
Oo Yaawee anee innaaruna rakee maseenana qumureenana aaqanauqa auqamasainanoo ida muna minakiqari ururaani.
Miqimmaseenana aneenna aakuasaa panana qirana quqasainanoo qumureenoo ani namuqaauqa furu faramma nimaqaannoo. Aakuasaa aneenna feefara foora dindai qinaqa quqasee sandaaqa.
Oo Yaawee anee innaarunaindari qini mara miami anaamuru nisaukuki nammari faruma kiara foora marunnana uqeereeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa. Anaamuru afeeka ameemaanai marunnana mareeqee kaqinni quqaqisaa.
Mi anaamurusa nifaurusaa unnufa kai qumbiqanoo marifaqa misa kuqaa ufa qiraree qimasee nimana aiqamasee unna ufa kai qidaqa.
Oo Anutu qinee aniara fuka idi ramamaqaanaura. Qinee piripunna aridaqa ani idi ramama qaanaura.
Anee kai karaambaiqauqa rakirana uriqarara afeeka nimimarianafa mariananoo. Anee aneenna ainainira fasiqa qini Davidisa namuqaa nisaukukinaana maree marianafa mariananoo.
Anee fitiqnarana qimi maria namuqaasa nisaukuki marunnana anee mara kaqinni quqaqisaa. Anaamuru afeeka ameemaanai marunnana mara kaqinni quqaqisaa. Mi anaamurusa nifaurusaa unna ufa kai qumbiqanoo maridanoo. Misa kuqaa ufa qiraree qimasee nimana aiqamasee unnufa kai qidaqa.
Maasa faiqi namu aanaaqisaaqari findifiqa ummaqira saqariara foora afeekaikammasee ururaaqa. Maasa qiraamuqmaaka faqa maqasaa karaambaiqa maaqakina amiqira afaaqa auqira sapatariara foora maridaqa maasa asasirana qimiaqa.
Maasa afeedira maaqaki oosana oosana nara ainaina qumbiqanoo mariani. Maasa maaqeena aandau sia kasoo anaaqiuqa uqanna maqaaqa.
Maasa maaqeena aandauqa kaifaa moomoo kiqa faiqi maqasaifanoo sia eedadaikinaqa kuquaqa. Maasa maqusaki sia teeroo faqa qiki raqarafa faqa mariani.
Miqi maria fasiqa anaaseesa amiqiranaki asasiranaki marifaranoo. Yaaweefa maasa Anutufa marifaqee qimaria fasiqa aanaaseesa asasiranaki maridaqa.
Qini Anutu qini Karaambaiqa, qinee anee uriqararafa mariannanara kooroo ianaura. Qinee ani naaruara naaruara dufi dufi amooqianaura.
Aiqama kari ani dufi dufi qimamaqaanaura. Qinee naaruara naaruara ani amooqianaura.
Yaaweefa uriqararafa marifaqa mina uriqaramasee amooqi mariafa maridanoo. Mina uriqararafa firaafa irirafa munu taikarana fiqaranoo maridanoo.
Anee auqoonna ainainnara maqee mariasa faqa naaru kambiqainausa faqa ani amooqifaranoo. Misa anee auqoonna afeeka ainainnara kooroo ifaranoo.
Misa ani qareenaranara faqa ani afeekara faqa ufa qifaranoo. Qinee ani naaquqara ainaina auquqoonnanara maqee maqee indee indee iqa fuanaura.
Faiqí anaasee afeeka ainaina anee auqee mariannanara ufa qimariafaqa qinee ani uriqararanara kooroo ianaura.
Misa ani andeeqaranara qima nimisee ani amiqi amiqiranara idi reefaranoo.
Yaaweefa aidi marifanoo nifauaidanoo. Mina aranaqarafa kasooaqee kasooaqee qimarifanoo mina sia taikaaninna amuqusirafa qumbiqaidanoo.
Mifa aiqamausa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaseenoo narí aiqama auqu quqaqoo ainainausara amuqusi marifa maridanoo.
Oo Yaawee anee aiqama aandau doodaani auquqoonausa ani amooqifaqa aiqama ani faiqí anaasee dufi dufi qirana ani amifaranoo.
Misa ani karaambaiqa afeeka areenaranara ufa qidaqa ani amudaanai qiranara qifaranoo.
Miqimmasaifaqa aiqamausa anee afeeka ainaina auqoonnanara irifaranoo. Misa ani afeeka areenara ququsara faqa irifarannoo.
Ani rakisi nimaqarafa naaru naaru marifa marifana anee naaruara karaambaiqa mariananoo. Yaaweefa narí qima afeekaika maqoo ufanasaa mapukinoo marifa maridanoo. Narí aiqama ainaina imarina nifauarana namu faqa idanoo.
Mifa ummaaraki mariasa dadaaqidanoo. Mifa rafaaqafu nimaqee mariasa uqeera nisaidanoo.
Aiqama kasi maria ainainausa narana nimianneera nifu mundusee ani kai qafaafana narana nimi mariananoo.
Anee misa nimana kai niminana aiqamausa nidirana amanaikiananoo.
Yaaweena aiqama ainaina auqaranaki andeeqarafa maridanoo. Narí aiqama ainaina imarina nifauarana namu faqa idanoo.
Mifa narí aaree mariasa naaqa maridanoo. Mifa nariqa nimuqusa ookiqari aaree mariasa naaqa faqa maridanoo.
Mifa nariara naaquqee marifaqa mina ufa qaindusi mariasa dadaaqira ainainauqa nimidanoo. Mifa misa qiki raqarana iriseenoo misa ummaarakinaana mara kaqinni quqannisaidanoo.
Mifa nariara rimariasa itita nimaqasee mandoosana maree mariasa kuridi nimaqaannoo.
Qinee aiqama kari Yaaweena amooqianaura. Mifa auqu aiqama ainainausa mina naaquqara andeeqara auqu naaru naaru amooqima amaqaaqa.
Yaaweena amooqia. Oo qini qimana Yaaweena amooqia.
Qinee kaqi marunna kamuqoo Yaaweena amooqianaura. Qeeqa aiqama kari maa maqa maaqanasaa mariranaki qeeqa Anutuna idi ramamaqaanaura.
Sia aneenna saqarikirana maqasaa qaraa uriqararausasaa quqaa. Sia faiqí faiqi amana ani dadaaqiannoo.
Maqasaa uriqararausa kuqufiqa kookoommaika mafidaqa. Mi faasaannasaa misa oosana oosana ainainara tipundaarammaqaafa taikaidanoo.
Yakooboona Anutunara dadaaqirana qimiannee qimari fasiqafa faqa Yaaweena nariqa Anutunasaa mundi mariasa faqa asasidaqa.
Innaaruna faqa maqa faqa ooruku nammari faqa minaki maria ainainausa faqa auqunasaa mundi mariasa asasidaqa. Mifa aiqama kari narí qima afeekaikiranasaa afu rusisee maridanoo.
Mifa uriqararanannai rafaaqa fuqaasa narí ufa iriranaki dadaaqidanoo. Naararee mariasa faa narana nimidanoo. Yaaweefa fifau rumbaranaki mariasa iduku nisaidanoo.
Iduku nisaseenoo nifu imbarausa nifu maqa nisaidanoo. Mifa aqufiqa mariasa uqeera nisaidanoo. Mifa narí andeeqara fasiqa aanaaseera aididanoo.
Yaaweefa asaqiraafai maasa maqa maaqaki mariasasaa itita nimaqaidanoo. Mifa adeedaana anaaseeuqa faqa fiaiqi faiqiuqa faqa dadaaqidanoo. Kafaa mifa manda oosana maree mariasa nariqa kuridiranaki quqa nisaidanoo.
Yaaweefa naaruara uriqararafa maridanoo. Oo Sioona maqusa ani Anutufa aiqama kari rakisi amaqaannoo. Yaaweena amooqia.
Yaaweena amooqia. Maasa Anutuna amooqira idi rarafa amiqira oosana maridanoo. Mina amooqirafa andeeqarafa adiafaairafa maridanoo.
Yaaweefa Yeerusaree maqusa kaifaa usakaidanoo. Isaraee maqannaasa narufaqa anaamurukiaqa moodaa moodaa iqa mariusa Yaaweefa kafaa suqeeqee quqaidanoo.
Mifa nimuqusa mandaiki marusa amiqimma nisaidanoo. Misa kaakadi narirana rumbannisaidanoo.
Mifa aiqama fasauqara iriseenoo asaana rirana amana kai quqaseenoo naadu naadu nuqu ranau.
Maasa Yaaweefa firaafa marida amudaanai qimarifa maridanoo. Mina amiqira irirafa sia oosana faqa ammuqu faqa marifa maridanoo.
Mifa nári mara maree qumi mariasa uqeerannisaidanoo. Kafaa mandoosana maree mariasa maqa mammaaqai radamidanoo.
Amooqira idi Yaaweenara rama amaqaaqa. Piripunannai aridaqa maasa Anutuna idi rama amaqaaqa.
Mifa oonnamu innaarunai rainaidanoo. Mifa aaku quqasaifanoo rifanoo amuaqu namusaaqaraa andandauqa ururaidanoo.
Mifa aandauqa narana nimisee ufini aanaaqiuqa naranara qiafanoo misa faqa nimidanoo.
Mifa qoosauqa afeekara sia ridanoo. Mifa afeeka sundiauqa rakiranaki paasoosi mariasa afeekara faqa sia ridanoo.
Mifa nariara naaquqaifaqa rufiee mariasara aididanoo. Misa nári irirana Yaaweena sia taikaaninna amuqusiranasaa rusimariasa misara aididanoo.
Oo Yeerusaree maqusaki mariasa innee Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Oo Sioona maqusaki mariasa inneeqa Anutuna kai amooqiaqa.
Mifa inni maqusa faandaamura kooqi afeekaikammasee ititaidanoo. Mifa minaki maria fasiqa anaaseesa amiqi amiqimma nimaqaidanoo.
Mifa inni Isaraee maqannaa oosusaa rakisidanoo amiqira narana inni nimana kai nimidanoo.
Mifa narí naamuaqira ufa maa maqana qimamisaifanoo mifa qii ainainafa kai kaqi kambiqaidanoo.
Mifa qaisara qifanoo aqufinoo qamunnara foora maqasaa rafaaqa fidanoo.
Mifa innaarunaindari pupusamu oonisamuara foora aqidanoo. Sia moo fannoo mifa nimi mari suaranaki amana kikiqiannoo.
Mifa pupusamuara qifanoo tasirisirinoo nammarikidanoo. Kafaa mifa ufaira qufanoo ufai uqufanoo qaisa fannoo firaa nammari kammafi ooqu finau.
Mifa narí ufa narí faiqí anaasee nimidanoo. Mifa narí sandufa faqa narí naakaparufa faqa Isaraee maqannaasa nimidanoo.
Mifa mi ainainna auqoona sia moo maqannaasa mina sanda ufa sia iri mariasarau auqinoo fau. Yaaweena amooqia.
Yaaweena amooqia. Innaarunai mirinni mariasa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Mina aiqama qangeeroouqa mina innaarunaindaraa rakira fasiqauqa mina amooqiaqa.
Innee suani faqa quqoona faqa aiqama fasau firaaqoo kaaqa qeemariasa faqa aiqama mina amooqiaqa.
Innaaruna meerai uqanna marianafa anee faqa Yaaweena amooqia. Innee mirinni innaarunai maria nammarisa innee faqa mina kai amooqiaqa.
Misa aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqanani. Mifa qufaqa misa kambiqaqau.
Mina ufannoo misa kambiqafi nariqa mariaqoo naaru naaru maridaqa sia amana Yaaweena ufa rukieefaranoo.
Maqasaaqaraa ainainauqa faqa ooruku nammariki maria firaa aandausa faqa nammari ameemaanai mariasa faqa aakuasaa faqa pupusamu faqa qaisa faqa oonnamu faqa afeeka ufai Yaaweena naakapara ufa mau fimari ufaifa faqa innee aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.

Innee aaqanauqa faqa amuaqu namuqa faqa qaqama iree maria saqarisa faqa aiqama nandauqa faqa aiqama aandau maaqeena faqa kaasau faqa nimuaqundari nimariasa faqa qaqamaree nimaria ufinisa faqa innee aiqama mina amooqima amaqaaqa.
<range>
Aiqama maqasaaqaraa karaambaiqauqa faqa aiqama maqannaasa faqa uriqararausa faiqi namu faqa aiqama maqannaa rakisirausa faqa kumaaraauqa faqa maanaaqauqa faqa asooqa fasiqa anaasee faqa faiqi uqaindi faqa innee aiqamausa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
<range>
Misa aiqama misoo maasoo Yaaweena auqu amooqiaqa. Mina auqu fannoo aiqamausa nuqu uriqararafa maridanoo. Mina areenarafa maa maqa maaqana faqa innaaruna faqa urinaaqaranoo maridanoo.
Mifa Yaaweefa narí maqannaasa afeekaikamma nisaifaqa mina faiqi anaasee mina amooqiaqeera. Isaraee maqannaasa mina afaaqasaa aqoondiuqa maridaqa mina amooqidaqa. Yaaweena amooqia.
Yaaweena amooqia. Yaaweena fuka idi ramamaqaaqa. Mina ufa mau fimariasa ufa suqiranaki mina amooqimamaqaaqa.
Isaraee maqannaasa inni auqu nisoonara irisee asasiaqa. Sioona maqusaki mariasa inneeqa karaambaiqara susumma amaqaaqa.
Innee idi raida niqoori raqaranannai faqa dukaanaannai faqa piripunnannai faqa mina auqu amooqiaqa.
Yaaweefa narí faiqí aanaaseera asasidanoo. Nári mara maree qumimariasa rakirana uriqararanannai amiqimma nimaqaidanoo.
Yaaweena faiqí anaasee nariqa rakiranara qufoonaridaqa asasira idi eendaki raqa fifi iaqaaqa.
Misa firaaqoo faaq rumasee Anutuna amooqiaqa. Misa nisaukuki dinni dinni raiqarana rakira paipana kaqi marinaqa mina namu faqa amooqiaqa.
Kaqi marifaqa misa minannai aanaamuru rafaaqa firara uaqee idaqa. Anaamuru fasiqa anaasee narirara uaqee idaqa.
Misa karaambaiqauqa sainandannai rumbarana uaqee idaqa. Misa karaambaiqauqa qainna sainandannai rumbarara uaqee idaqa.
Anutufa naamuaqundee iqa moo maqannaasa narirara uaqee idaqa. Anutuna faiqí anaasee rakirana uriqararafa miqimminoo maridanoo. Yaaweena amooqia.
aaweena amooqia. Anutuna naaquqara amaana maqaki mina amooqiaqa. Mina uriqarara afeeka innaaru nai marina amooqiaqa.
Mifa afeeka ainaina auqoo nara amooqima amaqaaqa. Mina amiqira uriqararanara amooqiaqa.
Ukeena fuaqaidaqa minannai mina amooqiaqa. Kaqikaa piripunnannai faqa firaa piripunnannai faqa mina amooqiaqa.
Dukaanaannai faqa idi raida niqoori raqaranannai faqa mina amooqiaqa. Piripunnannai faqa ufireenannai faqa mina amooqiaqa.
Innee qumiandau qaqama kaqikaa qanda faqa firaa qanda faqa qumaree narisaa narisaa ramoo ramoo idaqa Yaaweena amooqiaqa.
Aiqama naanna faqaa ainaina Yaaweena amooqiaqa. Yaaweena amooqia.
Maa aaquqira ufafa Soroomoonna ufa maridanoo. Dafidina amaaku Isaraee maqannaa karaambaiqa ufa maridanoo.
Maa aaquqira ufafa ani dadaaqinana amiqira irirana faqa andeeqara naamuaqira ufa faqa irisee mina oosana farumara foora meemai uqanna marina faqa irinnaranoo.
Irirana faqaa nira marirana uqannifiqara ufa maridanoo. Anoona ufa kai qira oosana faqa andeeqara oosana amana amana kai raina nimaqara oosana faqa nimianifeera maa ufafa maridanoo.
Maa ufafa irirana siaisa irirana nimidanoo kumaaraa maanaaqa irirana naakapama saina amiqira nira marirana faqaasa mariaqeera maa ufafa maridanoo.
Maa aaquqira ufafa irirana faqaasa irirana moo faqa moo faqa nimimarifa maridanoo. Amiqira irira aanara randee mariasa nimimarifa maridanoo.
Uqannifiqaafaqa aaquqira ufa oosana kukeeqarana faqa irirana faqaasa kukeeqara mariranauqa faqa irifara.
Anee irirana faqaafa mariraree qimasee Yaaweena ameemaanai maria. Furufari mariasa sia iriranara naaquqaidanoo irirana mararanara faqa nikooqaidanoo.
Qinee qimaaku anoofakoona ufa iria.
Ani anoona akoona aamuaqira ufa fannoo ani amiqira fasiqaikamma amaqaannoo, amiqira sarandaraqara foora aqinaaqa rumbasee kukukakana anukaki rufu amaqeera foora masainana amiqirafa marinnaranoo.
Qini qimaaku manda oosana maree mariasa ani amanifana sia misa ufa iria.
Misa aniara maaqi qifaranoo. Anee maasa faqa anirainaqa maasa faiqí kuqa narua. Aninaqa kukeeqafi qeeqa didirana taikeeqa oosana siaisa kuqa narua.
Misa kaqi marida amiqiqa marifaranoo maasa misa paqurimmasaanaqa kuqifaranoo. Amiqira fasiqa faqa manda fasiqa faqa dapi naruanauranoo.
Misa naruseeqa misa qumiasana oosana oosana mareeqee maasa nári maaqaki quqasaananoo maasa maaqa qumbiqaani.
Anee maasa faqa aninaqa maasa ummuara masainna aiqama ainaina ani faqa naida amianaura.
Qini qimaaku sia miqira fasiqa faqa fua. Misa mariaqooqari nianai maria.
Misa mandainaina auqarara sia anuqidaqa. Misa aiqama kari fidika ruiqaranara deedaqiqa maridaqa.
Anee ufini ufana fufinana sia aruani qinna ufinina afusaa fufua. Mifa qafamasee rufiaannoo.
Miqi maria fasiqausa nári nimaara ufaana fufidaqa. Nariqa ninuka arusee kuqifandinna ufanna fufidaqa.
Faiqí nári marusa mi oosanafa nariiundee inoo ummuari mariasa mi ummuarira oosanafa nári naruannoo.
Iriaqa, amiqira irirafa irirana faqaa anaas eera foora aana kindooraki faqa faiqí suqi mariaqoo maridanoo nammeera qidanoo.
Faandaamura ququsa kooqiki faiqí suqi mariaqoo maridanoo firaaqoo nammeera qidanoo.
Innee furufarirausa innee kisaaqasaa fee furufarida marifaree, innee kisaaqasaa fee irirana faqaasa iriranara uteeti qifaree. Sia fee innee minara irifaree.
Innee qini aaquqira ufa amiqimmasee iriaqa. Qinee qeeqa amiqira naakapara ufa faqa qeeqa irirana faqa inni nimianaura.
Inni naarauna sia irimariafanoo. Aniaqee qunaqa innee qini ufa irisee mana mana imariafanoo.
Innee qini naamuaqira ufa nimeesuqusee qini andeeqa nimaqaranara sia nididanoo.
Qinee irirausa innee umaaraki aqufi saamurifaqa qinee inniara naanaidara qianaura. Innee mandainainaki aqufifaqa qinee ataasa ataasa qima nimaqaanaura.
Mandainaina fannoo firaa aaku ufaira foora anireenoo inni nifu mara ookeendaandaa meeqeenoo aqusaannoo. Nidafirafa faqa ummaara faqa inni rafaaqafu sainaqa qinee naanaidara qianaura.
Innee mi mandainainna kiqari iriranara qini irirana faqaasa daaraifaa qinee sia irianaura. Innee firaaqoo qiniara aiqamai randeeqa sia paqurifaranoo.
Innee iriranara mandainainee qimasee sia Yaaweena ufa qaindusi mariafanoo.
Innee qini naamuaqira ufara sia nididanoo. Qini andeeqa nimaqaranara sia nididanoo.
Innee inneeqa mandoosana akiiqara feefauru marasaifanoo inni auriranara foora nimiannoo.
Irirana siaisa amiqira irirana nimeesa uqaanara kuqidaqa. Furufari mariasa amiqira irirafa sia marinara mandaikidaqa.
Yafasiqa fee qini irirausa ufa irinanoo mi ufafa minasaa rakisi amaqaanoo. Mifa asumu marinanoo sia mandainainara rufiara oosana mariannoo.
Qini qimaaku iria qinee auqaannee qimasee qimamianna ufana sia qaunua.
Amiqra ufa amiqimmasee iriseenana minara oonumafi iria.
Eeoo amiqira irirafa anee iannannai anianinnanara iramirisee iria.
Amiqira iriranara siruaa maqaki marifaqa randee mariandeemmasee randaa. Kukeeqara amiqira iriranara akaqa ainaina maqaki kukeeqaqaafaqa randee mariandeemmasee randaa.
Miqinana anee Yaaweenara rufiara oosanara iriseenana Anutunara irinnaranoo.
Yaaweefa kai amiqira irirana nimidanoo. Mifinnaindari kai irirafa faqa oonumafi irirafa faqa anidanoo.
Kuqaa anoona ufa kai qimariasa faqa andeeqara oosana maree mariasa faqa Anufufa dadaaqida itita nimaqaidanoo.
Anutufa faiqí amana amana kai amiqimma nimaqee mariasa faqa mina ufa mau maqee maqee fimariasa faqa Anutufa itita nimaqaidanoo.
Qini qimaaku anee qini ufa irinana amiqira ainainara faqa andeeqara oosanara amana amana kai rainara oosanara faqa irinnaranoo. Anee aneenna auqainna amiqira oosanara faqa irinnaranoo.
Anee moomoo amiqira irirana marasainanoo mi irirafa ani asasirana amiannoo.
Ani amiqimmasee marirafa faqa amiqira irirafa faqa anisaa itita amaqaannoo.
Mifa kai anee manda ainaina auqaranasaa itita amaqaannoo. Ummaara kambiqaanifeera qimariasa ufasaa itita amaqaannoo.
Miqi maria fasiqausa andeeqara marirana minnisee numoo asukunaki maridaqa.
Oosana oosana manda oosanara nidi marisa faqa amiqira irirana sia mari manda oosanara asasimariasa faqa furufara foomboo rimaria fasiqausa ufara faqa eerairiaqa.
Miqi maria fasiqausa oosana sia andeeqanoo maridanoo. Misa eerairi mariasa maridaqa.
Anee qini andeeqara ufa irinanoo moo fasiqa anaaqa fannoo narí fadameena akira ufannai aniara anirainaqa manda oosana auqaanee qinanoo mi amiqira irirafa ani itita amaqaannoo.
Miqira anaasee fannoo narí afaaqiara sia irirai Anutuna afusaa naaquqara qima afeekaikirufa qimaqoonara qaunuseenoo narí afaaqi minnisaidanoo.
Anee miqi mari anaaseena maaqai finana anee kuqirannai fimaria aatata finnaranoo. Minni finana kuqirausa maria maqa maaqanakiara foora finnaranoo.
Mi anaaseefinnai finafa sia kafaa oonurandee aninnaranoo. Anee sia kafaa oorurandee kaqi marira aanasaa aninnaranoo.
Anee amiqira irirana marirana mareenana andeeqara fasiqauqa naanna reenana amiqira marira marinnaranoo.
Andeeqara fasiqa anaasee faqa oosana siai fasiqa anaaseesa maqa maaqanara maasaindi fee qimasee minaki marifaranoo.
Miqiqa marifanoo Anutufa mi maqa maaqanaki manda oosana maree mariasa ummaqira ainainara foora raraku aquannoo.
Qini qimaaku qinee qimamianna ufana sia qaunua. Qinee qimamianna ufana aiqama kari iridana qinee qimamunnandee ia.
Qinee qimami marunna ufafa ani kuqirana kisaaqasaa sainana maridana amiqiranaki reemindeemi riranaki marinnaranoo.
Mapukusee marirana faqa fisoo fisoo irana faqa mi ainainna qanda mareeqee saufauruara foora rumbasaina anukaki mariani, aneena amuqusaki akara rumaqaina mariani.
Anee miqinnanannai faiqí faqa Anutufa faqa aniara nidifaranoo.
Aneenna amuqusa aiqamannai karaambaiqa saqarikia. Sia anee aneenna iriranara amanammifoo qimasee minasaa mundua.
Anee aiqama ainaina auqeenanana Yaaeenara ani aaqooki marinana kai auqaa. Miqimmasee finanoo mifa andeeqara aana ani uqafiqaannoo.
Sia anee aneennara irirana faqaasee qimasee mana mania. Karaambaiqa ufa mau fidana manda oosana auqarara qeerairia.
Anee miqinnanannai amiqira marasinnara foora ani afaaqai nammuana qunuseenoo aidafirana taika sainana amiqirafa mariannandee ina marinnaranoo.
Anee aneenna nara ainaina amiqirana kai aneenna maqakinaana unakuseenana Anutuna tatufirana suqa amia.
Anee miqinanoo Yaaweefa ani ainaina moomoo afuqaki rairaamma amiannoo. Anee miqinanoo Yaaweefa quandaki ani narana nammari moomoo rairaamma aminana afeedira maqaki quqararee qimasee sia amanai kinnaranoo.
Oo qini qimaaku Yaaweefa ani andeeqainana sia anee minara akooqaani, Yaaweefa aaquqira ufa qimidanoo fee qimasee amiqimmasee iria.
Yaaweefa narí aidi marisa aaqee foora andeeqa nimaqaidanoo. Faiqi anoofa akoofa narí faiqi andeeqaindee inoo miqidanoo.
Amiqira irirana faqaasa faqa andeeqara irirana faqaasa faqa asasidaqa.
Irirafa siruaa faqa koora faqa uriaaqararafa maridanoo.
Mi irirafa firaa feefauru qusee maree maria oonina faqa ani kaaqa aidi mari amiqira ainaina faqa uraaqararafa maridanoo.
Irirafa kisaaqasaa marirana ani amidanoo. Mi irirafa ainaina faqaasaikirana faqa uriqarara auqu aniamiannoo.
Amiqira irirafa ani marirana amiqimma amaqaseenoo ani amiqimmasee afiqee fuannoo.
Amiqira irirana faqaasa asasidaqa, amiqira irirafa misa marirana nimiannoo.
Yaaweefa narí amiqira iriranannai innaruna faqa maqa faqa auqinau. Oonumafi iriranannai innaaruna murufi atukaranau.
Yaaweena amiqira irirafa qufanoo nammari quminau, kafa oonamuara qufanoo aaku suqufufanoo maqasaa aqufinau.
Oo qini qimaaku anoona ufa faqa amiqira irirana faqa sandee foora atukaramma qumarasee sia uqaa.
Anee miqinanoo mi ainaina qanda ani marirana amisee ani amiqira doodapaaniara foora marifaranoo.
Anee miqinana aneenna aatata amiqimmasee finnaranoo sia aiku rupauraki saamurinnaranoo.
Anee faiqeenana sia rufieennaranoo amiqimmasee afu rirainana faiqeennaranoo.
Manda oosana maree mariasasaa tautummasee kambiqara ummaara firaafa firaa aaku oonnamuara foora kambiqoondee iranara sia rufieennaranoo.
Yaaweefa ani ummaarasaa itita amaqaannoo. Mifa anisaa rakisinana sia ufaanaki arinnaranoo.
Oo qini qimaaku faiqí moo fannoo moo ainainara dadaaqiannee qinana sia qaoo qia. Mi ainaina marinana kaqi dadaaqia.
Sia aneenna aqoonnanara finana duna ani maraannee qia. Aniki marinana aaqee kai amia.
Aneenna aqoonnanara sia oonumafi manda irirana iria mifa ani aaqa marifa narí afaaqa aniki quqee marifa marinara sia manda irirana minara iria.
Ani sia mandaikamma amaqainnana sia fifau aanoo qima amaqaa.
Anee sia faiqí narimarasa naanna raa. Misa oosana qafammasee sia qinee faqa miqiunoo qia.
Manda oosana maree mariasara Yaaweefa fidiaqaa midanoo. Andeeqara oosna faqaasa Yaweena afaaqasaa aqondi mariafanoo misara aididanoo.
Yaaweefa narí manda niqurara ufa manda oosana maree maria fasiqausa maaqasa uqaidanoo. Andeeqara oosana maree maria fasiqausa maaqasaa narí amiqi amiqirana uqaidanoo.
Faiqí nári nifaaqa nári nuqu uqeeqee fasiqausa Yaaweefa misara akooqaidanoo. Fisoofisoo idaqa nári mara maree qumi mariasara Yaaweefa aididanoo.
Irirana faqaasa nuqu uqeerarana mareefaranoo. Furufari mariasa nári mi furufarirafa nári nisaurirana nimiannoo.
Oo qini faiqi namu inneeqa nikausa qini naamuaqira ufasaa irirana rusisee oonumafi irira oosana mareefaranoo.
Qinee qimannimianna ufafa amiqira ufa maridanoo. Minara aiqama aiqamara iria.
Qinee faqa ooqai kaqikaa faiqi mariaafanausa maridaqa. Qinee qeeqa qinaukoo moodaa faiqi mariaafanausa maridaqa.
Qini qikoofa maaqi qimasee qini qimaqiminau. Qinee qimamianna ufana sia qaunua aiqama kari iria. Qinee auqaannee qianna ainaina auqeenana sia kuqinnaranoo.
Anee amiqira iriranara faqa oonumafi iriranara faqa randasee maraa. Qinee qimamianna ufana sia irisee qaunua.
Sia amiqira irirana minnisaa minara rinanoo ani faqa maridanoo mifa anisaa rakisiannoo. Anee minara rinanoo mifa anisaa itita amaqaannoo.
Irirafa kuqaa firaa ainaina maridanoo mina kai randasee maraa. Anee nana oosana oosana ainainee maraseenana oonumafi irirana sia aunua mina faqa maraa.
Anee amiqira iriranara aidinana rakisi qumarainanoo mifa ani firaa auqu amiannoo. Anee irirana oonumafi rakisi qumarainanoo ani auquara naaquqarana faqa qeerairirana faqa nimiannoo.
Anee irirana marasainanoo ani aqinaaqa amiqira faini afaira foora mariannoo. Mifa uriqararausa qafeera foora ani akiiqa afisu amaqanoo mariannoo.
Oo qini qimaaku anee oori kandamasee qini ufa irisainanoo ani marirafa kisaaqasaa mariannoo.
Qinee amiqira iriramau fimaria aanna aamuaqi marunausa maridaqa.
Anee mimau finanoo sia moo ainaina fannoo ani aana ititaannoo. Anee mimau finana sia aiku rupaurinnaranoo.
Anee aamuaqira ufa rakisi qumaraa. Sia uqaa. Aneenna ufa minasaa atukarama qaina mariani ani marirafa maridanoo.
Aaqee mariasa fimaria aatata sia fua. Sia manda oosana maree mariasa naanna raa.
Anee misa aatata faqa sia fua. Minniseenana aneenna aatata kai fua.
Mandoosana maree mariasa akaqausa mareeqee sia nári mandoosanaki uqaseeqa sia maqasaa faiqeefaranoo. Misa akaqausa rarisameeqee minaki uqaseeqa maqasaa faiqeefaranoo.
Misa manda oosana faqa faiqí kuqa narirafa faqa misa narana nammariara foora maridanoo.
Andeeqarausa nimari aanafa kaaqa qara aana uqanna maridanoo.
Manda oosana maree mariasa aana asukuna miqirafa maridanoo. Misa nanasee fee niku amaki saamrida fee, sia qafaidaqa.
Oo qini qimaaku amiqimmasee qinee qunna ufana iria. Qini ufa amiqimmasee iria.
Sia amiqira irirana minnisaina fuani. Aneenna amuqusaki quqasaina mariani.
Amiqira irirafa faqa oonumafi irirana faqa sia kuqirana faqa nifaaqa amiqi amiqirana faqa nimidanoo.
Maa firaa ainainnara qimamianaura. Aneenna amuqusasaa rakisia. Aiqama marirana oosana amuqusaki qari ururaidanoo minara aneenna amuqusa amiqimmaseenana rakisia.
Sia unna ufa qia. Unna ufa faqa eendaandira oosanrafa faqa sia qia.
Aneenna firaree qinnaqoo amiqimmasee aiuqummasee kuqaa qimaseenana fua. Sia aneenna akiiqa asauriranaki quqaa.
Aneenna nimarianna aannana andeeqasainanoo amiqinoo marinana nua.
Anee aneenna aatata fidana sia dinni quandee dinni quandee ia. Andeeqasee manda oosanara qeerairammasee ani aiku fannoo ani aatata kai fuani.
Oo qini qimaaku qini aakapara ufa amiqimmandee aaqoo uqasee iria. Qinee amiqira irirana faqa aakapara ufa faqa ani qimamidaqa.
Anee andeeqara oosana mau finanoo ani aiqama ufaqirafa irirana faqaasa ufara foora mariannoo.
Moo fasiqa anaaqa ufa fannoo kaaqa adiafaa iannoo. Ookasaasa anoona adiafaa imarina faqa uriaaqaranoo mariannoo. Mina ookinaa ufa fannoo fadameena miqirafa maridanoo.
Mifa taikainanoo mifa ani quqasee finanoo qisaaqa suka miqirafa faqa aidafirafa faqa mariannoo. Aseema miqirafa afai raiqarafa ani afaaqa ateekaanoo.
Mi anaaseefa ani afiqeenoo kuqira maqa maaqaki fidanoo. Mina nira aana kuqirafa maridanoo.
Mifa sia kaqi marira aatatau fidanoo fau. Mifa fimari aanafa eendaandirafa maridanoo sia minara irimarifa kaqi mi aatata fimarifa maridanoo.
Qini faiqi namu qini ufa iria sia qinee qimannimianna ufana qaunuaqa.
Anee mi anaaseefa mariqooqari nianai maria. Sia mina kooqi aaqa faqa fua.
Anee mina kooqi aaqa finana aneenna andeeqaree auqu aiqamausa nifusaa maqasaa uqaminanoo aqufuannoo. Anee nimudaoo qirana siaisa nisaukuki oonu rainaqa kuqa arifaranoo.
Anaamuru anireeqa ani ainaina kaqi mareefaranoo. Ani kadaapi rirafa moosaindika miannoo.
Anee aneenna faiqara qaarisaa annadannadidana kuqina marinaqa ani amaqi faqa aununu faqa fifau ainainauqa namaseefaranoo.
Miqidana annadannadidana maaqi qinnaranoo. Oo qinee nanaree aaquqira ufasa fidiaqaa iqiafanee. Qini qimuqusa fannoo aamuaqira ufara fidiaqaa imariafanausa maridaqa.
Qinee sia ufa qima qimusa ufa iriafanausa maridaqa. Qinee aaqafana andeeqa qimaqoosa ufa sia iriafanausa maridaqa.
Qinee maqee aiqamausa nifusaa tautummasee qisauriranaki firaridaqa.
Anneenna nammari kai naa. Aneenna taquki kai sakasee naa.
Moomoo aanaaseesaa faiqi maqasainausa sia ani andeeqa amaqeefaranoo.
Anee moo aanaaseesa maqasainna faiqifa mi anaaseena oosanaki mariannoo. Sia ani faqa mariannoo.
Aneenna anaaqa kumaaraasaa maroonnana mina faqa amiqidana asasammasee maria.
Mina afaaqa amiqirafa eeqaku miqirafa ummooqukirafa maridanoo. Mina faqa maqee maqee maria. Anee maqee maqee mina naammara kai aidiani. Mina aidirafa maqee maqee ani qumaraani.
Oo qini qimaaku nanaree anee moo aanaaseera ridanee. Anee nanaree moo fasiqa anaaqa naammara ridanee.
Anee aiqama ainaina auqaannana Yaaweefa qafaidanoo. Anee yaifee fuananoo Yaaaweefa anisaa rakisidanoo.
Manda oosana maree mariasa nári mandainaina fannoo ufaanara foora nári ninuka qumaraidanoo.
Mi fasiqausa sia nariqa nirana mariranasaa rakisira irirafa marinara kuqidaqa.
Oo qini qimaaku akaqausa dinnaa munnimma maraifana misa faqa qima afeekaika maseenana qinee mina akiiqra ianauree qimasee sia miqinana aneenna qima afeekaikianna ufanaki ufaana kiara foora aruananoo.
<range>
Oo qini qimaaku anee maaqi qimasee mi fasiqana ufaanakinaana aneenna faaqa mara kaqinni quaa. Doo anee aneenna afaaqa aneenna aqoonnana asaukuki quqaananoo kai kaqi moodaaqoo oonureenana mi ufana taikasaa.
Anee sia faiqaa sia kisaaqasaa adooaida maria.
Anee kaasau kuara miqirafa maria ufaanaki arufinoo munari minarindee dauni ratoofusee mina faqa ufa qima taikaa. Ufini ufaanaki aiku arindee ia, dauni aruratoofua.
Oo kudi fasiqauqa tarika mariqoo oonuree mina oosana qafaaqa. Innee mina oosana qafamaseeqa oonumafi iriseeqa irirana faqaasaikifaranoo.
Sia tarika rakisirafa moo maridanoo sia misa fukifaaki qimarifa moo maridanoo, sia moo fannoo misa aranaiqi qimannimifaqa ainainai fidaqa.
Suani aukuana misa nári kai nári narana moomoo afeedidaqa. Aaku aukuana narana taikainaqa nararee qimasee miqidaqa.
Oo kudi fasiqa kisaaqasaa fee innee miqoo faiqaqee ifaree. Yairee fee innee findi fifaree.
Innee maaqi qimariafanoo maasa qusasaa faiqaanauree qimariafanoo. Maasa qeeqa qisauku raqandaammasee kaqikaaqoo idooaanauree qimariafanoo.
Innee faiqaafanoo inni faiqarafa ummuara fasiqara foora inni aiqama ainaina ummuara maraanoo.
Mana oosana maree mariasa unnufa qiqa nidaqa.
Nikaru qiraree qimasee nifu quandaqaandi mariasa misa niku munuree miniree imariasa maridaqa.
Misa nimuqusaki nikaruqirafa qumbiqarausa maridaqa. Maqee maqee mandainainara kai ufa qimariasa maridaqa. Misa aiqamatinai nidaqa ummaara kambiqaanifeera kai andaana riqa nidaqa.
Miqi marianara firaa ummaara sia aaquqima nimaqarai tautummasee misa naruannoo.
Yaaweefa qisauku dinni taikasee dinni oonu qaara marasee ainaina auqaanara kaaqa fidiaaidanoo.
Maa ainainnara fidiaqaa idanoo. Oori uqeeraranara faqa unna qimari afaurunara faqa fifau fidika ruiqee marinara faqa manda oosanara nári iriranaki tipundaari mariana faqa mandainainaki dauni niku ree mariana faqa kootaki unnufa qimariana faqa nári nikaaqaafasaa ummaara nimimaria oosannara faqa Yaaweefa fidiaqaa idanoo.
<range>
<range>
Oo qini qimaaku ani akausa qimamunnandee inana aneenna anoona ufa sia qaunua.
Aiqama kari aneenna anaukoo ufa sia quqaa, aneenna amuqusaki quqasee atukaraa.
Misa qimaminna ufafa ani indaarunnikamma amaqaanoo. Eendaki anisaa itita amaqaseenoo faasaana niranaki ani aakapaannoo.
Ani anaukoo aakapara ufa qoomara foora kaaqaqaidanoo. Misa andeeqara ufa fannoo ani maa maqanasaa marirana andeeqa amaqaidanoo.
Mi ufafa dapi maraqa nua anaasee finnai firanasaa itita amaqaannoo. Akaqa fasiqauqa ninaaqmaaka fadameena akira ufasaa itito amaqaannoo.
Sia anee misa amiqira nifaaqara rua. Afunnai ani mareeqeenoo ufaanaki aruaneera quqainana sia minara iria.
Dapi maraqa nua aanaaseefinnai finana kaqikaa feefauru narana maree mariana amana kai aqinnaranoo. Faiqí moo anaaqa faqa finana firaa feefauru faqa aneenna aiqama ainaina faqa aqinnaranoo.
Amanee anee ida auri marina qumaree amuqusasaa uqasainanoo qamunna sia qaannoo fee. Ani qamunna faqa afaaqa faqa aiqama ida qaannoo.
Amanee anee ida auruki aiku reennaree sia amana reennaranoo. Aiku turuquannoo.
Doo miqi kai inoo faiqí moo fannoo narí aqoonnana anaaqa faqa sia faiqaannoo. Miqinafa aupurarana maraannoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo aararainanoo ummuara masainanoo sia minara firaaqoo ufa qifaranoo.
Akaqausa mifasiqana paqurimmasaifanoo moodaa ainaina ummuarinnana akiiqara dinni taikasee dinni ani qaara marasee 7 ainaina amiannoo. Mifa narí uaqeei ainaina aiqama amiannoo.
Narana ummuari fasiqanara miqimminoo marifanoo anaasee ummuari marinara maaqimminoo maridanoo. Moo fasia anaaqa faqa manda oosana auqee marifa narí kai narí kurididanoo.
Mi fasiqafa arirana faqa aqirana faqa maraidanoo. Mi fasiqafa naaruara asauriranaki mariannoo.
Mi anaaseena afaaqi paqurinanoo rairai qirafa idara foora atakuquannoo. Minara ufa qifanoo sia kaqi irinoo minnisaannoo, arana qarafa kisaaqasaa mariannoo. Sia kai kaqi taikaannoo.
Sia mifa feefauruara iriannoo munnimma ainaina oosana oosana aminanoo siamma iriannoo sia doo fee qiannoo.
Oo qini qimaaku qinee qimamianna ufana iria. Qinee auqaannee qianna ainainnara sia qaunua.
Anee qinee qunnandee inana amiqimmasee marinaranoo. Qini aamuaqiira ufa aneenna afu rakisinnandee amiqimmasee rakisia.
Qini aakapara ufa aiqama kari uaqeeina ani faqa mariani. Aneenna amuqusasaa akara rumasaina mariani.
Oo qini qimaaku anee amiqira iriranara qini qisookifee qia. Oonumafi iriranara qifaaqa saa qiqoondi fee qia.
Anee miqinanoo mi irirafa moona anaaqa faqa firanasaa aitita amaqaanoo. Mi anaaseesa fadameena akira ufasaa itita amaqaannoo.
Qinee qeeqa maaqaki ooqufaqee qeeqa kooqirunna qafaunanoo dapi kumaarauqa marianakiqari moo furufarira kumaara fannoo ummuarimari anaaseena maaqa marindanai ubeekaidanoo mina kooqindanai fidanoo doo mina naambeeqandanai finoo suani keeqaifanoo sisisasa qeenoo fee eendaki fee asukunai fee doo mifinnai fidanoo.
<range>
<range>
<range>
Mi anaaseefa doo oonu afiqararee qimasee anidanoo. Aatata nua aanaaseesa qamunna afisusee anidanoo.
Mi anaaseefa kambaaramasee ufa qimarifa asaurirana siaifa maridanoo. Mifa aiqama kari fifau aatata oonuree aniree inoo nifa maridanoo.
Anee aanai finana miqoo qafeennaranoo. Anee maqusa qambaanai finana mina miqoo qafeennaranoo. Mifa aiqama aana kindooraki oonureenoo afu munu maqee mini maqee iannoo.
Mi kummaaraana paqurimandee asauku qaqusee qumaseenoo amooqa namaseenoo afuki kai qafanoo maridanoo qiannoo.
Doo qinee maqee amaana maqaki keeqafiqa tatufirana suqeeqee qiannoo. Doo qinee tatufirana suqaidaqa aandau ati maree mini quqasee anidaqee qiannoo.
Qinee qeeqa maaqakiqari raudamaki aniara randamaree doo ani paquriqa.
Doo qinee qeeqa qaari amiqirana ufiqiseeqa. Isipa maqanna qamunna amiqirananoo minasaa ufiqiseeqa.
Qinee minasaa fadameena afundi marina adieesee makaqa anoona faqa saadapu anoona faqa adieeseeqa doo anee aniraina maaqooqari oosana arasee nariara nariara nidira nammari neenee iaqasaa.
<range>
Qini qifaaqi sia maridanoo nianai fifinoo mifa munnimma moomoo maree finoo mifa qaara amaana minni maraannoo sia kai kaqi aniannoo.
<range>
Mi aanaaseefa narí naammannai mina qumaraseenoo ummooqifira ufannai mina rarisaidanoo.
Mi anaaseena ufa fannoo mi kumaaraana afu dapikammasaifanoo aandau miqirafa sia irirai kuqiranaki kaqi fidanoo.
Kaasau kuara ufaanaki arinoo marifanoo faiqí oonu qafeenoo doo amuqusa arifanoo kuqidanoo. Mifa ufiniara foora sia irirai ufini ufanaki keeqafinoo kuquannoo. Mifa narí marirafa manda marinara sia iridanoo.
Oo qini faiqi namu innee amiqimmasee qinee qianna ufana iriaqa.
Inni nimuqusa fannoo sia mi anaaseena faqa firara findifuani. Sia kambaaramasee mi anaaseefa marinnai fuaqa.
Mifa moomoo fasiqa mandaikamma nimaqaseenoo kuqirana niminoo. Sia amana nisaana rirana amana kuqa narimarifa maridanoo.
Anee mi aanaaseena maaqai finana anee kuqira aatata fimariananoo. Mi aanafa kuqirannai fimaria aanafa qusa aana maridanoo.
Iriaqa, amiqira irirafa irirana faqaa aanaaseera foora nammeera qidanoo. Oonumafi irirafa dadaaqinoo firaaqoo naaraidanoo.
Amiqira irirafa aaqana namusaa fee aanasaa fee aana kindooraki fee kikiqinoo maridanoo nammeera qidanoo.
Maaqusa kooqiki fee maqusa atinni fee kikiqinoo maridanoo maaqi qimasee nammeera qidanoo.
Inni aiqamausa qimannimidaqa, inni aiqama maa maqa maaqana saaqaraasa naaraidaqa.
Innee irirana siaisa irirana maraaqa. Furufarirausa inneeqa furufarirana kiqari nifu maqasaa qafamasee iriaqa.
Qini amiqira ufa iriaqa, aiqama qinee qimannimi marunna ufafa kuqaa kai maridanoo.
Qinee qimarunna ufafa kuqaa anoona maridanoo. Qinee unna ufara fidiaqaa midaqa.
Qini aiqama ufa kuqaa kai maridanoo. Sia unna qirafa faqa eendaandirafa faqa minaki maridanoo.
Irirana faqaafa qini ufara aiqama iriannoo kaaqa qara ufa fee qiannoo. Irirana faqaasa qini ufara kuqaa anoonee qifaranoo.
Innee siruaa minnisee qini naakaparanara amiqira ainainee qimasee maraaqa. Innee koora munnimmara rimariana minnisaaqa, irirafa mifa naaru naaru marirafa maridanoo mina maraaqa.
Qinee amiqira irirausa maridaqa qinee nifaaqa auqi maria amiqira ainainausa faqa uriaqararausa maridaqa. Sia moo ainaina innee rimariafa qini qimana maridanoo.
Qinee irirausa ufa raina nimaqarana akausa maridaqa. Qinee irirausa akooqoo irirana auqi marunausa maridaqa.
Yaaweenara qeerairida mina ufa qaindusiraree qimasee manda oosanara fidiaqaa ia. Qinee ramoo ramaa iranara faqa nári nuqu uqeerara oosanara faqa manda oosanara faqa unnufa qiranara faqa fidiaqaamidaqa.
Qinee ainaina auqararee qimasee qeeqa iriranaki qima irisee auqaanaura. Qinee oonu mafi irirana faqaasa maridaqa qinee afeeka maridaqa.
Qinee uriqararausa faqa rakisirausa faqa dadaaqunaqa amiqira irirana qimasee maqa maaqaki rakisi nimaqaidaqa.
Aiqama maa maqanasaa qaraa rakisirausa qini dadaaqirananoo rakisi nimaqaidaqa. Uriqararausa miqi kai idaqa.
Qiniara rimariasara qinee faqa misara ridaqa. Nimudaanai qimasee qiniara randee mariasa misa qini paqurifaranoo.
Qinee moomoo munnimma faqa uriqarara auqu faqa uaqeeidaqa nimianaura. Aiqama ainaina auqainafa anoona kambiqarana faqa reemindeemirirana faqa nimianaura.
Qini ainaina maraafa koora uraaqararafa maridanoo. Mina amiqirafa kaaqa amiqira siruaa faqa uriaqararafa maridanoo.
Qinee andeeqara aatata kai fidaqa. Qinee ufa amana amana kai raina nimaqara aatata fidaqa.
Qiniara rimariasa moomoo qumiasana nimidaqa misa maaqaki qumiasana qumbiqannisaidaqa.
Ooqai Yaaweefa aiqama ainaina auquanee qimaseenoo qini irirana naaree auqinau.
Ooqai uqanna aiqama ainaina sia auquqoo qini irirausa naaree auqinau. Maa maqa maaqana sia auquaqee idanoo qini naaree auqinau.
Ooqai ooruku nammari sia maruqoo qinee naaree kambiqaafanausa maridaqa. Maqakiqari nammariuqa sia ururee marufaqa qinee naaree kambiqaqiafana.
Aaqanauqa faqa amuaqu namuqa faqa sia maruqoo qinee naaree kambiqaafanausa maridaqa.
Yaaweefa maqa maaqa faqa kookoomma faqa sia auqu aukuana qinee irirausa naaree mariafanausa maridaqa.
Qinee faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa innaaruna auqu quqanau. Qinee faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa ooruku nammari fiqufiqumma auqu quqanau.
Qinee faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa oonnamu auqu quqanau. Qinee faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa ooruku nammari maqakiqari ururee maruna auqu quqanau.
Qinee irirausa Yaaweena faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa ooruku nammari mandiranara maa oosirana amana kai mandiannee qufanoo miqinninau. Qinee faqa mariafananoo Yaaweefa maa maqana maaqa atunara foora rakiasoofanoo maridanoo.
Yaaweefa mi ainainausa auqi marufaqa qinee amiqira irirausa mina aaqa faiqi aanaaqiara foora mariaafanausa maridaqa. Qinee mina afusaa maridaqa aiqama kari asasirana amimariqiafana.
Aiqama maqa maaqai asasiqa niniaafanausa maridaqa. Qinee faiqí faiqi faqa asasiqa niniaafanausa maridaqa.
Doo maqee kumaaraa fasiqa anaasee qini ufa iriaqa. Qinee qiannandee iqa innee asasifaranoo.
Innee qini naakapara ufa iriaqa, sia minnisaaqa. Iriseeqa irirana faqaasa mariaqa.
Qini ufa irimariasa asasifaranoo. Qini kooqiki aiqama kari mariasa faqa eeqá maaqai fimarunna aanna afainni maridaqa qiniara rakisi mariasa asasifaranoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo qini irirausa paqurinafa kaqi marirana faqa paquriannoo.
Faiqí qini irirausara sia randee mariasa nariqa kai nariqa mandaikamma nimaqaidaqa. Qini irirausara fidiaqaa imariasa kuqiranara nididanoo.
Irirafa narí maaqa atuna qisauku dinni taikasee dinni ani qaara marasee 7 pausasaa usakaseenoo.
Irirafa narí aandau arusee suqeenoo. Narana faqa uainna nammari faqa deedaqamma narana neemaria qaindanasaa oomaqa saka quqanau.
Mifa narí ainainira maanaaqauqa niqiqoofaqa maqusasaa aaqanaikiraqoo ooruree nammeera qiaqeera niqiqoofaqa fiqau.
Innee ooruree maaqi qimasee nammeera qiaqa. Innee irirana siaisa mai aniree qoomaqa naaqee qiaqa. Furufarirausara maaqi qimasee nammeera qiaqa.
Mai aniree qini narana nammari naaqee qiaqa.
Inneeqa furufarirana minnisee kisaaqusaa mari faranoo. Amiqira iriranamau fuaqa.
Anee náriara maasa amiqirausee qimaria fasiqausa qaoo qinaqa misa ani namuqaaka mifaranoo. Nariara andeeqarausee qimariasa aaqaranara qaoo qinaqa misa ani arifaranoo.
Anee ufa rukiee maria fasiqausara qaoo qinaqa misa aniara fidiaqaa mifaranoo. Anee irirana faqaa fasiqa andeeqa amaqainanoo ani ufara eedoo qimasee ani ameemaanai keeqaannoo.
Nana ainainaree irirana faqaana qimaminanoo mifa misa kaaqa firaaqoo irirana faqaasaikamma nimaqaannoo. Andeeqara fasiqauqa qimanniminaqa misa moo faqa moo faqa irirana mareefaranoo.
Yaaweenara rufieenana irirana faqaafa mariannaranoo. Anutuna naaquqara ainainara irinanoo mifa ufa irirana oosana amiannoo.
Amiqira irirafa faiqí marirana maa maqanasaa kisaaqa kamu rarisama nimaqaidanoo.
Anee irirana faqaafa marinanoo mi irirafa ani moomoo amiqirana amiannoo. Anee mi irirana minnisainanoo aupurarafa aniki mariannoo.
Furufarirafa asaurirana siai anaaseefara foora maridanoo. Firaaqoo faaqa quqasee ufa qimari anaaseefara foora maridanoo.
Miqira anaasee fannoo narí maaqa kooqi afaisaa ooqumarifinoo aiqama maqusa mirinni urinnaaqaramafa maridanoo.
Akaqausa nári qimaqaannai nári ainainai aiqaree fimariasa misa naarama narí maaqaki quqaidanoo.
Mi aanaaseefa maaqi qimasee furufarirausa qimannimidanoo. Irirana siaisa doo mai aniaqee qidanoo. Furufarirausara maaqi qidanoo.
Ummuarira nammari adiafaa irafa maridanoo. Ummuarira feemu narafa adiafaa midanoo.
Mi anaaseefinnai fimariasa kuqimarianara furufarira fasiqa fannoo sia iridanoo. Mi anaaseena maaqaki keeqoosa maqee kuqira maqa maaqaki maridaqa.
Maana Sooroomoonnana aaquqira ufa maridanoo. Irirana faqaasa nári rukausa mara asasirana nimidaqa. Furufarirausa nári ninausa nisaurirana nimidaqa.
Unna qira aatata marainna ainainafa sia ani dadaaqiannoo. Anoona qira aatata marainna ainainafa ani marirana dadaaqiannoo.
Anutufa sia andeeqara fasiqauqa naarararana nimiannoo. Manda oosana maree mariasa nári nidimari ainainna mararanasaa Anutufa itita nisaidanoo.
Kudoosaaparafa kudikirana amiannoo. Kadaapi rirafa ani ainaina faqaa faikamma aisaidanoo.
Irirana faqaafa narana qaanaakifaqa afeedidaqa. Moo fannoo narana unnakara aukuana faiaqee idanoo sia narana deedaqafi asauriranaki mariannoo.
Andeeqara fasiqa anaasee amiqi amiqirana mareefaranoo. Manda oosana maree marina ufa fannoo mina manda irirana kukeeqasaifanoo akaqausa mandaikamma nisaidanoo.
Amiqira fasiqa kuqufinaqa amiqira ainainara foora iriranaki kaqi minara oonu mafi irifaranoo. Manda oosana maree mari fasiqafa kuqufinaqa misa mi fasiqanara kai kaqi qaunuseefaranoo.
Irirana faqaasa amiqira naamuaqira ufa iriseeqa nári nimuqusaki mara quqaidaqa. Fifau faafau iqa nuasa kuridifanoo.
Kuqaa qira oosana fannoo faiqí mareeqeenoo andeeqaranaki quqaannoo. Unna qira oosana fannoo faiqí mareeqeenoo maaniki aquannoo.
Noorinnai nifunnai imariasa ummaara kambiqaanifeera miqidaqa. Aiqama nifufsaa paasoosammandee manda oosanara qaoo qinafa mifa asooarana nimidanoo miqidanoo.
Amiqira fasiqa ufa fannoo nammariara foora, maqakiqari urureenoo kaqi marirana nimidanoo. Mandoosana maree mari fasiqana ufa fannoo narí irirana kukeeqa saifanoo narí aqoonausa mandaikamma nimaqaidanoo.
Faiqí aanaaseera fidiaqaa ira oosana fannoo ummaara kambiqaidanoo. Faiqí aanaaseera nidira oosana fannoo aiqama misa aaqarana minninnisaidanoo.
Irirana faqaa fasiqa afaurusaa amiqira ufa kai ururaidanoo. Furufarira fasiqa arirafa kai maridanoo.
Irirana faqaasa irirana oosana oosana moodaasaqa maridanoo. Furufarira fasiqa ufa qinanoo ummaara sia nianai mariannoo aaqa uqanna mariannoo.
Ainaina faqaana narí ainaina fannoo itita amaqaidanoo. Kudi fasiqa fannoo ainaina sia marinara kuridiannoo.
Amiqira oosana auqaana akiiqara kaqi marirafa maridanoo. Numoo fannoo nifiqeenoo firaa numooki kai fidanoo.
Naakapara ufa iri mariasa sia kuqifaranoo. Naakaparanara nikooqee mariasa manda aatata fifaranoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo faiqí aanaaseera ookiqari amiqi amiqidanoo umee fidiaqaa imarifa unnaqi marifa maridanoo. Munuqi miniqinoo nifa furufari marifa maridanoo.
Ufa moomoo qinana moomoo aaqarana mareennaranoo. Anee irirana faqaafa maridana qireeda marinnaranoo.
Amkiqira fasiqa ufa fannoo amiqira siruaara foora maridanoo. Mandoosana maree mari fasiqana irirafa maannukuara foora maridanoo.
Amiqira fasiqa ufa fannoo moomoosa dadaaqidanoo. Furufari marifa narí furufariranannai narí kai aridanoo.
Anutuna amiqi amiqiranannai kai ainaina faqaafaikinnaranoo. Ani kadaapirirafa sia amana minaki ookaa iannoo Anutufa kai amiannoo.
Furufarirafa manda oosana auqarara kai asasidanoo. Amiqira irirana faqaafa amiqira oosana auqee marinara kai asasidanoo.
Andeeqarausa nári nidimari ainainna mareefaranoo. Mandoosana maree mariasa kaaqa rufiee maria ainainna mareefaranoo.
Deedeefaa ufai firaafa uqinanoo mandoosana maree mariasa fuaqamma aqusaannoo. Andeeqarausa sia fuaqa aquannoo. Misaki kaqi marifaranoo.
Anee kudoosaapara fasiqa sia aneenna ainainiani feera afiqaa. Afiqasainanoo kudoosapee marinana afai sandurinafaara. Ida muna aninna afuki keeqeenoora foora iandoora sia afiqaa.
Yaaweena ufa qaindusinana sia dauni kuqinnaranoo kisaaqasaa marinnaranoo. Manda oosana maree mariasa kuqirafa kisaaqasaa marifaqa kasaaqai kuqidaqa.
Andeeqara fasiqa anaasee nidimari ainainafa kuqaa kambiqainaqa asasifaranoo. Manda oosana maree mariasa sia moo ainaina mareefaranoo.
