Ooqai tamummaqara fasiqa maaqi qimasee akara riqau. Anutufa aiqamausa naamuaqira ufa qimannimiannoo. Qinee mi ufana iridaqa maaqi qimasee inni qimannimidaqa. Aiqamausa qini qikoona ufa iriseeqa mina aamua qira ufa irimariasa qinee ianannai anidaqa.
Sia moo fannoo qini qikoona qafeenoo. Anutufinaindari qumufa kai mifa kai qini qikoona qafeenoo.
Qinee anoona ufa uqanna qimannimidaqa faiqí moo fannoo irirana qinisaa rusimarinafa naaru marirana doo mareenoo.
Qinee kaqi marira feemuara foora marunausa maridaqa.
Ooqai inni nikeeku nikaaku Mooseena faqa kaasau maqa maaqakina nimaru aukuanna innaarunaindaraa feemu minauqa manna fee qimariqau. Mi feemufa ufaasu marifandinna feemuna namasaida kisaaqasaa moomoo aukuana mariufaqa kaqi kuqimariqau.
Maa qinee kaqi marira feemuara foora maridee qimarunausa faiqí namasee sia kuqifandinna feemusa maridaqa.
Qinee kaqi marira feemu innaarunaindari qumu marunausa maridaqa. Faiqí anaasee moo fannoo qinee amianna feemuna namasainafa naaru naaru mariannoo. Qinee nimianna feemufa qini qimaqi maridanoo. Maa maqa maaqana afaaqasasa mariasa kaqi mariaqeera nimidaqa.
Yisufa miqi qimasoofaqa Yuda maqannaasa narí afumau narí afumau aanoo qidaqa qiqau. Naqimasee maa fasiqafa narí amaqi maasa qiminaqa naanauree qidaqinoo fee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa qimannimidaqa. Innee qini faiqí nimaaku qimaqi fidika sia naifanoo sia kaqi marirafa inniki mariannoo.
Moo fasiqa anaasee fannoo qini qimaqi faqa qini fidika faqa namasainafa naaru marirana doo mareenoo, marainara taikara faasaana mina uqeeraanaura.
Qini qimaqi narana uqanna maridanoo qini fidika nammari uqanna maridanoo.
Faiqí anaasee moo fannoo qini qimaqi fidika neemarifa qiniki maridanoo qinee minaki faqa maridaqa.
Qini qikoofa Anutufa kaqi marira oosana faqaafa qini diqiqoofaqa maaqoo maridaqa minasaaqaraa marirana maraidaqa. Miqi kai inoo qini namasainafa qinisaaqaraa marirana maraannoo.
Doo qinee innaarunaindaraa naranara foora maridaqa. Sia inni nisaifaqausa neemaru naranausara foora maridaqa. Misa mina namasee mariiqa aiqama faiqí faiqi oosanamau fiqa kuqimariqau. Maa naranna namaseeqa naaru naaru kaqi marifaranoo.
Yisufa mi ufana Kapeeranaumma maqusai ufa suqira maqaki qimanniminau.
Yisuna faiqi namu akaqausa mi ufana iriseeqa qiqau. Oo yafee maa ufana amana iriannoo fee. Irisee sia auqaaqaa ira ufa maridanoo.
Misa miqi qimasee noori runusee randoofanoo Yisufa narí kai iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Innee qini amiqira afeeka ufara rufiasee qini minnisararee qidee.
Qinee kafaa uqeeree qumuafannannai ooru fuanaqa innee mina qafamasee naqi fee ifaree. Mikari qini ufara kuqaa anoonee qimasee firaaqoo rufieefaranoo.
Amaqiara qunnana amaqi fifau ainaina maridanoo sia mina naaqee qiqa maraquna fannoo kai anoona maridanoo mifa kaqi marirana nimidanoo. Qinee qeeqa dookinaa ufa qimannimimarunafa mifa maraquna maridanoo kaqi marirana anoona maridanoo.
Doo qinee akooqoo kooroomasee qimannimunaqa innee akaqausa siamma irimariafanoo. Yisufa narí faiqi namu oosana faasai irinau. Misaki akaqausa mina ufa sia irusa faasai Yisufa nindafanau. Misaki moodaa fannoo ueeqaaninnana faasai qafanau.
Yisufa minara maa ufana atiki kafaa qimanniminau. Qinee minara faasai qunnana sia amana moo fannoo narí kai qinee ianannai aniannoo. Qini qikoofa dadaaqinanoo kai qinee ianannai aniannoo.
Miqi qimasoofaqa Yisuna faiqi namu moomoo Yisuna minnisee sia kafaa mina faqa firara qiqau.
Yisufa miquna nindafamasee quandafi narí faiqi namu (12) qisaukuqara taikasee qikunnoo ooqu qaara marasee faiqi namu maaqi qimasee qimanniminoo qinau. Innee faqa misa naanna reefaree qini minniqiseeqa fifaree.
Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa mina iriseenoo Yisuna qimaminoo qinau. Oo karaambaiqa ani minnisee yanasaa fee atooqaanauree. Naaru marirana nimira ufa anee kai marananuananoo.
Doo maqee maasa aniara kuqaa anoonee qidaqa aniara Anutufinaindari naaquqarafa mariifoo qidaqa.
Yisufa iriseenoo kafaa qimanniminoo qinau qinee qeeqa kai qisaukuqara taikasee qikuqara marasee fasiqa naarauna qini faqa nimariafanoo. Moo fannoo inniki afaanna maridanoo.
Yisufa afaannee quna Yudasinara narí qumee qimirinau. Yudasifa Keerioota maqusanaafa moo fasiqa Simoona amaaku marinau. Yudasifa Yisuna (12) qisaukuqara taikasee qikunni ooqu qaara marasee faiqinamu misaki marufa marinau. Kasooqaqee mi fasiqafa Yisuna uqeeqasainaqa aunirira saqarisaa arifandinnanara Yisufa minara oonu mafi iriseenoo afaanna fee qinau.
Miqooqari Yisufa Kariree maqa maaqaki nimarinau. Sia Yudeeaa maqa maaqai finau. Yuda maqannaasa miqoo mina arira ufa qimarunara sia finau. (Ooqai Isaraee maqannaasa Isipa maqusaindari qaara fasiqa niku nisauku taikasee aukuana nifuru faiqaqa uqiqaana maaqaki fimarufanoo Anutufa innaarunai maridanoo narí afeekannai Isaraee maqannaasa maqasaaqaraasa qumee dadaaqidanoo aandau narana nimimarufaqa naqafimariqau. Kaasau maqa maaqai nini iusa oonu randee nári maqasaa Isaraee maqasaa animaridaqa aukuana aukuana Yeerusareenni suqufidaqa uqiqaanarasaida faiqeeunara iriseeqa minara afaarurumanaida nári naambeeqa nári naambeeqa uqiqaana maqa usakasaida dinni qisauku taikasee dinni ani qaara marasaida (7) faasaana minaki faiqaida qoomaqa sakasaida namasaida minara susu imariqau.)
Yuda maqannaasa qoomaqa firaafa uqiqaana maqa qoomaqa adeedi roofaqa Yisuna akaqaafasaa Yisuna qimamiqa qiqau.
Maa Kariree maqa maaqa minniseenana Yudeeaa maqa maaqaki fua. Oonurainaqa miqoo ani ufa irimariasa firaa ainaina auqee mariannana misa faqa uqannifiqaa.
Faiqí moo fannoo narí auqu uqeeraannee qimasee sia moo ainaina auqee mariana kukeeqaidanoo aiqama ainaina kooroomasainaqa aiqamausa mina qafaaqa, anee faqa miqiaqaana. [
Yisuna akaqaafasaa sia Yisunara irimariqau. Fifau maqasaa fasiqa fee qimariqau.]
Yisufa iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Qini anoona aukuana sia adeedi ranoo maridanoo. Innee faiqí faiqi aiqama faasaanara maasa aukuanee qimariasa mariafanoo. Maa maqa maaqanasaaqaraasa sia inniara fidiaqaaidanoo. Qiniara kai fidiaqaaidanoo. Qinee maqee maqee misa manda ainainara kooroomannimaqaunaqa minara kai qiniara fidiaqaamaqimaqee mariafanoo.
<range>
Yisufa narí akaqaafasaa kaqi qimanniminau. Innee kai Yeerusareenni ooru fuaqa. Qinee sia mi qoomaqanara inni naanna ree akooqoo ooru fuanauara qini anoona aukuana sia qusa raidanoo.
Yisufa miqi qimaseenoo miqoo Kariree maqa maaqaki kaqi marinau.
Mina akaqaafasaa Yeerusaree qoomaqai ooru fufanoo Yisufa inaaqianna qumee moo aatata ooru finau.
Yeerusaree maqusa qoomaqaki Yuda maqannaa rakisirausa Yisunara randoosia narí qimami narí qimami qidaqa qiqau. Mifa yai fee marinoo fee.
Qimasoofaqa faiqí anaasee Yisuna aufakiana qumee narí qimami narí qimami qimariqau. Akaqausa Yisunara amiqira fasiqee qimariqau. Akaqausa faiqí anaasee nikaru qimari fee qimariqau.
Sia moo fannoo Yisunara akooqoo qimariqau. Narí Yuda maqannaa uriqararausara rufiasee qumee kai qimariqau.
Qoomaqa taikarara imarufanoo Yisufa Yeerusaree amaana maqaki keeqafinoo faiqí anaasee ufa qimanniminau.
Yuda maqannaa faiqí firaasa mina qafamasee firaaqoo tautiqa qiqau. Maa fasiqafa sia sukuraki keeqeemarifa. Naqi fee mandeenoo firaa irirana iridanoo fee.
Yisufa minara iriseenoo aiqamausa qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee qimannimira ufa sia qeeqaindi maridanoo qini diqiqoofa Anutufa mina ufa qimannimidaqa.
Qini ufa Anutunaindi fee qinee qeeqa fee qidee. Faiqí moo fannoo Anutuna iriranamau firarimarifa qini ufara Anutufa fee qiannoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo narí ufa kai qidanoo narí auqu kai uqeeraidanoo. Faiqí moo fannoo narí aqiqainna fasiqana auqu uqeerararee qimarifa mifa kuqaa ufa qidanoo, sia nikaruqirafa minaki maridanoo.
Mooseefa sandufa akara rumaqoona inni nimufaqa innee mina qumaree mi mau fimarunausee qimasaidaqa fifau qidaqa inniki moo fannoo sia mi mau fimariafanoo. Innee moo mau fidaqa qini kuqa darirara qimariafanoo.
Yisufa miqi qimasoofaqa misa aiqama maaqi qimasee narí qimamiqau. Ani aunduraki afaanna marifana anee miqi qimariananoo. Yafee moo fannoo ani kuqaruannoo fee sia moo fannoo.
Miqi qimasoofanoo Yisufa maaqi qimasee nári qimanniminau. Qinee faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainainna moodaa auqaunaqa innee aiqama tautiafanoo.
Mooseefa faiqi aanaaqiuqa nipata aukimarunara fainanduqu nisaaqee qimarinau, innee minara irisee maasa amaana Saririqasaa miqimariafanoo. Sia Mooseefau mi oosanna aranau. Narí akeeku akaakundi mareenoo miqi qinau.
Innee Mooseena sandufa rukiaanoo qimasee faiqi aanaaqiuqa maasa amaana Saririqasaa fainanduqidaqa nipata aukimariafanoo innee amaana Saririqasaa kaqi faiqi nipata aukidaqa nanaree Saririqasaa aurimari fasiqana idaaqamasaunnanara innee aanoo qida fee.
Innee fifau dapi iriranasaa faiqí ufa nimimarifanoo mina minnisaaqa. Kuqaa anoona iriranannai kai faiqí andeeqaaqa.
Yeerusaree maqusanaasa Yisuna qafamasee mina ufa iriqa maaqi qiqau. Maana misa kuqariraree qidaqa.
Qafaa mifa faiqí qambaana faiqí nifusaa kikiqamambi ufa qimannimimarifaqa sia misa mina qumaraannee qidaqa. Abee maasa uriqararausa faqa minara kuqaa Anutuna asauku mundirafee fee qidee.
Anutuna asauku mundirana oosana maasa siamma irianaura. Kaqi tautumannimaqaannoo. Maasa maa fasiqana oosana iridaqa, Nasareeteendaraafa maridanoo.
Yisufa firaa amaana maqaki faiqí anaasee qimannimidanoo mi ufana iriseenoo maaqi qimasee firaaqoo qimanniminau. Kuqaa fee innee qiniara iridee. Qinee yaindaraasee marunaqee innee kuqaa qiniara irida fee. Sia qinee qeeqa kai animaridaqa qini diqiqaifa mifa kuqaa anoona maridanoo. Innee kuqaa minara sia irimariafanoo.
Qinee minara iridaqa qinee mindari qumuafanausa mifa qini diqiqoofaqa qumumaridaqa.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mi ufana irisee qumarararee qimasoosa minnisaqau. Yisuna kuqira aukuana sia adeedi roofanoo Anutufa qumee misa ititannisoonara minnisaqau.
Faiqí anaasee moomoosa Yisuna kuqaa Anutuna asauku mundira fee qiqau. Misa maaqi qimasee narí qimami narí qimami qidaqa qiqau. Asauku mundirafa anireenoo naqi fee mandeenoo maa fasiqana uraaqarainanoo fee moomoo faiqí dadaaqimari firaa ainainna uqannifiqaannoo fee. Sia amana. Doo maana mifa uqanna maridanoo.
Faiqí anaasee miqi qimasee narí qimami narí qimami qimarufaqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa iriseeqa tautumasee amaana maqasaa rakisimarusunnai oonuree qimannimiqa qiqau. Qimannimisoofaqa misa amaana maqasaa rakisimaru poorisausa qimannimiqau. Innee ooru Yisuna rumbasee maree aniaqa.
Misa oonuroofanoo Yisufa maaqi qimasee faiqí anaasee qimannimimarinau. Qinee qusasaa inni faqa marianaura. Quqaseeqa qusasaa qini diqiqoofinnai fuanaura.
Innee qiniara randee sia paqurifaranoo qinee fuanannai sia innee amana fifaranoo.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mi ufana iriseeqa narí qimami narí qimami qiqau. Mifa yai fee finaqa maasa sia amana fuanauree. Mifa aanaamuru Kirisa maqannaa mariannai fee fuannoo fee. Yuda maqannaasa miqoo mariasa faqa maridaqa Kirisa maqannaasa narí ufa qimannimiraree fidanoo fee qida qinoo fee.
Mifa qinoo innee qiniara randasee sia paqurifaranoo. Qinee fuanannai innee sia fifaranoo. Mina ufoosana sia maasa iridaqa.
Uqiqaana maqa qoomaqa taikara faasaana uriqarara faasaanee qiqau. Mi faasaanna Yisufa findifinoo faiqí anaasee firaa kari qimanniminau. Yafasiqa anaasee fee nammariara aididanoo fee qinee iannaqoo nammari uqanna ani naa Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqa moo ooqai maaqi qimasee akara rinau. Kaqi marirana nimira nammari misa nimuqusa ookiqari ururee fuannoo fee qinau. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qiniara kuqaa anoonee qinafa misa nimuqusa ookiqari mi nammarifa ururee fuannoo.
<range>
Yisufa nammariara quna Anutuna maraqunara nammari kikiqa usinau. Kasooqaqee Yisunara kuqaa Anutuna faiqi fee qifandinausa misa mi maraqunna mareefaranoo. Mi aukuanna Yisufa kaqi maru aukuanna sia maraquna nimirafa marinau. Yisufa kuqiranakiqari findifinanoo afaaqa areenainanoo miqoo narí afeeka maraquna nimiannoo fee qinau.
Faiqí anaasee Yisuna ufa iriseeqa qiqau. Maafa Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqa kambiqaannoo fee qufa maafa mifa maridanoo.
Akaqausa minara maafa Anutuna asauku mundira fee qiqau. Akaqausa maaqi qimasee furufaramasee qiqau. Anutuna asauku mundirafa sia Kariree maqusakiqari kambiqaannoo.
Tamummaqara fasiqa akara minara Anutuna asauku mundirafa Dafidina ati mariannoo. Dafidina ooqeenaa maqusaki Beetareeqeemma miqoo kambiqaannoo fee qiqau.
Faiqí anaasee misa rainafufaqa akaqausa moo ufa qufaqa akaqausa moo ufa qufaqa qimariqau.
Akaqausa doo Yisuna qumarasee rumbaannee qimasee sia qumaree rumbaqau.
Amaana maqasaa rakisira poorisauqa Yisuna ufa kaqi irisee amaana maqasaa rakisirausa faqa Farisai amaana ufa qimariasa faqa maruqoo oonuroofaqa iraidaqa qiqau. Naqaa fee ifaqee sia rumbasee maree anidee.
Poorisauqa qiqau, sia moo fasiqa ufa fannoo maa fasiqana aanna raidanoo.
Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa mina iriseeqa niqidaqa qiqau. Doo mi fasiqafa inni faqa nikaruqinoo fee. Maasa uriqararausakiqari moo fannoo mina ufa irinoo fee. Farisai amaana ufa qimarifa moo fannoo irinoo fee. Sia uqanna iria. Maasa Mooseena sandufa irimarunausa maridaqa.
<range>
Maaqooqaraasa kaqiqee fasiqa anaasee Mooseena sandufa sia irianara Yisunara anoonee qidaqa. Anutuna aqira ufa misasaa maridanoo.
Nikoodeemusafa mifa faqa misaki marinau. Mifa ooqai qumee Yisufinnai fimarufa marinau.
Mifa misa Yisuna aqira ufa iriseenoo Yisuna saaroo qinau. Mooseena sandufa maaqimminoo maridanoo. Sia fifau faiqí moo arirafa maridanoo. Mina ufa naaree irisee mina mandainaina marinaqa minara qimasee aruananoo amana mariannoo qinau.
Misa mi ufana iriseeqa Nikoodeemusana aqidaqa qiqau. Anee faqa Kariree maqannaa fee maridanee. Anee tamummaqara fasiqauqa akarauqakiaqa asaanarumasee iria. Sia moo tamummaqarafa Kariree maqasaa kambiqaannoo. Miqi qimasee aiqama daraani mambufanoo Yisufa amaana maqakiqari raudamakufanoo Oorifa aaqanai oorufinau.

Oorifa aaqanai kaqimma ooru faiqeenoo iqaqoofanoo Yisufa Yeerusaree firaa amaana maqaki kaifaa ooquree keeqafufaqa faiqí anaasee moomoosa suqufufaqa mina fiqu fiqumma marufanoo ooqumarifi Anutuna ufa qimannimimarinau.
<range>
Mooseena sandufa akoofasauqa faqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa faqa anaasee moo fasiqa qummuari marufaqa aaqee oonu qafamasee qumaree doo maree aniqau. Yisufa maruqoo mini quqaseeqa maaqi qimasee qimamiqau.
Oo ufasaa rakisira maa anaaseefa qummuari marifaqa maasa qafamasee qumaree anidaqa.
Mooseena sandufa miqiasara oonisamu kai nariqa nini iqa kuqa narusaaqee qinoo maridanoo. Anee minara nana ufee qidanee.
Misa mi ufanannai puteera foora fufidaqa qiqau. Yisufa aruanifeera qimasaida miqi marufanoo Yisufa narí iriseenoo fifau kummaramafufanoo asaukunnoo maqa akara rinau.
Mifa maqa fifau akara rimarufaqa misa fuki faaki qidaqa mi anaaseena oonisamu aruanauree sia fee aruanauree ritidaqa ireemariqau. Kaqikaaqoo marikinoo Yisufa findifi qimanniminau. Yafee inniki moo fannoo numoo siainafa mifa kai oonisamu indaaru aunaa atufinoo maa anaaseena aruannoo fee.
Yisufa miqi qimaseenoo kafaa kummaramafinoo maqa akara rimarufaqa doo misa moodaa kai qaara kai idaqa nári aaqaranara nisaurusee findimeeqaida doo fifainimariqau. Faiqí firaasa naaree fufaqa kafaa miqoo oorudupirausa fufaqa kumaaraa inaaqianna doo fifiqau. Misa fifufanoo mi anaaseefa kai miqoo kikiqinoo marinau.
<range>
Yisufa findifinoo mi anaaseena irammirinau, misa yai fee fifee. Sia fee moo fannoo ani kuqira ufa amianinafa maridanoo fee. Aiqama fifee.
Mi anaaseefa qinau. Oo rakisira sia kuqira ufa moo fannoo qimimarifa maridanoo. Yisufa iriseenoo qinau. Doo qinee faqa sia kuqira ufa ani amianaura. Doo fua, sia kafaa manda oosana maraa.]
Moo kari Yisufa Yeerusaree amaana maqaki faiqí anaasee maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Qinee maqasaaqaraasa qooma maridaqa. Yafasiqa aanaaseesa qini faqa finausa misa kaqi marira qooma mareefaranoo sia uqanna asukunaki fifaranoo.
Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa mina iriseeqa qimamiqa qiqau. Anee aneennara kai ufa qidana aneenna auqu uqeeree mariananoo. Miqianna ufafa sia anoonaikidanoo. Fifau ufa kai qimariananoo.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo qinau. Kuqaa qinee qeeqaraa ufa qidaqa. Qinee miqi qidaqa anoona ufa kai qidaqa. Qinee qeeqa kambiqafi aniafannanara iridaqa qeeqa fuannanara iridaqa. Innee sia qinee kambiqaafannanara irimariafanoo.
Innee faiqí faiqi ufa irisee dapi iriranannai faiqí anaasee rainannimaqee mariafanoo. Sia qinee moo fasiqa aanaaseera rainannimaqee marunausa maridaqa.
Qinee akaqausara rainannimaqaidaqau andeeqasee rainannisaunaiqini. Sia qeeqaraafau maridaqau ufa nimidaqau. Qeeqa qikoofa qini diqiqamaqoona faqa maridaqa dadaaqi marifaqa ufa qimannimidaqa.
Inni sandufa akara ufa moo maaqimminoo maridanoo. Qaara fasiqa moo ainaina nári nifunnai qafamasee munu kooroo qimasaifaqa aiqamausa minara anoona ufa fee qifaranoo.
Qinee qeeqaraa ufa qidaqa qini qikoofa qini diqiqoofa mifa faqa qini dadaaqifaqa anoona ufa tia qimannimidaqa.
Miqi qimasoofaqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa maaqi qimasee irammiriqau. Ani akoofa yai fee maridanoo ani dadaaqidanoo fee qufanoo Yisufa qinau. Innee qiniara faqa qini qikoonara faqa sia irimariafanoo. Innee qiniara irifau qini qikoonara faqa irini. Innee sia maaqandara irimariafanoo.
Yisufa maa ufausa Yeerusaree firaa amaana maqaki qimannimimarinau. Mi amaana maqanaki oosirafa moo marinau. Amaana maqaki quqee maru munnimma difaanifa minaki marufanoo mi oosiranaki Yisufa maridanoo mi ufausa qimanniminau. Misa Yisuna qumaraanee qimasee sia qumaraqau. Sia mina kuqira aukuana adeedi ranoo marunara Anutufa qumee rafaaqafusoofaqa sia qumaraqau.
Moo kari Yisufa maaqi qimasee Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa qimanniminau. Qinee moosaa fuanaqa qiniara randainaisia inneeqa mandainainaki kuqifaranoo. Qinee fuannaqoo innee sia amana fifaranoo.
Yuda maqannaasa uriqararausa mi ufana iriseeqa narí qimami narí qimami qiqau. Mifa maasara sia narí innai fuaqeera qidaqinoo. Maasa sia mina ufa iridaqa. Mifa narí fee narí aruannoo fee miqi qidanoo fee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qimanniminau. Innee maindaraasa mariafanoo qinee mirindaraasa maridaqa. Innee maa maqanasaaqaraasa mariafanoo qinee sia maa maqanasaaqaraasau maridau.
Qinee minara qunnana innee inneeqa mandainainaki kuqifaranoo. Innee sia qinee marunnanara anoonee qimariafanoo minara kuqaa innee inneeqa mandainainaki kuridifaranoo.
Misa uriqararausa mina iriseeqa qiqau. Anee yafee maridanee qufanoo Yisufa qinau. Indaaru qimannimiafanausa misa kai maridaqa.
Qinee moomoo ainainara inniara qimannimianaura. Qini diqiqamaqoofa mifa anoona ufa kai qimarifa mifinaindaraana kai inni maa maqanasaa mariasa qimannimidaqa.
Yisufa narí akoona aufakiana qimannimimarufaqa siamma irimariqau. Minara Yisufa kaifaa maaqi qimasee qimanniminau.
Kasooqaqee innee qini faiqí nimaaku uqeereeqee aunirira saqarisaa quqaqisaseeqa mikamuqoo qinee mariaafannanara irifaranoo. Qini qikoofa qimaqimiqoo ufana kai inni qimannimidaqa. Mikari innee minara faqa amiqimasee irifaranoo.
Qini diqiqoofa qini faqa maridanoo. Qinee mina aidira oosanamau kai fidaqa minara sia minniqisaifaqau qeeqaraafau maridaqau. Mifa qini faqa maridanoo.
Faiqí anaasee moomoosa mi ufana iriseeqa Oo kuqaa mifa Anutuna asauku mundira fee qimasee minasaa mundiqau.
Yisufa minara iriseenoo qimanniminau. Innee qini ufa qimannimunnana irisee mi mau maqee maqee fifaqa kuqaa qini faiqi namu marifaranoo.
Innee kuqaa anoona ufa kai irifaranoo. Anoona ufa fannoo inniqa mandainainakiqari inni idukuannoo.
Misa mi ufana iriseeqa qiqau. Maasa Abarahaamana ati maridaqa, sia moona rumbaranaki maridaqa. Nanaree anee maasara idukuaqee qidanee.
Miqi qufanoo Yisufa kafaa qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa inni qimannimidaqa. Faiqí moo fannoo mandoosana maree marifa mi manda oosanafa mina rumbaqaifa maridanoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo moona ainaina iinoo oosana oosana ainaina narindiara foora iinoo. Kasooqaqee doo ainaini taikaseenoo mi aiqama ainainna narí amiseenoo doo kaqisamu fuannoo. Mi ainainna faqaana faiqi fannoo sia amana taikaannoo kaqi narí akoona amaaku mariannoo kaqi narí akoona amaaqa maqa finoo mina qumiasana maraseenoo sia ainainira faiqi naanna reenoo taikaannoo, kaqi miqoo mariannoo.
Qinee Anutuna amaaku maridaqa. Qinee inniqa manda oosanakiqari idukusaanaqa innee kuqaa idukiqa marifaranoo.
Innee Abarahaamana ati mariafaqa qinee minara iridaqa sia innee mina aanna reemariafaqa, qini ufa sia marararee qidaqa qini dariraree qimariafanoo. Abarahaamafa sia miqi marufa minara innee sia Abarahaamana faiqi namu uqanna mariafanoo.
Qini qikoofa qini uqaqifiqoona kai inni qimannimidaqa. Innee mina minniseeqa inneeqa nikoona moo Sadannana ufa irimariafanoo.
Misa mi ufana iriseeqa maaqi qiqau. Maasa qikoofa Abarahaamafa maridanoo. Yisufa minara qinau. Innee Abarahaamana faiqi namu maridaqau mina ufamau fini.
Qinee qeeqa qikoonasaaqaraa ufa kai inni qimannimimarunaqa innee quandafiqa qini darirara qimariafanoo Abarahaamafa sia mi oosanna maranau.
Innee inneeqa nikoona uqanna oosana maraidaqa miqi mariafanoo. Misa mi ufana iriseeqa qiqau. Maasa sia qummuara faiqifau maridaqau. Maasa moodaa fasiqa faiqi Anutufa narí uqanna maasa qikoofa maridanoo.
Yisufa misa ufa iriseenoo maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Anutufa inni nikoofa marinaqau kuqaa innee qiniara rini. Qinee Anutufinaindari maaqoo qumumaridaqa. Qinee sia qeeqafau qumiqau mifa diqiqoofaqa qumiqiafana.
Innee naqaa fee ifaqee sia qini ufa oosana iridee. Innee qini ufa iriafanoo nikooqaidanoo miqidaqa sia irimariafanoo.
Afaanna nikoofa Sadannafa maridanoo. Innee mina faiqi namu maridaqa mina aanna ree mariafanoo. Ooqaindari faiqí kuqannarimarufa maridanoo. Sia anoonufakifau mapukinoo maridanoofau. Anoona ufa sia uqanna minaki marifa maridanoo. Mifa unna ufa qinoo narí oosanamau kai fidanoo. Mifa unna ufa qimarifa maridanoo unna ufa qimariasa nikoofa maridanoo.
Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa kai qimannimi marunnanara innee sia irimariafanoo.
Qini manda oosana moodaa maridanoo fee sia fee maridanoo. Innee qafee qiqa qimaqimiaqa. Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa kai inni qimannimunaqa naqi fee ifaqee innee sia minara anoonee qidee.
Anutufa dadaaqifaqa mina faiqi namu araamuqmaakaiki mariasa kai Anutuna ufa irifaranoo. Innee sia Anutunaindaraasau mariafanoofau sia qini ufa irimariafanoo.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa Yisuna ufa iriseeqa aqiqa qiqau. Anee manda Samaria maqannaa mariananoo afaanna moo ani aunduraki marifa mariananoo. Maasa kuqaa fee qidee, sia fee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qinau. Afaanna sia qiniki maridanoo. Qinee qeeqa qikoona auqu uqeeraidaqa innee qini duqu maqasaa quqeemariafanoo.
Qinee sia qeeqa duqu uqeeraranara randaidaqa. Moo fannoo qini duqu uqeerarafa maridanoo. Innee qini duqu maqasaa quqeemariafanoo Anutufa kai qini dadaaqinoo inni rafaaqa fuannoo.
Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini dookinaa ufa irisee marainafa mifa sia kuquannoo naaru mariannoo.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mi ufana iriseeqa qiqau. Doo maasa ani oosana iriseeqa anee kuqaa afaanna faqaafa mariananoo, Abarahaamafa maasa qikoofa doo ooqai kuqinau. Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqauqa doo kuqiqau. Anee naqi fee masee maa ufana qidanee qini ufa irimariasa sia kuqifaree qidanee.
Maasa qikoofa Abarahaamafa kuqinau. Anee mina uriqarara fee maridanee qidanee. Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqauqa maqasaa fasiqauqa kuqufufana anee aneennaraa naqira fasiqee maridee qidanee.
Miqi qimasoofanoo Yisufa qimanniminau. Qinee qeeqa duqu fifau uqeerasaana sia anoonaikiannoo, fifau mariannoo. Qini qikoofa Anutufa qini duqu uqeeraidanoo dadaaqidanoo, innee unna qimasee minara maasa Anutunee qimariafanoo.
Innee ooqaindari sia mina auqu irimariafanoo. Qinee mina auqu iridaqa. Qinee minara sia iridau inni naanna reemarunausa unna ufa qimarunausee qini. Qinee qeeqa qikoonara iridaqa mina ufamau fimarunausa maridaqa.
Inni nikoofa Abarahaamafa ooqai kaqi maridanoo qinee maqee marunnanara kaaqa qafaaqaa imarufa marinau. Doo qiqafamaseenoo asasinau.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mi ufana iriseeqa maaqi qiqau. Anee kumaaraa mariananoo. Anee naqimasee Abarahaamana qafanee inau, ooqai mariufa maridanoo.
Yisufa minara maaqi qimasee qimanniminoo qinau. Abarahaamafa sia kambiqoo aukuanna qinee maa marunausa mikamuqoo mariqiafana.
Yuda maqannaasa mina iriseeqa oo maa fasiqafa nariara Yaawee fee qidaqinoo qimasee aanoomasee oonisamu qumaree aruaneerufanoo mifa kukeeqakinoo amaana maqakiqari raudamaki moosaa finau.
Yisufa aatata fidanoo moo fasiqa mina anoofa innaamunai afu dimbarana maqaqoona qafanau. (Mi aukuanna nifu niku mandaikirausauqa mai mariandee sia amana ainainamasee naaqaa imariqau. Faasaana kaqi marida narana feefaurira munnimmara ireemarufaqa nimimarufaqa marasaida neemariqau misa nuqu iramasaida neemariasee qiqau.)
Yisuna faiqinamu mi afu qimbarana qafamasee Yisuna irammiriqa qiqau. Oo ufasaa rakisirafa maa fasiqafa yana mandainainasaa fee maaqinoo afu dimbanoo maridanoo fee. Narí akoona anoona mandainainasaa fee narindisaa fee miqinoo maridanoo fee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Sia narí anoona akoonasaa qaraanau, sia narindisaafau afu dimbanoo maridanoofau. Anutuna afeeka kasirana qinikiqari kooroo ianifeera mina afu dimbanoo maridanoo.
Qini diqiqoofa qini qimiqoo ainainirana sia amana asukunaki auqaanaura maasa faasaana auqaanaura. Doo kaqikaaqoo eendinaqa sia miqoo faiqí moo fannoo auqaannoo.
Qinee maa maqa maaqanaki maridaqa misa qooma maridaqa, kaaqa qamannimaqaanaura.
Miqi qimasee Yisufa maqasaa aqaara fidaquseenoo asaukukoo doonaikamaseenoo afu dimbara fasiqa afusaa akuseenoo qimaminoo qinau.
Doo fua. Doo oonu Sirooamma farummaki aneenna oori afuakai ruquannee qinau. Sirooamma farumma auqu oosana niqiqamaqai farumma fee qinoo marinau. Mi afu qimbara fasiqafa eedoo qimasee oonu narí oori afuakai ruqufanoo afu aiqamaqara amiqimasee qoofanoo oonu quandakufanoo sandee kafaa aninau.
Mi fasiqana aqoonausa mina qafamasee moomoosa mina qafeemarusa mina qafamasee qiqau. Maa fasiqafa maaqoo maridanoo narana munnimmara ireemari fasiqa fee mifee.
Akaqausa doo mifa kai fee qiqau, akaqausa moo fannoo mina fooqaa fee qiqau. Mi fasiqafa narí irisee qinau. Qinee qifu dimbarausa maaqoo marunausa maridaqa.
Misa mina iriseeqa iraqau. Naqimasee afu maqeenee qufanoo mifa qinau.
Faiqí moo mina auqu Yisufa qaqaara fidiseenoo doonaikamaseenoo qini qifuki akuseenoo doo fua Sirooamma farummaki oori nammari uqua qufaqa miqi qifaqa nammari uqusaunanoo doo qifu maqeenoo.
Miqi qimaasoofaqa misa qiqau. Miqimasaifa yai fee finoo fee qufanoo mifa sia qinee irida fee qinau.
Miqi qimasoofaqa misa mi fasiqana afiqeeqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa uqannifiqanau.
Mi faasaanna Yisufa mi fasiqana afu maqoo faasaana misa amaana Saririqa marunara Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa marunnai afiqee fiqau.
Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa mi fasiqana afu maqoonara iroofanoo qinau. Mifa doona qini qifusaa akusaifaqa doori nammari uqunanoo qifu maqeenoo.
Farisai amaana ufa qimariasa akaqausa Yisunara maaqi qiqau. Maa fasiqana afu maqaifa sia Anutunaindarifau amaanasaa ainainimarifa manda fasiqa maridanoo. Akaqausa mina iriseeqa qiqau. Naqimasee mandainaina maree marinafa maa firaa ainainna amiqira ainaina auqararee sia amana fee qimasee mi ufanannai rainaqau.
Miqi qimasee Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa afu dimbarana irammiriqa qiqau. Anee mi fasiqana ani afu maqainaree qidanee. Anee minara nana ufee qidanee. Afu dimbarafa mina iriseenoo qinau. Mifa Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqa maridanoo fee qinau.
Yuda maqannaasa uriqararausa mina iriseeqa maaqi qiqau. Maana sia afu dimbarafau moo fasiqa maridanoo qimaseeqa misa mina anoona akoona naaramasee irammiriqa qiqau. Maa fasiqafa inniqara faiqi fee. Kuqaa fee anee mina maqoonna kari afu dimbaranee maqanau. Naqimasee maqee afu maqeenoo fee qufaqa mina anoofa akoofa uriqararausa amaana maqaki keeqeemariana qaoo qimaqiseefoo qimasee rufieeqa qimannimiqa qiqau. Maa fasiqafa maasa qimaaku maridanoo maasa minara iridaqa. Ooqai aanaaqisaa innaamunai miqirana maqaafanafa maridanoo maasa minara faqa iridaqa.
<range>
<range>
Mina afu maqainara yafasiqa fee mina afu maqeenoo fee siamma iridaqa faiqí maridanoo irammirifanoo qimannimiannoo.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa Yisunara faasa maaqi qimariqau. Faiqí moo fannoo Yisunara Anutuna asauku mundira fee qinnana maasa amaana maqakiqari aqiqaananoo raudamaki aqoosai finoo sia kaifaa keeqaannoo.
Mi ufanara afu dimbarana anoofa akoofa doo faiqimmifoo narí iraaqee qiqau. Misara rufiasee miqi qiqau.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mina iriseeqa afu dimbarana kafaa aaramasee qiqau. Anee Anutuna afusaa kuqaa anoona ufa kai maasa qimannimia. Ani afu maqaifa mifa mandainaina maree marifa maridanoo.
Afu dimbarafa mina iriseenoo qimanniminau. Mi fasiqafa mandainaina maree mari fee sia qinee mina oosana iridaqa. Moodaa ainainara kai qinee iridaqa qinee qifu dimbarausa mariafanausa maqee qini qifu maqee marifaqa maridaqa minara kai qinee amiqimasee iridaqa.
Misa mina iriseeqa kaifaa irammiriqa qiqau. Mi fasiqafa nana ainainee auqu amifanoo ani afu maqeenoo fee.
Afu qimbarafa niqinoo qinau. Doo faasai qimannimisaunaqa sia irimariafanoo. Nanaree innee kaifaa qiana irifaree innee faqee mina faiqinamukifaree.
Misa mina iriseeqa aanoomasee mina aqiqa qiqau. Anee mi fasiqana ufa irimarianafa mariananoo. Maasa Mooseena ufa irimarunausa maridaqa.
Anutufa Mooseenannai maasa qimaqimufaqa maasa iridaqa. Mi fasiqafa Yisunara maasa sia mina oosanara iridaqa.
Afu dimbarafa mina iriseenoo niqinoo qinau. Innee moo irirana maree mariafanoo mifa qini qifu maqaqisaifaqa innee nanaree mi fasiqanara yaindari fee anidanoo fee qidee.
Anutufa sia manda oosana maree mariasa dadaaqidanoo. Faiqí anaasee minara rimariasa mina ufa irimariasa misa kai Anutufa dadaaqidanoo.
Ooqai oosana aroo aukuannasaaqari sia faiqí moo fannoo afu dimbarana nifu maqannisanau, maqee kai.
Maa fasiqafa sia Anutufinaindari aninaqau naqimandee maa firaa ainainna auqararee, siamma amanaikiannoo.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mina iriseeqa qimamiqa qiqau. Anee mandainainaki kambiqoonafa mandoosanaki findifuanafa doo see fifuannee qimaseeqa misa amaana maqakiqari aqiqoofanoo raudamaki finau, sia kafaa anianifeera doo ateekaqau.
Misa afu qimbarana aqiqoonara Yisufa iriseenoo paqurimasee irammirinau. Anee faiqí nimaakuara Anutuna asauku mundira fee fee qidanee minasaa irirana rusidanee.
Mi fasiqafa Yisuna sia qafoofa maridanoo maaqi qinau. Doo mina uqaqifiqainaqa minara anoonee qimasee minasaa atooqaanaura.
Yisufa qinau doo anee qafaananoo doo mina faqa ufa qimariananoo.
Mi fasiqafa mina iriseenoo qinau. Oo Karaambaiqa aniara kuqaa Anutuna amaaku fee qidaqa qeeqa qimuqusa irirana aniki rusidaqa qimuqusannoo ani amooqimamaqaidaqa. Miqi qimaseenoo mi fasiqafa Yisuna oorinni maqasaa kummaramafinoo amooqinau.
Yisufa mina qafamasee miqoo marusa qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee maa maqanasaaqarasaa rainannimaqarara qumuafanausa maridaqa. Qinee nifu dimbarausa maqaaneera qumuafanausa nifu maqarausa dimbaaneera qumuafanausa maridaqa.
Farisai amaana ufa irimarusa miqoo marusa mina iriseeqa iramiriqa qiqau anee maasara faqee nifu dimbarausee qidanee.
Yisufa qinau. Inni nifu dimbanoo marinaqau inni numoo sia marini innee unna qimasee maasa qifu kaqi marifaqee qimarianara inni numoo kaqi maridanoo nifu dimbarausara foora mariafanoo.
Yisufa kafaa miqooqaraasaa qimannimidanoo sipsipara qinoo faiqiara qinau. Qinee anoona ufa qimannimidaqa. Faiqí moo fannoo sia sipsipa ququsa kooqiki keeqeemarifa kaqinaindari ququsasaa akareemarifa mifa qummuarimari fasiqafa mariannoo.
Sipsipa kooqiki keeqee marifa mifa sipsipasaa rakisimarifa maridanoo.
Sipsipa nikoofa moo fannoo anirainanoo kooqisaa rakisirafa kooqi atuasaifanoo sipsipa akoofa narí sipsipa nuqu ramasee naarainaqa mina ufa iriseeqa raudamaki narí faqa nifiqainaqa andanda narara fifaranoo.
Sipsipauqa nári rakisimarina ufa iriqa raudee qumuraifanoo mifa indaaru fifaqa misa mina aanaaqianna fidaqa.
Sipsipa sia moo fasiqa afaqee fifaranoo mina ufa irisee moo fannoo fee qimasee sandeefaranoo.
Yisufa mi quandara ufana qimannimufaqa siamma iriqau.
Minara iriseenoo kafaa kooroomasee qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa qimannimidaqa qinee qeeqa kai sipsipa kooqi maridaqa.
Ooqai qini doorini indaaru anusa qummuari maru fasiqausa kai animariqau. Sipsipauqa sia misa ufa iriqau.
Qinee Anutuna ququsa kooqi maridaqa yafasiqa aanaaseefee kooqisaarafoo qinisaa keeqee marinafa Anutufa mi fasiqanaaseesa kuqiranakinaana marasee innaaruna asumu mariranaki quqaannoo. Mi fasiqanaaseesa Anutuna ququsaki sipsipara foora keeqee raudeeida narana neemarifaranoo.
Qummuarimari fasiqafa qummuaramasaina taikaanifeera fifau faafau qummuarianifeera faqa kuqannaruanifeera faqa kuridi nimaqaanifeera faqa aniannoo. Qinee faiqí anaasee asumu marirana nimianeera anidaqa. Sia kaqi dapi mariranarau qidau. Asumu marirana amiqirana moo faqa moo faqa rairaairana nimirara mina kai nimiraree qimasee qumidaqa.
Qinee sipsipasaa amiqimasee rakisimarunausa maridaqa. Sipsipasaa amiqimasee rakisimarifa narí sipsipasaara kuquannoo.
Feefauruara ainainimarifa sia miqiannoo kaasau faini anirainanoo rufiasee sandaannoo. Sandamafinanoo kaasau faini anireenoo sipsipa qumarainaqa daraanifaranoo.
Feefauruara ainainimarifa sia sipsipara amuqusiannoo feefauruara kai rakisidanoo.
Qinee sipsipasaa amiqira rakisirausa maridaqa. Qini qikoofa qiniara iridanoo. Qinee miqi kai iqa qeeqa qikoonara faqa iridaqa.
Miqi kai iqa qeeqa sipsipara iridaqa misa faqa qiniara faqa iridaqa. Qinee qeeqa sipsipasaara amana kuquanauree qidaqa.
Sia maaqooqaraasa kai qini ququsaki mariaqeera. Qini ququsa fannoo moomoo maqusanaasaki faqa maridanoo. Minakinaasauqa faqa nifiqa quqaanaura. Misa faqa qini ufa irisee eedoo qifaranoo. Miqoo moodaanaki marifaranoo moodaa rakisirafa misasaa mariannoo.
Qeeqa sipsipara qimuqusina qeeqa marirana misa nimaaqa maqaseeqa kuqirinaki quqasee kaifaa qeeqa marirana minakiqari maraanaura. Qinee miqiraree qunnanara qini qikoofa qiniara ridanoo asasidanoo.
Sia moo fannoo narí afeekannai qini marirana maraannoo. Qinee qeeqakai qeeqaraa irisee qeeqa marirana kuqiranaki quqaanaura. Qini qikoofa qinaqa qeeqa marirana kuqiranaki quqararee qimasee quqaanaura. Quqasee kafaa marararee qimasee maraanauranoo. Qini qikoofa miqi qimasee ufa qimaqimifaqa iridaqa.
Yuda maqannaasa miqooqaraasa Yisuna mi ufana iriseeqa rainafufaqa akaqausa qiqau. Maa fasiqana audurai afaanna maridanoo, marifanoo dapi dapi ufa qidanoo, nanaree innee mina ufa iridee.
<range>
Miqi qimasoofaqa akaqausa misa qimannimiqa qiqau. Akasaa afaanna aunduraki marinafa sia maa fasiqafa indeemasee ufa qiannoo. Afaanna fannoo amanee afu dimbarana maqaiseenoo fee sia amanaikiannoo.
Mookari Yuda maqannaasa Yeerusaree maqusai suqufufaqa amaana maqara qoomaqammasaida neemariqau. (Ooqai namuqaa amaana maqaki mini madaapee quqasoofaqa mina anukamaquseeqa doo miqooqari aukuana aukuana anukara qoomaqaqee qimasaida sakasaida neemariqau.) Suara aukuana mi qoomaqana imariqau Yeerusaree maqusai.
Yisufa Yeerusaree maqusai oorureenoo amaana maqa atisaa tida auquqoonasaa aakuara rufiasee minaki nimarinau. (Faiqí anaasee moomoo aaku suarara rufiaseeqa minaki kai mariqau.) Amaana maqa atimau tidasaa kisaaqa firaaqoo marinau. Yisufa Sooroomoona amarana maaqa atimau tidasaa nimarufaqa Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa ititaseeqa irammiriqa qiqau. Anee sia quandaqaandia, amiqimandee akooroomasee maasa qimaqimia, kuqaa fee Anutuna asauku mundira fee maridanee.
<range>
Yisufa maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Doo qimannimuna siamma irimariafanoo. Qinee moomoo qeeqa qikoofinaindaraa ainaina auquseeqa minannoo inni uqannifiqaunausa maridaqa.
Innee sia qinee firimarunna aandau sipsipauqau mariafanoofau minara sia qiniara anoonee qimariafanoo.
Qini sipsipauqa qini ufa iridaqa qinee misara faqa iridaqa, misa minara aiqama qini faqa fidaqa.
Qinee naaru naaru marirana nimidaqa sia kuqifaranoo. Sia amana moo fannoo qini qisaukukinaana rafieefaranoo.
Qini qikoofa qini sipsipauqa qimufa aiqamausa uriqararafa maridanoo, sia moo fannoo mina asaukukinaana rafieefaranoo.
Qini qikoofa faqa qinee faqa moodaa marunnanara sia amana rafieefaranoo.
Yuda maqannaasa mi ufana iriseeqa aanoomasee oonisamu qumaree Yisuna arirarufanoo qinau.
Qinee moomoo amiqira ainaina auqaidaqa qini qikoofa qimu ainaina auqaidaqa innee nana amiqira ainainara irisee fee minasaara oonisamu qini darirara qidee.
Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa mina iriseeqa kafaa aranaiqi qimamiqa qiqau. Sia amiqira dadaaqira ainaina auqaananarau ariraridau. Aneenaraa Anutuna mandaikammamaqaidana anee aneennaraa maqasaa fasiqa marianafa anee Anutufaikina mariannanara ariraridaqa.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo qinau. Inni sandufa akaraki Anutufa qinau. Innee faiqí faiqi Anutunaikammida mariafanoo.
Sandufa andeeqanoo maridanoo naaru naaru sia aaqee mariafanoo, innisaimbaqa minara iridaqa. Anutufa narí ufa misasaa quqaseenoo misara Anutu fee qinau.
Anutufa qini maraseenoo maa maqa maaqanaki diqiqamaqoonaki maridaqa. Qinee qeeqaraa Anutuna amaaku fee qunnanara naqimasee fee minannai Anutuna mandaikamma amaqaanauree sia amanaikiannoo.
Qinee qini qikoofa auqamaqai ainaina auqaanaqa qafamasee kuqaa anoonammifoo qiaqaana. Qini qikoofa sia auqamaqai ainainna auqaanaqa qafamasee unnammifoo qiaqaana.
Innee qeeqaraa ufa qunnanara unna fee qimasaida qinee faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainainna auqaanaqa qafamasee qiniara kuqaa anoona fee qimasee kuqaa mina akoofa minaki marinara miqidanoo fee qiaqaana kaifaa mifa faqa nariki marinara miqidanoo fee qiaqaana.
Yisufa miqi qimasoofaqa misa qumaraaneerufanoo kaqimbinau.
Yisufa Yooradanna nammarinni ooqureenoo ooqitaqa mareenoo ooqai Yoohaneefa maridanoo nammari nimiuqoo miqoo ooqu marinau.
Faiqí anaasee moomoosa suqufufaqa Yisufa maruqoo maridaqa narí qimami narí qimami maaqi qiqau. Yoohaneefa nammari nimimarufa sia moo ainaina firaa ainaina auqanau. Yoohaneefa maa fasiqanara qufa doo aiqamainaina anoonaikidanoo.
Miqoo faiqí anaasee moomoosa Yisunara kuqaa Anutuna faiqi fee qimasee mina saqarikiqau.
Faiqí moo auqu Rasarusafa mifa Beetani maqusaindaraafa aurida marinau. Rasarusafa narí asookiqanda Mariana amarana faqa Maratana faqa misa Beetani maqusaindaraasa mariqau.
Mariafa maafa kasooqaqee amiqira afundimaru fadameena Yisuna aikusaa adiaseenoo narí akiaqa asausi kisaaqannai rukaaninafa maana mi Mariafa maridanoo. Sia Yisuna anoofau mina amarafa marinau.
Mi Mariana afasaafa Rasarusafa kuqira aurira maroofaqa mina asookiqanda qafamaseeqa faiqí moo aiqeeqa anee Yisuna ooqu afiqee uruannee qufanoo ooqu finau. Mifa maaqi qinau ani afaaqasaa aqoondi Rasarusafa kuqira aurirana maraidanoo.
Yisufa mi ufana iriseenoo narí faiqi namu qimanniminau. Rasarusafa aurida maridanoo. Sia kuqiranaki firarau Rasarusafa mi aurirana maraidanoofau mina auriranannai Anutufa narí amaaku qini duqu uqeeraanifeera mi aurirana maraidanoo.
Yisufa miqanda qisanasaasa faqa misa nisookinara faqa kaaqa misara rimarinau. Yisuna afaaqasaa aqoondi marunara rimarinau.
Rasarusana auriranara iriseenoo sia dauni finau qaara afuru faiqanau.
Qaara afuru faiqee iqaqoofanoo narí faiqi namu qimanniminau. Uqeeraifaqa innisaimbaqa kafaa qumurandee Yudeea maqa maaqai Rasarusafa aurida qina ooru qafa.
Miqi qufaqa misa tautumandee maaqi qiqau, Oo ufasaa rakisirafa innau kai Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa oonisamu ani arirara qufana kafaa fee miqoo fidanee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qinau, iqaqaifanoo kai suani urureenoo kaaqa qaidanoo. Faiqí miqi mariqoo nidaqa sia saamuridaqa. Misa maa maqanasaa kaaqa qarafa marifaqa qafaida sia saamuridaqa.
Faiqí moo fannoo asukunai nidanoo oonisaa aikuamaki saamuridanoo, sia kaaqa qarafa minaki marinara miqidanoo Anutufa qi faasaana ooru fiqa sia saamuruanaura kaaqa qeemarina ooru fuanaura.
Yisufa maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Rasarusafa maasa qiqoondi doo faiqaqee ifaqa qinee oorureeqa afaurianaura.
Mina faiqi namu mina iriseeqa qiqau. Oo karaambaiqa mifa fifau faiqaqee idanoo findifuannoo amiqirafa.
Yisufa kuqiranara faiqeefoo qimasoofaqa misa sia iriqau.
Minara Yisufa kooroo qimasee qinau. Rasarusafa doo kuquaraasinoo maridanoo.
Dufi dufi sia qinee miqoo maridaqa inniara iridaqa kasooqaqee Anutuna afeeka qafeeqa kuqaa qiniara Anutuna amaaku fee qifaranoo doo uqeeraifaqa fua Rasarusafinnai.
Toomasina auqu qaara auqu marinau. Moo auqu Toomasifa moo auqu Qaaraqanda maqara fee qimariqau. Toomasifa Yisufa Yudeeaa maqa maaqai ooru firanara iriseenoo qinau. Doo uqeeraifaqa maasa ufasaa rakisirana faqa Yeerusareenni oorureeqa moodaanaki kuquanauree qimasoofaqa misa aiqama Yisuna faqa Yooradanna nammarindari ooru fiqau.
Narí Yisufa iriseenoo Beetani maqusai ooruroofaqa qimamiqau Rasarusafa doo innau kuqufufaqa akundamaqaafanoo qaara faqa qaara faqa eenda madikaki faiqaqee idanoo.
Beetani maqusa Yeerusaree aaqa uqanna maridanoo. (Beetani maqusa Ubandeenara foora marida Yeerusaree maqusa Faarumaaqaira foora marinau.)
Yeerusaree adeedi marunara moomoo mindaraasa qumuree Maratasa Mariasa dadaaqi ikifaafau qida rooípee mariqau. Nári nifasaafa Rasarusafa kuqunara ikiraqee mariqau.
Maratafa Yisufa ani qu ufana iriseenoo raudamakufanoo oonu afiqaidanoo minara qimamirara fufanoo Mariafa kaqi maaqaki marinau.
Maratafa Yisuna qafamasee qimaminoo qinau, Oo Karaambaiqa anee anirainanoofau sia qini qifasaafa kuqiqini. Qaara faqa qaara faqa faasaana doo kuqufifaqa akundamasee maridaqa.
Miqinoo marifaqa maridaqa, aneenna kai maqee nana ainainaree Anutufinnai nana ainainaree innaaru qinanoo ani amiannoo.
Maratafa narí asookifa kuqunara iridanoo miqi qimasee qimaminau. Yisufa irisee qimaminoo qinau, Anutufa ani afasaana kaifaa mara findifumaiseenoo kaqi marirana amiannoo.
Maratafa mina iriseenoo qinau maa maqa maaqafa taikara faasaana Anutufa qini qisookina uqeerasee kaqi marirana amiannoo qinee minara iridaqa.
Yisufa qimaminau, kuqiranakiqari mara findifirafa qiniki maridanoo. Kaqi marirana marirafa qiniki maridanoo. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini saqarikinoo kuqinoo kaqi mariannoo kuqiranakiqari findifirafa qiniki marinara kaqi mariannoo.
Yafasiqa anaasee fee kaqi maridanoo qini saqarikinoo naaru sia kuquannoo kaqi marirana marirafa qiniki marinara naaru naaru sia kuquannoo. Marata anee minara kuqaa fee qidanee.
Maratafa iriseenoo qinau, eeoo karaambaiqa anee ooqai maa maqa maaqanaki qumuaneera asauku mundirafa Anutuna amaaku uqanna marianafa marianaqa qinee minara kuqaa iridaqa.
Maratafa miqi qimaseenoo quandaki maqusai oonureenoo qumee kai Mariana aaramasee qimaminau. Ufasaa rakisirafa anidanoo ani aaraidanoo.
Mariafa mi ufana iriseenoo kaqi kaqi findimeeqee kaqi unnaqufanoo oonu afiqarara finau.
Yisufa sia maqusai aninau. Aanai Maratafa paquruqoo miqoo kai kaqi marinau.
Mariafa raudamaki kaqi unnaqufanoo fufaqa Yuda maqannaasaa mina faqa mariusa mina qafamasee minara madikai ikiraqarara fidanoommifoo qimasee afaqee fiqau.
Mariafa Yisufa marunnai oonu qafeenoo oorindari maqasaa aqufinoo ufa qimaminau. Oo karaambaiqa anee animariananoofau sia qini qifasaafa kuqiqini.
Yisufa Mariana ikiraqarana qafoofanoo amuqusufanoo Yeerusaree maqannaasa faqa ikiraqoona qafoofanoo amuqusinoo mina aunduraki mandaikinau.
Miqimasee Yisufa irammirinoo qinau. Innee yai fee Rasarusana akundee fee qufaqa misa qiqau Karaambaiqa doo mai aniree qafa.
Miqi qufanoo Yisufa faqa ikiraqanau.
Yeerusaree maqusanaasa miqoo mariusa mina ikiraqarana qafeeqa qiqau. Oo qafa mifa minara kaaqa rimarifa ikiraqaidanoo.
Miqi qufaqa akaqausa niqira ufa qiqau. Mifa nifu dimbarausa amiqimannisee marifa nanaree Rasarusana qaoo qinanoo sia kuquaqaana.
Yisufa narí kai misa miqi qu ufanara akooqoofanoo narí aunduraki mandaikufanoo mi ufanara aiaaee qimaseenoo madikai oonuranau. Rasarusana iri ooni aamaraki quqasee ooni firaatia qumaree ititaqoofanoo marinau.
Yisufa qimanniminoo qinau. Innee maa oonina rafaqaameeqeeqa quanda quandamma aquaqa. Miqi qimasoofaqa Maratafa Rasarusana auna qinau, Oo karaambaiqa mifa qaara faqa qaara faqa afuru faififa marifaqa afunda mandaikammimarifaqa.
Yisufa iriseenoo qimaminau. Qinee faasai qimamunnana anee qini saqarikinana anee Anutuna afeeka eeraarirana qafeennaranoo.
Misa mina iriseeqa ooni firaatia afeeqeeqee mafi quqasoofanoo Yisufa narí oori uqeeraseenoo Anutunara akooqoo innaaru qinoo qinau, Oo qini qikoofa dufi dufi anee qini ufa irimarianafa mariananoo.
Anee maqee maqee qini innaaru qirana irimarianafa marianaqa. Maaqoo mariasa iriaqeera innaaru qidaqa. Maaqoo mariasa anee qini diqiqamaqoonnanara iriaqeera innaaru qidaqa.
Yisufa miqi qimaseenoo innaaru qimaseenoo firaa kari kuqirana aareenoo qinau. Rasarusa minakiqari rauda.
Miqi qimasoofanoo qamunna afaaqa kukuqamaqoofa kaqi marufanoo Rasarusafa findifinoo raudee qumuranau. Mina akiaqa faqa qamunna rumbaqoonarirandee qumuranau. Yisufa qimanniminoo qinau. Doo qamunna idukusaifanoo fuani, qimasoofaqa miqimandoofanoo andeeqasoofanoo finau.
Yeerusaree maqusanaasa moomoosa Rasarusanara ikiraqeeusa misa Yisufa Rasarusana findifumasoona qafeeqa kuqaa Anutuna faiqi fee qimasee minasaa mundiqa mariqau.
Misakiqari akaqausa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa nimaaqai Yeerusareenni ooruree Yisufa Rasarusana findifunara niranaqarufa qimannimiqau.
Misa mina iriseeqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa faqa amaana maqasaa rakisimarusa faqa aiqama faiqí firaasa rakisirausa faqa moodaa qoo suqufi ufa qidaqa qiqau. Maasa naqi fee masee mina Yisuna rafaaqafuanauree. Maa fasiqafa Yisufa moomoo firaa ainaina naaquqara ainaina auqaidanoo.
Maasa mina afauaidaqa faiqí anaasee maasa minnisee minasaa kai atooqeefoora. Miqifanoo Roomma maqannaa sundiauqa anireeqa maasa faiqí anaasee faqa daru taikaidaqa maasa naaquqara amaana maqa faqa rapeepaamma aqifaranoo. Miqifaqa maasa Yuda maqannaa kuridianaura.
Misakina uriqararana auqu Kaiafasafa mifa qimanniminoo qinau. Inniki moo fannoo sia irirana faisa mariafanoo.
Faiqí anaasee maasa aiqama kuquanoora moodaa fannoo aiqamausara kuqifaqa amana maasa amiqimandee marianaura. [
Kaiafasafa sia narí kaifau mi ufana qimanniminau. Anutufa qimamunara kai mi ufana qimanniminau. Kaiafasafa Yisunara Yuda maqannaasa nikiaqara kuquannoo Anutuna faiqi namu mina ufa irimarinausara faqa moodaa iriranasaa mariaqeera kuquannoo fee qinau.]
<range>
Doo mi faasaannasaaqari Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa Yisuna arira ufa oosanarasee deedaqiqau.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo miqooqari sia Yudeeaa maqa maaqaki akooqoo nimarinau. Maqusa moo auqu Eefaraimma maqusai narí faiqi namufaqa ooqu marinau. Eefaraimma aadana maqa maaqa atisaa marinau.
Yisufa Eefaraimma maqa maaqaki marufanoo Yuda maqannaa qoomaqa firaa qoomaqa ainnaaqarara qoomaqa adeedi ranau. Aukuana aukuana Yuda maqannaa oosana ainnaaqarara qoomaqa adeedi ramafufaqa faiqí anaasee aiqama suqumaree miqoo Yeerusaree maqusai ooruraidaqa nári mandainaina findaukee mariqau. Aukuana aukuana miqimariqau.
Faiqí anaasee firaa amaana maqaki Yeerusareenni suqufufaqa Yisunara randaidaqa maaqi qimasee narí qimami narí qimami qiqau. Yisufa firaa qoomaqaki anifeeraannoo sia fee aniraannoo. Innee minara nana iriree iridee.
Amaana maqasaa rakisimarusa faqa Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa faqa Yisunara faiqí anaasee qimannimiqau. Innee ninnabaqa Yisuna paqurimasee dadi oonurandee mini qimaqimifaqa maasa mina qumaraanaura.
Mi ainnaaqarara qoomaqafa Yeerusaree maqusai adeedi reenoo dinni qisauku taikasee dinni ani moodaa faasaana aiqaqainanoo mi qoomaqafa kambiqarara imarufanoo Yisufa Beetani maqusai oonuranau. Yisufa Rasarusana kuqiranakinaana findifu maqusanaki aniranau.
Yisufa aniroofaqa (Rasarusana mara findifunara iriseeqa mina akiaqara qoomaqa firaana suqasee naida amiqau.) Maratafa qoomaqa sakeeqaida nimimarufanoo Rasarusafa Yisuna faqa ooqumarifi narana nanau. (Misa oosana maaqimminoo marinau. Misa qaindasaa fifandirifiqa nisaataa saunarasaida niku uqusaida neemarusa marida miqimandee neemariqau.)
Neemarufanoo Rasarusana asookifa Mariafa Yisuna anoona amarafa fadameena taqu firaana firaa feefauru aqusaida mareemaruna qumareenoo amiqira afundimaru fadameena mina auqu narada fadameena Yisuna aikumau adia amaqanau. Adia amaqaseenoo narí akiaqa asausi kisaaqa qumareenoo minannai utitiqanau. Miqimasoofanoo afunda firaafa misa maru maqanaki qumbiqanau.
Yisuna faiqi namukiqari moo fannoo mina auqu Yudasifa Keerioota maqannaafa Yisuna ueeqaaninna fasiqafa marinau. Mi fasiqafa Yudasifa amiqira afudimaru fadameena moomoo qafamaseenoo maaqi qinau.
Maa fadameenna firaa feefauru mareemaria fadameenafa. Nanaree fifau adieenee. Saina marinana qumiasana faqaana amiseenana moomoo munnimma 300 maraaqaana. Maraseenana kudi fasiqa anaaseeuqa kaqi nimiaqaana. (Mi aukuanna Yuda maqannaasa Mooseena ufa qaindusidaqa kudi fasiqauqa aiqama ainaina dadaaqiqa nimimariqau.)
Yudasifa sia kudi fasiqara irimarufa kaqi fifau ufa marunara miqi qinau. Mifa ummuarimarufa marinau Yisuna faiqi namu pausakinaana kaqi ummuarimarufa mifa maridanoo miqi qinau.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo narí maaqi qimasee qimaminau. Marianara sia miqi qia. Saina miqiani. Afundi fadameenna ataa kaqi marina qinee kuquananoo qini qifaaqai akuqimaqaani.
Anee kudi fasiqa anaaseeuqara qianandee. Kudi fasiqa aanaaseeuqa naaru naaru inniki marifaranoo. Qinee sia kisaaqasaa marianaura qusasaa taikaanaura. Saina fadameena adiaqimaqaani.
Yisufa Beetani maqusai animarufaqa Yeerusaree maqusaindari moomoosa qafarara ooqu fiqau. Kuqiranakiqari findifuna Rasarusana faqa qafararee qimasee ooqu fiqau.
Faiqí anaasee moomoosa Yeerusareendari Yisunasaa atooqaidaqa moomoo ooqu fiqau. Miqiufaqa amaana maqasaa rakisimarusa oommasee qiqau. Rasarusafa kuqiranakiqari findifunara irisee misa Yisunasaa atooqarara ooqu fimarifaqa saina Rasarusana faqa aruanauree qimasee deedaqiqau.
<range>
Faiqí anaasee ainnaaqarara oomaqara maqusa maqusaindari Yeerusaree maqusai suqusee mariusa Yisufa aanai urufaqa afiqarara moomoosa ooqu fiqau.
Ooqu afiqarara ooqu fidaqa koopeena amanee fooqaana moomoo ateekamaree ooqu fiqau. (Misa nariqa qimiriqa Yisunara maaqi qiqau. Ooqai Anutuna asauku mundirafa kambiqanoo marifa uridanoo. Mifa maasa qiqa karaambaiqaikirara uridanoo.) Misa ooqu fidaqa maaqi qimasee firaa kari faaqariqau. Anutuna amooqia mina auqu uqeeraa. Anutufa qufanoo kambiqarafa uridanoo, Anutufa mina amiqi amiqiani, Anutufa Isaraee maqannaa Karaambaiqa amiqi amiqiani.
Yisufa doonki moo maqee innooqee marunnasaa paqurimasee minasaa akaramafi ooqumari finoo Yeerusareenni ooru finau. Miqiuna ooqai tamummaqara fasiqa akara rumaqoomau ooru finau.
Yeerusaree maqusa moo auqu Sioona maqusee qimarinau. Minara ooqeenaa tamummaqara fasiqafa maaqi qimasee akara rinau. Innee Sioona maqusanaasa sia rufiaaqa. Inni karaambaiqa innee iannai uridanoommi, doonkisaa ooqu marifi uridanoo.
Yisuna faiqi namu faiqí anaasee qambaana Yisuna faqa ooru fiqau. Misa tamummaqara fasiqa akara iridaqa anoonara sia iridaqa fiqau. Kasooqaqee Yisufa kuqiranakiqari findifufaqa misa oonumafi iriseeqa qiqau. Maasa ooqai akara rumaqoomau Yisuna faqa Yeerusareenni ooru fiqiafana.
Yisufa Rasarusana aaroofanoo findifuna qafeeusa Yeerusaree maqusaki suqiqa marusa Rasarusanara qimannimiqau.
Faiqí anaasee moomoo mi ufana iriseeqa maaqi qiqau. Firaa ainaina auqeemarina ooqu afiqamaree uruaqee qimasee ooqu afiqee uriqau.
Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa oomasee maaqi qiqau. Qafaa doo maasa kadiqaidaqa faiqí anaasee minnikai quandaidaqa.
Yeerusareenni ainaaqarara qoomaqara suqimarusaki Kirisa maqannaasa nianai nári maqusaindari anusa faqa miqoo Yuda maqannaasa faqa animariqau. Misa faqa Anutuna qoomaqa sakasee namasee Anutuna amooqiraree qimasee animariqau.
Kirisa maqannaasa aniree Firipina irammiriqa qiqau. Oo maa fasiqa, Yisuna qafararee qidaqa amanee maasa qifiqee finaqa qafaanauree. Firipifa Beetasaida maqusaindaraafa Kariree maqa maaqakinaafa marufa.
Firipifa Anduruna paqurimasee misandiri Yisufuqoo oonuree Kirisa maqannaasara qimamiqau.
Yisufa misara iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Anutufa faiqí nimaaku qini duqu firaaqoo uqeerara aukuana doo animaridanoo. Sia maa maqee imariasa imariandeefau maseenoofau qini duqu uqeeraannoofau. Qini firaa aupurara kuqiranannai qini duqu uqeerainanoo areenaannoo.
Qinee anoona ufa inni qimannimidaqa. Nandi asumu naríara kaqi maridanoo aaduma maridanoo. (Yisufa narí kuqiranara qidanoo nandi asumu kikiqa usinau.) Mifa maqaki ummaqusaifanoo putaa inanoo moomoo kambiqaannoo sia nariraa mariannoo.
Yafasiqa anaasee fee maaqoo narí mariranara rimarifa nandi asumuara foora sia kafaa kambiqaannoo mifa narí marirana kukupaannoo. Yafasiqa anaasee fee maaqoo maa maqanasaa narí mariranara akooqainafa maqaki ummaqusainanoo narí marirana afeediiseenoo naaru marirana maraannoo.
Innee Kirisa maqannaasa qimannimia. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini ainainira faiqikiraree qimaseenoo aufadeemarifa mifa narí maaqoo marirana quqasee qini faqa finafa qinee fuannannai mifa faqa miqoo oonu marida qini dadaaqiannoo. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini duqu uqeeraannoo mina auqu faqa qini qikoofa uqeeraannoo.
Yisufa Yeerusareenni oorufidanoo narí aaqa marusa qimanniminau. Maqee qini daundura fifau faafau inoo marifaqa nana ufee qianauree. Qinee naqimasee qeeqa qikoonara qiana qini kuqiranara qaoo qiannoo fee. Qinee firaa aupurarana marasee maa marunandee fuka kuquanauree qimasee qumuafanausa maridaqa doo qusasaa maridaqa naqimasee qaoo qiraree sia qaoo qianaura.
Miqi qimasee narí aaqa marusa qimannimiseenoo Yisufa quandafinoo narí akoonara Anutunara innaaru qinoo qinau. Oo qipoo, aneenna auqu amooqirana uqeeraa. Miqi qimasoofanoo Anutuna ufa inaarunaindari quminoo qinau. Doo qinee qeeqa duqu amooqirana uqeereeqa doo kafaa uqeeraanauree qinau.
Miqi qimasoofaqa faiqí anaasee moomoo Yisuna faqa Yeerusareenni ooru fimarusa mi ufana iriseeqa qiqau. Innaarunai qiifoo qufaqa akaqausa qiqau. Qangiroo moo fannoo mina faqa ufa qidanoommi.
Yisufa misa ufa iriseenoo qimanniminoo qinau. Sia qiniarau qidaqinoo inniara qidaqinoo.
Doo maqee Anutufa maa maqa maaqanakinaasa qini darifandinnanara narí aanooqira ufa nimiannoo. Doo maqee maa maqa maaqanaki uriqararafa Sadannafa taikaannoo.
Qini daruseeqa auniriranasaa quqaseeqa maqaki rakiqasee uqeeraqisaifaqa maqasaa aiqamatinaindaraasa suqu moodaaqoo qeeqa daaqa quqaanaura.
Miqimasee Yisufa narí kuquaninna oosana qimanniminau.
Qimannimufaqa misa qiqau. Maasa sanda akarakinaa ufa asauku mundiranara naaru naaru mariannoo fee qidaqa. Anee faiqí nimaaku aunirira saqarisaa kuqiraree qimariannana, naqi fee qidanee miqi qidanee. Faiqí nimaakuara anee qianafa yafee mifa maridanoo fee.
Miqi qimasoofanoo Yisufa mina iriseenoo qinau. Kaaqa qarafa inniki qusasaa mariannoo. Kaaqa qarafa mariqoo mi kaaqa qaranasaa kai mariaqa. Miqimmasee marifanoo asukuna fannoo sia rafaaqafuannoo. Asukunaki nimarifa sia aana qafaidanoo kaqimbidanoo.
Kaaqa qarafa mariqoo innee minara riqa anoonee qimasee mi mau fuaqa miqiqa innee kaaqa qaranafaqaasa mariaqa. Miqi qinoo qimannimiseenoo naríara moosaa finau. Miqoo oonu kukeeqanau.
Yisufa oosana oosana firaa ainaina faiqí anaasee nifusaa auqeemarinau. Sia misa minara oonumafi iriqau.
Ooqai Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqa moo auqu Eesaia mifa misa oosanara akara rumaqoofa maridanoo. Mifa maaqi qimasee akara rinau. Oo karaambaiqa, yafee moo fannoo maasa ufa irinoofeeinau sia moo fannoo. Karaambaiqa narí afeeka yau yausee uqannifiqoofaqee anoonee qidee. Sia moo fannoo kuqaa fee qinau.
Miqi qimasee ooqai akara rumaqoofa marufaqa umimmaqidaqa sia Yisunara anoonee qiqau. Eesaiaafa misara kaifaa maaqi qimasee akara rumaqoofa maridanoo.
Anutufa misa nifu dimbaqaifaqa maridaqa. Mifa misa nitikura ititaquqaifaqa mariaqeera. Misa nifu sia qafaaqeera misa naaqoo sia iriaqeera. Qinee unnannai faqa sia quandafifaqa sia amiqimannisaaqeera.
Eesaiaafa sia fifaufau maa ufana qimasee akara rumaqoofau maridanoofau. Mifa ooqaindari Yisufa sia kambiqooqoo afu pisipasamafinoo Yisuna afeeka eeraarirana qafaidanoo akara rimarufa maridanoo.
Kuqaa moomoosa Anutuna tamummaqarausa ufamau fidaqa Yisunara sia iriqau. Miqidaqa Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa akaqausa moomoosa Anutuna tamumaqarausa ufamau fidaqa Yisunara sia iriqau. Miqidaqa Yuda maqannaa uriqararausa akaqausa kukeeqasee Yisunara iri mariqau. Farisai amaana ufa qimarusa amaana maqakiqari maasa diqiqamasaifaqa sia kaifaa keeqaanauroo qimasaida qumeeree mariqau.
Misa sia Anutuna afusaa eedoo qiranara rimariqau. Faiqí nifusaa eedoo qiranara kai kaaqa rimarunara Yisunara kukeeqee mariqau.
Yisufa kafaa moo kari faiqí anaasee qimanniminoo qinau. Yafasiqa anaasee qini saqarikidanoo fee. Mifa sia qini kai, qini diqiqamaqoona mina faqa saqarikidanoo.
Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini qiqafaidanoo fee mifa qini diqiqamaqoona mina faqa qafaidanoo.
Qinee kaaqa qarausa maa maqa maaqanaki animaridaqa. Qiniki mariasa sia asukunaki mariaqeera animaridaqa.
Yafee moo fannoo qini ufa irisee sia auqainnana sia qinee qeeqa ufa amianaura. Sia qinee doori runira ufa nimiraree qimasee qumuafanausa maridaqa. Qinee faiqí anaasee Anutuna nifairiranakinaana qumarasee asumu marirana nimianeera qumuafanausa maridaqa.
Yafee moo fannoo qini minnisainafa qinee ufa qimarunnana minnisainaqa sia qeeqa ufa mina amianaura. Kasoo taikara faasaana Anutufa qini dookinaa ufa maqee qimannimimarunnana maraseenoo minannoo naruannoo.
Qinee sia qeeqa iriranannai ufa qimannimidaqa qini diqiqamaqoona qini qikoona uqaqifiqoo ainaina kai qimannimidaqa uqannifiqaidaqa.
Qinee qeeqa qikoona ufa iridaqa mina ufa fannoo kai naaru naaru marirana nimidanoo. Qinee minara iridaqa qeeqa qikoona ufa kai qimannimidaqa.
Anutuna ainnaaqarara qoomaqa adeedi ramafufanoo Yisufa maa maqana quqasee doo narí akoofinai firafa adeedi reemarufanoo minara Yisufa irimarinau. Maa maqa maaqanakinaasa narisaa atooqeemariasara amuqusufanoo ridanoo kaqi misara aidimarufanoo fidanoo kasaaqai munu kuqinau.
Yisufa narana eendaki sakasaida narí faiqi namufaqa neemarinau. Yudasifa Keerioota maqusaindaraafa indaaruqaa Simoona amarana amaaku mifa Yisuna faiqi namufaqa miqoo marufa faasai Sadannafa mina dadaaqufanoo Yisunara ueeqararee qidanoo deedaqimarinau.
Anutufa aiqama afeeka innaaruna faqa maqa faqa Yisuna aramandunnai quqaqoofanoo marufanoo Yisufa mina irida marinau. Narí Anutufinaindari qumufa iridanoo marinau. Narí kaifaa Anutufinnai ooru firafa adeedi ranoo marufanoo minara faqa irida marinau.
Yisufa narí faiqi namufaqa narana namaseenoo findifinoo narí siuta raipaqusee taura qumareenoo narí aranandauqanna rumbaseenoo difaani maraseenoo nammari minaki adiaseenoo narí faiqi namu niku nammaruqusaidanoo taurannai rukannimaqeemarinau. (Yisufa maru aukuana mina maqannaa oosana maaqimminoo marinau. Faiqí moo fannoo moo maqusaindari narí aqoondi qafararee qimasee ani mina maaqaki keeqafinanoo maaqa akoofa mi fasiqana qafeenoo narí ainainira fasiqa ureeqarana aaramasee qimaminoo anee maa fasiqana aiku nammaruquseenana taura qumaree rukasainanoo ooqumariani. Mi oosanna niku nammaruqira saika sia uriqararausa maree mariqau ureeqarausa faaqu fasiqa fooqaasa miqimariqau.)
<range>
Yisufa Simoona moo auqu Peetooroona aiku nammaruqirarufanoo Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa qinau. Oo Karaambaiqa kuqaa fee anee qini qiku nammaruqiraree qidanee. Sia miqia, anee uriqararafa mariananoo.
Yisufa qinau, Eeoo nammari uquanaura anee maqee sia qini oosana irimariananoo kasooqaqee irinnaranoo.
Peetooroofa qinau, anee maasa uriqararafa mariananoo naaru naaru sia uqanna qini manda qiku nammaruqua. Yisufa mina iriseenoo qinau. Qinee ani aiku sia nammari uquanana maaqooqari anee sia qini faiqikinnaranoo.
Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa mi ufana iriseenoo qinau. Oo karaambaiqa sia qiku kai nammaruqua qisauku faqa qikiaqa faqa aiqama nammari uqua.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo qinau. Faiqí nammari auqeemariasa aiqama nifaaqa amiqinoo maridanoo niku kai doona kookoomma akinoo maridanoo. Innee aiqama amiqiqa mariafanoo moodaa fannoo mandaikinoo marifaqa qafaidaqa.
Yisufa faasai narí ueeqee maruna qafaidanoo miqi qinau. Inni nifaaqa aiqama nammari uqinoo maridanoo. Moodaa fannoo kai sia nammari auqara fee qinau. Narí ueeqaaninnanara iriseenoo miqi qinau.
Yisufa narí faiqi namu niku nammari uquseenoo kafaa narí siuta afisumaree kafaa misa faqa ooqumari finoo qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee inni niku nammari uqunnanara iridee sia fee iridee.
Doo maqee mina nammari uqunnana oosana kooroo ianaura. Innee qiniara ufasaa rakisira fee karaambaiqee qimariafanoo. Doo mina kuqaa qimariafanoo qinee miqirausa maridaqa.
Qinee inni ufasaa rakisirausa inni karaambaiqa maridaqa ureeqarausa saika mareemariana misa naanna raidaqa inni niku nammari uqidaqa innee miqi kai iqa qini daanna reeqa ureeqara fasiqa anaaseera foora narí dadaaqi narí dadaaqiaqa.
Qinee uqannifiqaunnana qafeeqa qinee unandee kai iaqanani.
Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa inni qimannimidaqa. Ainainira fasiqa fannoo sia narí rakisirana uriqararafa maridanoo. Ufa maree fimari fasiqafa sia aqiqeemarina uraaqararafa maridanoo.
Innee maqee maa ufana anoona naaqooki irimariafanoo. Innee maa ufana irisee auqaifanoo asasirafa mariannoo.
Yisufa kaifaa narí faiqi namu maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Anutuna tamummaqara fasiqauqa ooqeenaa akara oosana maaqimminoo maridanoo. Innikiqari moodaa fannoo qini narana qini faqa neemarifa mifa qini namuqaakinoo aranaiqi daruannoo. Maa akarana oosana inniki kambiqaannoo, sia inni aiqamara qidaqa. Qinee oonu mareeqee qeeqaindika maqaunausa mariafanoo moodaa fannoo kai.
Qinee maqeesaa qimannimidaqa sia kambiqai kamuqoo qimannimidaqa. Kambiqainaqa innee qiniara irifaranoo. Qinee qeeqaraa ufa qunausa doo misaki maridaqa.
Qinee anoona ufa kuqaa qimannimidaqa. Faiqí anaasee moo fannoo qinee inni niqiqamaqaanausa niqoondikinafa qini faqa qiqoondikidanoo. Faiqí anaasee moo fannoo qini qiqoondikamma qimaqainafa qini diqiqamaqoona faqa kai aqoondikidanoo.
Yisufa minara qimanniminsoofanoo narí aunduraki oonumafi irufanoo amuqusufanoo kafaa kooroomasee qimanniminau. Qinee anoona ufa qimannimidaqa innikiqari moo fannoo qiniara ueeqaannoo.
Yisuna faiqi namu mi ufana iriseeqa tautumakufaqa narí qafee narí qafee idaqa randaqau.
Yisuna afaaqasaa aqoondi fannoo mina aaqa ooqumarifi marinau.
Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa mi fasiqana auqamaseenoo qinau anee karaambaiqa irammirisee iria. Yafasiqanaree qidanoo fee yafee ani ueeqaannoo fee.
Miqi qufanoo mi fasiqafa Yisuna aaqa firambaqafufanoo maqandanai irammirinau Karaambaiqa yafee ani ueeqaannoo fee.
Yisufa qinau, qinee feemu rakeemandeeqa sauna anoona fooqaanaki raaraamandee amianana qafa. Mifa kai qini ueeqaannoo. Miqi qimasee Yisufa feemu rakeemaseenoo sauna anoona fooqaanaki raaraameeqeenoo Yudasifa Keerioota maqannaa Simoona amarana amaaku aminau.
Yudasifa mi feemuna qumarasee namasoofanoo doo Sadannafa mina aundurai keeqanau. Miqufanoo Yisufa Yudasina qimaminoo qinau. Doo anee aneenna inna ainaina doo dauni dauni ia.
Miqoo marusa sia Yisuna ufa oosana iriqau.
Yudasifa Yisuna faiqi namu munnimmasaa rakisimarufa marufanoo Yisufa aqiqoofaqa misa narana aina fi fi maraanifeera aqiqee maqi qiqau. Kudi fasiqauqa munnimma nimiannoo fee qiqau.
Yudasifa mi feemuna mara namaseenoo findimeeqeenoo aaqee kai eendaki raudamaki finau.
Yudasifa fufanoo Yisufa kaifaa narí faiqi namu qimanniminoo qinau. Doo maqee faiqí nimaaku qini amiqi amiqira afeeka eeraarirafa doo kooroo inoo maridanoo.
Anutuna afeeka eeraarirafa qinisaa kooroo inoo maridanoo, Anutufa narí uqanna quandaki qini qifaaqa firaaqoo areenaannoo, qusasaa maqee uqanna miqiannoo.
Qini faiqi namu sia kisaaqasaa inniki marianaura. Yuda maqannaa qimannimiafannandee kai inni qimannimidaqa. Innee qiniara randee sia paqurifaranoo. Qinee fuannaqoo sia innee amana fifaranaoo.
Doo maqee qinee fuka aaquqira ufa qimannimidaqa. Innee nariara nariara nimuqusidaqa nariara nariara ruaqa. Qinee inniara qimuqusufaqa inniara rimariqia innee faqa qini daanna raaqa nariara nariara ruaqa.
Innee nariara nariara rimarifaqa aiqamausa inni nindafeeqa inniara boo Yisuna faiqi namu miqidammiafoo qiaqa.
Yisufa miqi qimasoofanoo Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa irammirinoo qinau, Oo Karaambaiqa anee yai fee finaqee maasa sia ani faqa fuanauree. Yisufa iriseenoo qinau, Qinee maqee fuanannai anee sia amana qini faqa finnaranoo, kasooqaqee anee qini faqa finnaranoo.
Simoona moo auqu Peetooroofa iriseenoo qimaminau, Karaambaiqa anee naqi naqee qinee sia ani faqa fuanauree. Qinee aniara kuquanauranoo.
Yisufa mi ufana iriseenoo qimaminoo qinau, Kuqaa fee anee maqee qiniara kuqinnaree, qinee anoona ufa ani qimamidaqa fafaa eendaki kookooraana sia ufa qinnakamuqoo anee kuqiranara rufiaseenana qaaramoo kari qiniara sia qafaunausee qinanoo kookooraana ufa qiannoo.
Yisufa miqi qimaseenoo aiqama qimanniminoo qinau. Innee sia nimukee marinaqa maparaaiaqa. Innee Anutuna saqariki mariafanoo doo qini faqa saqarikiaqa.
Qini qikoona innaaruna maqusaki moomoo maqa narí aaqa narí aaqa maridanoo. Qinee maindari ooruree innee ooru fifandinna maqana auqirara ooru fidaqa. Minara qinee kuqaa anoona ufa kai inni qimannimidaqa. Sia anoona marinaqau sia qimannimunaiqini. Kuqaa anoona marifaqa qimannimidaqa.
Qinee innaarunai oorureeqa innee ooru fifandinna maqusana deedaqamasee qumu nifiqee minni murunnisaanaura. Innee qini faqa mariaqeera miqianaura.
Innee qinee marunnannai fimaria aanara irimariafanoo.
Toomasifa mi ufana iriseenoo qinau, Anee fimariannanara maasa sia iridaqa. Naqimasee fee mi aannara irianauree.
Yisufa iriseenoo maaqi qimaseenoo qimaminoo qinau, qinee mi aanausa maridaqa. Qinee kuqaa anoona ufa maridaqa. Naaru naaru marirafa qiniki maridanoo qinee misa maridaqa. Sia moo fannoo kaqi qini qikoofinnai fidanoo qinimau kai fifaranoo.
Innee qiniara irifau qini qikoonara faqa irini. Maqee mariaqooqari qini qikoonara iriqa qini qikoona qafee mariafanoo.
Firipifa mi ufana iriseenoo Yisuna qimaminoo qinau, Oo karaambaiqa aneenna akoona uqaqifiqainaqa qafamasee doo fee qianaura.
Yisufa mina iriseenoo akooqoofanoo raiqaseenoo qinau. Firipi qinee kisaaqasaa inni faqa mariafanausa marunana anee sia irirana irimariananoo. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qini qiqafainafa doo qini qikoona qafaidanoo. Anee nanaree qiniara aneenna akoona uqaqifiqaannee q inanee.
Firipi anee sia fee qini ufara anoonee qidanee. Qinee qipaqeenaki faqa maridaqa mifa qiniki faqa maridanoo sia fee anee mi ufana iridanee. Yisufa kafaa narí faiqi namu aiqama qimanniminoo qinau. Qinee inni ufa qimannimimarunafa sia qeeqa daundurakinaana qimannimidaqa. Qini qikoofa qiniki marifa narí irirana iriseenoo qifaqa narí qimau kai fidaqa qimannimidaqa.
Innee maa ufana irisee anoonee qiaqa. Qinee qeeqa qikoonaki maridaqa mifa qiniki faqa maridanoo. Innee qini ufara sia fee qimasee qinee auqaannainaina faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainaina nifunnoo qafamasee Anutufa mina faqa maridanoo fee qiaqa.
Qinee anoona ufa qimannimidaqa faiqí anaasee moo fannoo qini saqarikinafa qinee ianandee iannoo. Qinee qeeqa qikoofinnai fuannanara qini saqarikinafa sia qini daanna kai raannoo qini saika uraaqaranoo mariannoo. Mina oosana maaqimminoo maridanoo.
Innee innaaru qidaqa qini duqusaa qimasee innaaru qifaqa nimianaura. Sia moo ainaina sia nimianaura innaaru qifaqa nimianaura. Qini qikoona afaaqa areenarafa qinisaaqari faqa areenaanifeera nimianauura.
Innee qini duqusaa qimasee innaaru qifaqa qinee mi ainainna miqimannisaanauranoo.
Yisufa narí faiqi namu kaqi qimannimidanoo qinau. Innee qiniara riqa qinee qimannimiafannufana andeeqasee qumareefaranoo. Sia qiniara riqa sia qinee qiafannufana qumareefaranoo.
Qinee inni minnisee ooru fiqa qeeqa qikoona irammiriananoo Anutuna dadaaqira afeeka maraquna nimiannoo. Mifa kuqaa anoona ufa qiroosana maraquna qumu mariannoo, mi maraqunafa naaru naaru inni faqa mariannoo.
Maa maqanasaa mariasa sia qini Yisusa mandaaqee marinausa sia amana mi maraqunna mareefaranoo. Misa sia mina qafaidaqa sia minara irimariafanoo minara sia mareefaranoo. Mifa inni faqa mapukusee maridanoo kuqaa inni naundurai anoona mariannoo. Mifa inni faqa marifaqa innee mi maraqunna oosana irimariafanoo.
Qinee sia inni mininnisaanaura qinee oorureeqa Anutuna maraquna aqiqaananoo qumuree inni faqa marida dadaaqiannoo.
Kaqikaaqoo maa maqanasaaqaraa irirana faqaasa sia qini qiqafeefaranoo. Innee kai qini qiqafeefaranoo. Qinee kaqi marirausa maridaqa minara innee kaqi marirana mareefaranoo.
Qinee qeeqa qikoonaki maridaqa kafaa innee qiniki mariafanoo qinee inniki maridaqa. Anutuna maraquna qumuaninna faasaana mi faasaanna mi ufana oosana amiqimandee irifaranoo.
Yafasiqa anaasee fee qinee qimannimiafanna ufana irisee maree marifandinausa misa kai qiniara rifandinausa marifara. Qiniara rimarina fasiqa anaaseesara qini qikoofa misara faqa ruannoo qinee faqa mi fasiqa anaaseesara ruanaura qeeqaindi anoona afeeka uqannifiqaanaura.
Yudasina amarafa Yisuna irammirinoo qinau, Oo Karaambaiqa naqimaseenanee anee maasa qifusaa kai kooroo innaree maa maqa maaqanasaaqaraa irirana faqaasa nifusaa kukeeqararee qidanee.
Yisufa iriseenoo qinau. Yafasiqa anaasee fee qiniara rimarinafa qini ufa maree mari fasiqa anaaseefa mifa qiniara rimarifa mariannoo. Miqinna fasiqa anaaseena qini qikoofa Anutufa minara faqa ruannoo. Mifa faqa qinee faqa mi fasiqa anaaseesa innannai oonuree umee mina faqa marianaura, miqimaseeqa maasa inni nifusaa kai koorooianaura. Maqasaaqaraa irirana faqaasa nifusaa kukeeqaanaura.
Yafasiqa aanaaseesee sia qiniara rinausa misa qini ufa sia irifara. Qinee qimannimira ufa innee irimariafanoo, sia qinindi maridanoo, qini qikoofa qini diqiqamaqainaindi minaindi maridanoo.
Qinee maa ufausa inni faqa kaqi maridaqa qimannimidaqa.
Inni fuka dadaaqirafa naaquqara maraquna qini qikoofa kasooqaqee nimianinnafa mifa aiqama ainainara qimannimiannoo. Qinee faqa aiqama ufa qimannimiafannana mifa minara inni naaqoo auqainaqa oonumafi irifaranoo.
Qinee naundura asooarana inni nimidaqa. Qinee qiniki mari naundura asooarana inni nimidaqa. Maa maqanasaa mariasa sia misa naanna ramasee inni nimidau. Amiqimandee qeeqa asooarana nimianaura. Sia inni naundura rapikiani sia rufiaqa rufiaqiaqa.
Qinee maqee maaqooqari kafaa ooru fuanaura oorureeqa marikiqa oorurandee qumureeqa inni faqa marianaura. Sia qinee ooru fuannanara innee minara rufiaaqa. Innee kuqaa qiniara ridau qinee qeeqa qikoofinnai fuannanara susummaqimaqani. Qini qikoofa qini uriqararafa maridanoo minara susummaqimaqani.
Qinee maqee sia kambiqauna kamuqoo aiqama ainainara qimannimidaqa. Kambiqafinaqa innee qiniara iriaqeera qimannimidaqa.
Qinee sia amana inni faqa kisaaqasaa ufa qianaura. Maa maqanasaa rakisirafa Sadannafa doo anidanoo qini afeeka fannoo mina afeeka uraaqaranoo maridanoo.
Maa maqanasaaqaraasa qinee qeeqa qikoonara rimarunnana minara iriaqeera mina ufamau andeeqasee fidaqa qinee qeeqa kai irisee Sadanna asauku ameemaanai oonuree kuquanaura. Miqi qimaseenoo Yisufa narí faiqi namuara doo uqeeraifaqa maaqooqari moosaa fuanee qimasee uqeereenoo moosaa finau.
Yisufa fidanoo maa ufana narí faiqi namu qimanniminau. Qinee saunara foora qinee marunna saqarisa maridaqa. Qini qikoofa sauna saqamasaa rakisimarifa maridanoo.
Qini qikoofa Anutufa mi sauna saqarina sia irainanoo ateeka idaraannoo. Ireemari oosanna amiqimandee iraani fee qimasee anukamasaidanoo amiqimasee rakisidanoo.
Qinee qimannimimarunnufana innee irisee maraifanoo doo inni mandainaina rukannisaifaqa anukaraqoo mariafanoo.
Innee saqari asaanara foora qinisaa ariqa mariaqa. Innee sia qinisaa ariqa maridaqa sia qini amiqira marira nirana mareefaranoo.
Qinee saqari anoona maridaqa. Innee asaana miqirausa mariafanoo sia anoonasaa arufinafa sia sauna iraannoo. Qiniki marinausa qinee faqa misaki mariananoo saunara foora moomoo ireefaranoo. Innee inneeqaraa marinausa kudi marifaranoo qini faqa marinausa sauna amiqimasee ireemarifaranoo. Innee minara iriseeqa amiqimasee qinisaa atooqaifaqa qinee faqa inniki marianaura.
Faiqí moo fannoo sia qiniki marinafa sauna asaana miqirafa aadanusidanoo marinanoo saunasaa rakisimarifa asaana qafamasee aadanusinausa aiqama ateekasee suqeeqeenoo idaki aqusainanoo qamataikaannoo.
Innee qiniki marirara kai idaqa marifaqa qinee qimannimunna ufafa inniki marirara kai imarinaqa innee nana ainainaree qiniara iraifaqa nimianaura.
Innee andeeqara marirana qaqammara foora moomoo iraifanoo minannai qini qikoona amiqira afeeka eeraarira areenarana kooroomannimaqaannoo. Miqiuqanna iqa qini faiqinamuka mafifaranoo.
Qini qikoofa qiniara firaaqoo ridanoo qinee faqa miqikai iqa inniara firaa qoo ridaqa doo sia innee moo fannoo minakiqari aiaki fuaqa. Kaqi kai qini didiranaki mariaqa.
Innee qinee qimannimuna ufana irisee qumareeqa qini didiranaki marifaranoo. Qinee miqikaimasee qeeqa qikoona ufa iriseeqa qumareeqa mina aidiranaki maridaqa.
Qinee sia kaqi qimannimidaqa qini susuirafa inniki marianifeera inni susuirafa anoonaikianifeera qimannimidaqa.
Qinee ufa moo aaquqira ufa qimannianaura iriaqa Innee qini daanna ramasee nariara nariara ridaqa nidiani.
Faiqí moo fannoo narí aqoondi amaaqa maqasee kuqinna fasiqafa mina aidirafa aiqama nidirana arusee uriqaramaqaraasa uqanna inoo mariannoo.
Maqee maqee qini aaquqira ufa irisee mi mau fimariasa misa kai qini qiqoondiuqa maridaqa.
Qinee sia maaqooqari inniara qini ainainira faiqí fee qianaura. Rakisirafa narí fuaninnanara faqa auqaaninnanara faqa maraaninnanara faqa sia ainainira faiqiuqa qimannimidanoo miqimmianauree maaqimmianuree qidanoo narí kai. Ainainiaqee ufa kai qimannimidanoo. Qinee sia fifau saikira faiqi fee qidaqa inniara qini qiqoondi fee qimasaidaqa qinee qini qikoofa auqaaninna saika ufanara aiqama inni kooroomannimidaqa.
Sia innee qini rusandeesamumandee qini qumaraafanoo. Qinee naaree inniara rusandeesamumandee inni qumareeqa. Inni marirafa nirafa qini daanna ramasee mariaqeera qinindikiaqeera qimasee inni mareeqa. Mi marira oosanafa sia putaa iannoo afeeka kai mariannoo. Innee minara irisee nana sarauimari ainainaree qini qikoofinnai innaaru qimasee qini duqusaa innaaru qimasaifanoo nimiannoo.
Doo qeeqa aaquqira ufa maaqi qimasee qimannimidaqa. Innee nariara nariara ridaqa nidiaqa.
Maa maqanasaaqaraasa inniara fidiaqaammifaranoo maanara iriaqa indaaru qini Yisusara fidiaqaaiaasa mariafanoo innindi inaaqianna fidiaqaairafa mariannoo.
Innee qini faiqi namu maa maqa maaqanasaaqaraasa faqa moodaa irirana faqaasa marifaqau misa inniara maasaindi fee qimaseefau inniara rini. Qinee inni maa maqa maaqanakinaasa rusandeesamumasee qumaraqaunausa mariafaqa maqee sia misaindi marianara minara kaukaata qimannimaqaidaqa.
Maa ufana qimannimunnana kaifaa iriaqa ainainira fasiqa sia narí rakisirana uriqararafa maridanoo. Misa qini inni rakisirana dariqa quandaki inni faqa qini ufa irimariasa faqa narifaranoo, misa qini ufa iriqa quandaki inni ufa faqa irifaranoo.
Innee qinindi marianara oosana oosana mandainaina maa maqanasaaqaraasa inni nimifaranoo. Misa sia qini diqiqoonara Anutunara iridaqa miqifaranoo.
Qinee maa maqanasaaqaraasa mandainainara sia kooroomma nimaqaananoo fau sia misa manda numoo mariqini. Doo qinee misa mandoosanara kooroomasee misa qimannimiqauna iridaqa Anutuna narira ufa ameemaanai maridaqa sia amana unnufannai mina ititeefaranoo, narirafa kaqi naruannoo.
Faiqí moo fannoo qiniara fidiaqaammidanoo qini qikoonara faqa fidiaqaammidanoo.
Qinee misa nifusaa faiqí sia auqaaqaa ira ainaina auqaafannana sia maqasaa fasiqa moo fannoo mi ainainna auqoofanoo anoona kambiqanau. Qinee sia miqimaseeqa mi ainainna auqaananoofau misa numoo sia mariqini. Qinee oosana oosana ainaina auqaunaqa misa sia amiqimasee maaqanda qisakoosara irirai maaqandara fidiaqaamma qimaqaidaqa.
Mooseena sandufa ooqai misara akara rumaqoofa maridanoo. Mifa maaqi qimasee akara rinau. Misa kaqi fifau miqidaqa qiniara fidiaqaaida marifara. Anutuna ufa miqinoo maridanoo naqimasee moosaa fifaree. Minara misa qiniara fidiaqaaidaqa.
Yisufa kaqi narí faiqi namu qimannimidanoo qinau. Qinee ooru fuananoo fuka dadaaqirafa qumuannoo. Mifa kuqaa anoona ufa qira oosana maraquna mariannoo qini qikoofinaindaraafa mariannoo. Qinee qeeqa qikoofinaindaraana aqiqaananoo qumureenoo mifa qiniara qimannimiannoo.
Mifa inni naakinaqa innee faqa qiniara ufa qifaranoo. Innee oosanakiqari qini faqa niniaasa maridaqa qiniara ufa qifaranoo.
Innee aanai fiqa niku rupauraki saamuriqa qini minnisee foora minara naamua qimarunausa maridaqa.
Kasooqaqee faiqí misa nariqa amaana maqakiqarifee ufa suqira maqakiqarifee aanoommasee inni niqiqeefaranoo. Kasooqaqee nariqa aaqamasee kuqaa Anutuna dadaaqidee qiqa inni kuqa narifaranoo.
Misa qini qikoona Anutunara faqa qiniara faqa sia iridaqa miqifaranoo.
Maqee maa kamuqoo qinee marunnaqoo maa ainainnausara qimannimimariana irimarifanoo kasooqaqee kambiqainaqa inneeqa naaqoonnai oonumafi iriaqeera qidaqa. Qinee indaaru sia qimannimiqa qinee inni faqa kaqi maridaqara qiqa sia qimannimiafanausa qinee qusasaa firaridaqa qimannimidaqa.
Maqee qini qikoofa qini diqiqamaqoonnai ooru firaridaqa innikiqari moo fannoo sia qini iraidanoo anee yai fee fidanee miqidanee.
Doo qinee firara inni qimannimunaqa inni naundura qumaara raifaqa noori runusee mariafanoo.
Qinee anoona ufa qimannimidaqa qinee ooru fuanaqa innee amiqiranaki mariaqeera ooru fuanaura. Qinee sia ooru fuananoo fuka dadaaqirafa sia qumuree inni dadaaqiannoo. Qinee ooruree fuka dadaaqirana aqiqaananoo qumu inni faqa maridanoo dadaaqiannoo.
Fuka dadaaqirafa qumu maridanoo inni maqasaaqaraasa irirana aaqaidanoo fee qiannoo inni andeeqaranara faqa manda oosanara faqa Anutuna narira ufa nimianinnanara faqa aaqee mariafanoommifoo qimasee qimannimiannoo.
Maqasaa fasiqauqa qiniara sia irifaqee qidaqa minara nári manda oosanara amiqira oosana fee qimasaidaqa aaqaidaqa.
Qinee qeeqa qikoofinai ooru firaridaqa maqasaaqaraasa sia kaifaa qini qiqafeefaranoo, minara fuka dadaaqirafa maqasaaqaraasa andeeqara oosanara aaqee mariafanoo fee qiannoo.
Maa maqanasaaqaraa rakisirana aakaaqaindaraa fasiqa doo Anutuna arira ufa doo mi manda fasiqanasaa maridanoo. Minara Anutuna narira ufa fannoo maa maqanasaaqaraa fasiqa aanaaseesaa faqa maridanoo minara faqa misa sia andeeqasee iridaqa aaqaidaqa.
Qinee moomoo ainainara qimannimianaqa qumaara rainaqa siamma irifaranoo.
Miqimarianara kuqaa anoona ufa qira maraquna fannoo qumureenoo inni mareeqeenoo anoona ufa mariranaki mara quqaannoo. Sia mi maraqunafa narí kai ufa qimannimiannoo qini dookinaana kai irinoo inni qimannimiannoo. Mifa kasooqaqee kambiqaaninna ainainara tamummaqasee iriseenoo inni qimannimiannoo.
Mifa qini irira ufa mareeqee inni niminaqa minannai qini Yisuna asasirana qimimarifaranoo.
Qini qikoona Anutuna ainaina aiqama qinindi kai maridanoo. Minara qinee inni maana qimannimiqa kafaa qimannimidaqa. Qinee qeeqa irirana marasee anoona ufa qira maraquna qimamiananoo mifa quandaki inni qimannimiannoo.
Yisufa narí faiqinamu kaqi qimannimidanoo qinau. Kaqikaaqoo innee sia qini qiqafeefaranoo kaqikaaqoo marikiqa kaifaa qini qiqafeefaranoo.
Yisuna faiqi namu mina irisee akaqausa maaqi qiqau. Maa ufana nanaree qidanoo fee. Mifa nariara kaqikaa qoo sia qini qiqafeefaranoo fee qidanoo. Kaifaa kaqikaaqoo marikiqa qini qiqafeefaranoo fee qidanoo. Kaifaa nariara qeeqa qikoofinai firaree qidaqee qidaqinoo.
Mifa kaqikaa qoo fee qidaqinoo mi ufana oosanara maasa randaidaqa. Maasa sia mina ufa oosanara iridaqa naqi fee qidaqinoo fee.
Yisufa misa randaranara irisee maaqi qimasee qimanniminau. Qinee qiqa. Kaqikaaqoo sia qini qiqafeefaranoo. Kaqikaaqoo marikiqa qini qiqafeefaranoo. Innee minaree narí qimami narí qimami qidee.
Qinee anoona ufa qimannimianaura. Qinee kuquanna kamuqoo innee ikifaafau qifaranoo. Innee miqimariafaqa maqasaaqaraasa qiniara sia irimariasa susuifaranoo. Innee noori runusee marifaranoo qinee kuqiranakiqari findi fuanaqa kafaa mi noori runirana minnisee quandakinaqa asasifaranoo.
Anaasee moo fannoo amuaqu uqafaqa maridanoo oori runusee maridanoo, doo aupurarafa aidafirafa minaki marinara miqidanoo. Miqidanoo mariifanoo faiqi maqasaifanoo doo aupurarafa faqa aidafirafa faqa taikeefoo qimaseenoo doo qini faiqi kambiqaifaqee qimasee aidafiranara aunusee asasidanoo.
Innee mina aanna reefaranoo. Maqee kamuqoo noori runusee marifaranoo. Kasooqaqee qini qiqafamasaifanoo miqoo inni nimuqusaki asasirafa firaaqoo qumbiqanoo mariannoo. Mi asasirana sia moo fannoo mareemaria asasirafa mariannoo. Afeeka asasirafa amiqirafa kaqi mariannoo.
Qinee kuqiranakiqari findifiqa qeeqa qikoofinnai ooru marianaqa innee sia kafaa qiniara moo ainainara irammirifaranoo. Qinee anoona ufa qimannimidaqa. Innee qiniara faiqi namu maridee qimasee qini qikoona irammirifanoo iraifandinna ainaina oosana oosana nimiannoo.
Maa maria kamu sia moo ainainara qiniara aqoondi fee qimasee Anutufinnai innaaru qimariananoo. Irammiriaqa. Irammirifanoo nimiani. Innee asasirafa anoonaikianifeera Anutufa nimiannoo.
Qinee kukeeqara ufannai inni qimannimi mariafannana. Qusasaa sia qinee kukeeqaanaura kooroomandee qeeqa qikoona Anutunara akooqoo qimannimianaura.
Mi faasaanna anirainaqa qini duqusaa Anutunara innaaru qifaranoo. Innee innaaru qifaqa qinee sia qeeqa qikoona afusaa oonuree mi ainainnara inni fifau dadaaqianaura.
